NK066(chu)001:3776: rigs bdag gi shul du mi bskyod pa 'byung ba yin no //
NK066(chu)001:3777: 'o na 'dir rigs kyi dbye ba gang zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:3779: mi bskyod byed po yum dang bcas //
NK066(chu)001:3780: rdo rje 'dzin par phyag rgyar bstan //
NK066(chu)001:3781: byams pa sa snying de bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:3782: gzhan dag rang gi phyag rgyas te //
NK066(chu)001:3783: gshin rje gshed la rtags par bshad //
NK066(chu)001:3785: zla dang bral ba'i dpa' bo che //
NK066(chu)001:3786: zhes pas mi bskyod pa yab yum //
NK066(chu)001:3788: zla bo yum dang phral bas dpa' bo gcig pa'i lha thub drug ste /
NK066(chu)001:3789: rdo rje'i rigs kyi lha bcu la mi bskyod pa bdag por gyur pas dbu brgyan te /
NK066(chu)001:3790: thog mtha'i rkang pa gnyis gnyis kyi lung don no //
NK066(chu)001:3793: gshin rje gshed rnams so so'i yum dang bcas pa'i
NK066(chu)001:3794: de bzhin rigs kyi lha brgyad la rtag pa rnam
NK066(chu)001:3795: par snang mdzad bdag por gyur pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:3796: lung gi rkang pa gsum pa dang lnga pa'i don no //
NK066(chu)001:3797: de dag gi shugs las lha gzhan rnams kyi rigs kyang shes par 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:3798: mi bskyod pa rdo rje'i rigs yin par shes pa'i shugs kyis /
NK066(chu)001:3802: don grub las rigs yin par shes pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:3803: sa snying dang byams pa de bzhin rigs yin pa'i shugs kyis nam snying dang sgrib sel rin chen /
NK066(chu)001:3804: spyan gzigs dang kun bzang pad+ma //
NK066(chu)001:3805: phyag rdor dang 'jam dpal las rigs yin par shes pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:3806: gshin rje gshed de bzhin rigs yin pa'i shugs kyis /
NK066(chu)001:3809: 'khyil ba las rigs yin par mtshon nus pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:3810: gzhan dag rang gi phyag rgyas te //
NK066(chu)001:3813: shar dang shar lho'i lha rnams mi bskyod pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:3814: zhes sa snying dang byams pa rdo rje'i rigs su bzhed pa na /
NK066(chu)001:3815: byams pa sa snying de bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:3816: zhes pa rkang pa snga ma'i rdo rje'i rigs la bsnyeg par dgongs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:3819: dbang lha kun bzang yab yum gyi rnam par spyan
NK066(chu)001:3820: drangs nas gnyis su med pa'i byang sems kyi chu
NK066(chu)001:3821: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bar
NK066(chu)001:3822: mdzad pa ni / de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK066(chu)001:3823: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bdag nyid chen pos bdag nyid
NK066(chu)001:3824: chen po'i ye shes dang byin bsdu ba /
NK066(chu)001:3825: zhes pa la dgongs sam snyam mo //
NK066(chu)001:3827: lha rnams kyi spyi bor klad pa dung khang gi
NK066(chu)001:3828: nang du zla ba la gnas pa'i yig dkar po
NK066(chu)001:3829: / mgrin pa'i dbus su pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aahdamara po /
NK066(chu)001:3830: thugs ka'i snying ga'i mdun du nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po /
NK066(chu)001:3831: de gsum gyi 'od kyis rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK066(chu)001:3832: rdo rje gsum gyi lha tshogs dpag tu med pa spyan drangs te so sor bstim /
NK066(chu)001:3833: yi ge gsum zhu ba'i 'od phung las /
NK066(chu)001:3834: spyi bor rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK066(chu)001:3835: mgrin par mtha' yas dmar po pad+ma /
NK066(chu)001:3836: thugs kar mi bskyod pa sngon po rdo rje 'dzin
NK066(chu)001:3837: pa gsum ka longs sku'i cha byad can gyis rgyas
NK066(chu)001:3839: rdo rje'i phyag rgya gnas so sor gtugs la /
NK066(chu)001:3840: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya dang /
NK066(chu)001:3842: tsit+ta sogs byin rlabs kyi sngags brjod cing /
NK066(chu)001:3843: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum
NK066(chu)001:3844: gyi rang bzhin nga'o snyam du nga rgyal bya ba'o
NK066(chu)001:3846: gnas gsum khyab 'jug yi ge las //
NK066(chu)001:3848: khams gsum byin rlabs gzi byin bsngosa //
NK066(chu)001:3849: rang bzhin rdo rje gsum gnas pa //
NK066(chu)001:3850: rgyu gnyis tshul gyis rang snang ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:3852: yang lte ba dang gsang gnas su zla ba la gnas pa'i yi ge gnyis las /
NK066(chu)001:3854: p+au dza'i sngags kyis yon tan dang phrin las kyi lha gnyis gong ltar bskyed par gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:3856: lte ba rnam gnyis zla ba la //
NK066(chu)001:3857: sngo ljang yi ge s+w+aa h+aa nyid //
NK066(chu)001:3858: rjes mthun 'od las yon tan las //
NK066(chu)001:3859: yan lag rdzogs pa'i gzi byin ldan //
NK066(chu)001:3861: de lta na yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu bsgom par bshad pa dang 'gal te /
NK066(chu)001:3862: lha bcu gcig byung ba'i phyir zer na /
NK066(chu)001:3864: yon tan phrin las gnyis sku gsung thugs kyi zhar byung yin pas /
NK066(chu)001:3865: lam bsgom pa'i dbang du lhag pa'i lhar bsgom mo
NK066(chu)001:3866: zhes bla ma rnams gsungs pa ltar 'thad pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:3868: gnas gcig ye shes sems dpa' bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:3869: spyi mgrin tsit+ta'i gnas gsum du //
NK066(chu)001:3870: byin rlabs rdo rje gsum du bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:3871: dbu yi gnas lnga'i ye shes lnga //
NK066(chu)001:3872: ye shes lnga dbang rdzogs pas brgyan //
NK066(chu)001:3874: mdor na lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po re
NK066(chu)001:3875: re la'ang lhag pa'i lha dgu dang rtsa lha gang
NK066(chu)001:3876: yin nyid dang bcu bcu ste /
NK066(chu)001:3877: thams cad kyang snang la rang bzhin med pa me
NK066(chu)001:3878: long nang gi gzugs brnyan lta bur shes par bya
NK066(chu)001:3879: ba'o // gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK066(chu)001:3880: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang zhing mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:3891: rig pa'i me tog dor ba /
NK066(chu)001:3895: stong pa shin tu'i tshig dang e h+ye hi'i sngags brjod cing /
NK066(chu)001:3896: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka'i h+aum gi 'od zer gyis
NK066(chu)001:3897: bskul bas rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i pho brang
NK066(chu)001:3898: na bzhugs pa'i phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs
NK066(chu)001:3899: pa thams cad kyis dgongs te /
NK066(chu)001:3900: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bzhin du gzugs kyi
NK066(chu)001:3901: sku bsgoms pa dang 'dra ba'i rnam par ngang gis
NK066(chu)001:3902: bzhengs nas 'byon ma rag bsgom pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:3904: slob dpon bi shwa mi tras /
NK066(chu)001:3905: mnyes dka' ma yin ba kur gnas phyir //
NK066(chu)001:3906: 'jig rten dbang po'i chos lugs kyis //
NK066(chu)001:3907: zhes pas ji ltar 'jig rten na rgyal po spyan
NK066(chu)001:3908: drangs pa'i thog mar snyan gsan 'bebs dgos pa dang
NK066(chu)001:3910: de ltar ma byas na rgyal po la brnyas pas ko long gi rgyur 'gyur mod kyi /
NK066(chu)001:3912: dam tshig pas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bkur gnas
NK066(chu)001:3913: su bya ba'i ched du sri zhu gus pa'i sgo
NK066(chu)001:3916: thugs rje'i lcags kyu'i tshig brjod cing dzahh+aum bam hoh'i sngags rgya dang /
NK066(chu)001:3917: dam tshig pa'i thugs ka nas phyag rgya'i lha mo spros te /
NK066(chu)001:3918: lcags kyu mas thugs dam bskul /
NK066(chu)001:3919: zhags pa mas gnas nas spyan drangs //
NK066(chu)001:3920: lcags sgrog ma gnas nas bskyod /
NK066(chu)001:3921: dril bu mas dgyes pa bskyed de //
NK066(chu)001:3922: mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs nas //
NK066(chu)001:3923: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor dang me ri 'dab 'byor
NK066(chu)001:3924: tsam du steng gi nam mkha' la bzhugs par bsgom
NK066(chu)001:3926: bdag nyid chen po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK066(chu)001:3927: spyan 'dren gshegs gsol mi dmigs kyang //
NK066(chu)001:3928: rang bzhin grub pa'i dkyil 'khor lha'i //
NK066(chu)001:3929: sku dang ye shes thob bya'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:3930: sa m+aa dzahdang e his dgug /
NK066(chu)001:3934: zhes sogs kyis rig pa'i me tog dor bas /
NK066(chu)001:3935: rang bzhin mthar phyin gyi dkyil dang //
NK066(chu)001:3936: 'dir ltar bsgoms pa'i lhag pa ting dkyil gyi sku
NK066(chu)001:3937: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las rnams gnyis su med
NK066(chu)001:3939: de ni dam ye gnyis ka yang rig pa'i rang
NK066(chu)001:3940: snang yin pa'i phyir sems nyid kyi ngang du dbyer
NK066(chu)001:3941: med par rig pa la rig pa'i me tog ces
NK066(chu)001:3942: bya ba la / de tsam na phyi rgyud pa
NK066(chu)001:3943: ltar bzang ngan dang tha dad du 'dzin pa'i rtog
NK066(chu)001:3944: pa dor bas na dor zhes bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:3945: 'di la so so ma yin par rig pa 'dun pa'i phyag dang /
NK066(chu)001:3946: rang snang gi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i tshul zhes kyang grags so //
NK066(chu)001:3948: ye shes rgyal po zhes sogs kyi tshig dang /
NK066(chu)001:3950: zhes sogs kyi sngags kyis bskul bas /
NK066(chu)001:3951: ye shes kyi lha rnams bdag gi sgrib pa sbyong ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:3952: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol ba la phyogs par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:3953: 'dir dngos grub skul ba la tshig gis bskul ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:3954: sngags kyis bskul ba gnyis bldabs so zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:3955: rje sgro phug pa'i zhal nas /
NK066(chu)001:3956: dang po ni dngos grub tsam bskul ba'i don dang /
NK066(chu)001:3957: phyi ma ni gnad la phab ste bskul ba'i phyir mi zlos gsung /
NK066(chu)001:3959: spyir gsang sngags lung gi sgo bzhir bzhed de //
NK066(chu)001:3960: don rnams gsal 'debs brjod pa tshig gi sgo //
NK066(chu)001:3961: thugs dam gnad bskul gsang ba sngags kyi sgo //
NK066(chu)001:3962: dmigs pa rtse gcig ting 'dzin yid kyi sgo //
NK066(chu)001:3963: mtshon pa brdar btags phyag rgya gar gyi sgo //
NK066(chu)001:3965: kun la bzhi ka tshang ba yang yod /
NK066(chu)001:3966: gsum gnyis gang rung tshang ba'ang yod pas kun la thams cad tshang bar ma nges pas /
NK066(chu)001:3967: 'dir tshig sngags ting 'dzin gyis bskul ba yin gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:3969: dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa phyag rgya bzhis chu la chu bzhag pa ltar dbyer med bsres te /
NK066(chu)001:3970: rin chen seng ge'i gdan la zhes sogs kyis 'gro
NK066(chu)001:3971: don ma rdzogs kyi bar du brtan par bzhugs su
NK066(chu)001:3972: gsol ba'o // 'di dag ni zur lugs pa spyi'i bzhed pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:3973: bdag gi rje bla ma ni /
NK066(chu)001:3974: tshig gis bskul ba'i rjes kyi sngags tshan gsum pos
NK066(chu)001:3975: rim bzhin dam ye dbyer med du bsres nas brtan
NK066(chu)001:3976: pa dang dbang du byas la /
NK066(chu)001:3977: phyag rgya bzhis ni shin tu brtan cing gsal bar
NK066(chu)001:3978: byas pa nyid yin pas sa bcad bzhi pa dang
NK066(chu)001:3979: lnga pa gnyis khong gcig tu bsdus na legs gsungs
NK066(chu)001:3980: te / sngags don dang shin tu 'byor zhing //
NK066(chu)001:3981: tshig dang sngags kyis bskul ba'i zlos skyon yang sel bas mkhas pas basngagasa par 'os pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:3984: glu ye shes kyi bar du dbul bar bya ste 'og nas ston no //
NK066(chu)001:3986: rang gzhan gyi rgyud dag par bya ba'i phyir spros pa med pa'i zhes sogs so //
NK066(chu)001:3988: 'dod pa'i don nye bar 'grub pa la smon pa'i
NK066(chu)001:3989: sgo nas shes bya thams cad zhes sogs kyis gsol
NK066(chu)001:3991: lhag pa'i bsam pa rtse gcig pa'i sgo nas bde bar gshegs pa zhes sogs so //
NK066(chu)001:3993: 'dzab khang phye ste 'od zer spro bsdu'i dmigs gnad
NK066(chu)001:3994: kyi man ngag dang ldan pa'i sgo nas 'dzab bskul
NK066(chu)001:3996: rjes la bstod nas dkyil 'khor gnyis dbyer med du basre'o //
NK066(chu)001:3998: rnal 'byor dbang phyug nyams chag bshags //
NK066(chu)001:3999: las la don phyir phrin las bcol //
NK066(chu)001:4000: bsgrub pa'i 'dod don gsol ba gdab //
NK066(chu)001:4002: rnal 'byor bsgrub phyir bzlas pa bya //
NK066(chu)001:4004: gnyis pa rjes kyi rim pa la lnga las /
NK066(chu)001:4007: brtan ma bskyang ba rnams 'chad par 'gyur la /
NK066(chu)001:4008: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:4009: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal gdab ste /
NK066(chu)001:4010: gtang rag mchod bstod dang nongs pa bzod par gsol nas /
NK066(chu)001:4011: rtag mtha' bsal phyir dkyil 'khor mi dmigs pa'i dbyings su bsdu /
NK066(chu)001:4012: chad mtha' bsal phyir de'i ngang las lhar rdzogs tshul du ldang /
NK066(chu)001:4013: spyi bor ham bkod la de zhu ba'i rgya gram gyis go bgo /
NK066(chu)001:4014: h+aum t+r+aum gyis mdzub rtse la khro bo gnyis bskyed nas lus bsrung /
NK066(chu)001:4015: dbu rgyan dang cod pan bcings te shin tu brtan par byas la bsngo ba bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:4016: de ltar yang rin d+r+wa las /
NK066(chu)001:4017: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor kun //
NK066(chu)001:4018: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsdu //
NK066(chu)001:4019: h+aum h+aum zhes ni rab brjod pas //
NK066(chu)001:4020: chos kyi dbyings su thim par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:4021: de nas snying po dran tsam gyis //
NK066(chu)001:4022: phyag rgya chen po gsal gyur nas //
NK066(chu)001:4023: go bgo mtshams bcad lus bsrung ste //
NK066(chu)001:4026: rtag chad mtha' las grol bya'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:4027: dkyil 'khor rim bzhin snying la bsdu //
NK066(chu)001:4028: mi dmigs ngang las gtso bor bskyed //
NK066(chu)001:4029: bskyed pa'i rdzogs pa bstan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4030: bar chod rgyun las grol bya'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:4031: rgya gram go dang khro lus bsrung //
NK066(chu)001:4032: de nyid 'gro don nus ldan phyir //
NK066(chu)001:4033: dbang bskur dbu rgyan cod pan ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4035: lnga pa spyod lam rgyun ting ni /
NK066(chu)001:4037: de nas rnal 'byor chen po des //
NK066(chu)001:4039: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong zhing //
NK066(chu)001:4040: spyod lam kun tu ma nyams par //
NK066(chu)001:4041: bdag nyid chen po brtan par bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:4043: gnyis pa khro bo'i mngon rtogs kyi las bsdebs la /
NK066(chu)001:4044: sngon 'gro thun mong du song nas /
NK066(chu)001:4048: ting nge 'dzin gyi dgos ched dang /
NK066(chu)001:4052: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK066(chu)001:4053: gdug pa srid gsum 'dul ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:4054: nga rgyal chen po brtan pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:4056: zhes pas sngon byung rgyal ba nyid gdug pa can
NK066(chu)001:4057: gyi yul la thugs rjes khros te btul ba bzhin
NK066(chu)001:4058: du / da ltar rjes 'jug tu'ang snying rje chen
NK066(chu)001:4059: pos gdul bya gdug pa can rnams 'dul ba'i don
NK066(chu)001:4060: du sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrub par bya'o snyam
NK066(chu)001:4062: 'di ni thog mar sems bskyed pa'i cho ga yin no //
NK066(chu)001:4066: las kyi rim pa'i ting 'dzin no //
NK066(chu)001:4069: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK066(chu)001:4070: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK066(chu)001:4071: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK066(chu)001:4072: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK066(chu)001:4075: e ma'o kun tu bzang mo ni //
NK066(chu)001:4076: bde chen spros bral thig le las //
NK066(chu)001:4077: stong pa nyid du rab gsal ba'i //
NK066(chu)001:4078: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom par bya //
NK066(chu)001:4082: nges pa las ni rdo rje che //
NK066(chu)001:4083: de las dpa' chen he ru ka /
NK066(chu)001:4084: 'bar ba chen po gar dgu yis //
NK066(chu)001:4085: 'jigs pa yi ni dus ltar drag /
NK066(chu)001:4086: ces rig pa h+aum mthing gsal brtan gyi tshad brgyad ldan pas 'phro 'du'i sbyor bas /
NK066(chu)001:4087: rdo rje rtse dgu pa mthing ga /
NK066(chu)001:4088: de 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu ba las rgyu'i he
NK066(chu)001:4089: ru ka tshon gang ba rdo rje dang thod khrag
NK066(chu)001:4091: 'di'i sku mdog la bzhed pa mi mthun te /
NK066(chu)001:4092: lha rje sgrol ma dang bla ma gra stag pa sogs sngon por mdzad /
NK066(chu)001:4093: rta ston gzi brjid smug nag tu bzhed cing //
NK066(chu)001:4094: rdo rje mthing ga ni thugs mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:4095: sku mdog smug nag ni cir yang 'gyur ba mtshon
NK066(chu)001:4096: pa yin pas de gnyis kyi kha dog 'gal bar
NK066(chu)001:4097: mi bsam mo zhes skyon spang yang mdzad de rang
NK066(chu)001:4098: gi rje bla ma'i dgongs pa'ang phyi ma'o //
NK066(chu)001:4104: gzhal yas khang dngos bskyed pa /
NK066(chu)001:4107: bdag rgyu'i he ru ka'i thugs ka'i h+aum las sa bon spros te /
NK066(chu)001:4108: 'phro 'du'i bya bas kro d+h+ai lnga'i mkha' dbyings kyi rang bzhin /
NK066(chu)001:4112: zhing chen gyi sa gzhi keng rus kyi ri rab kyis mtshan pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:4113: me dpung rnams bsgom pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4114: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas /
NK066(chu)001:4117: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa //
NK066(chu)001:4118: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrugs pa'i dkyil //
NK066(chu)001:4119: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi //
NK066(chu)001:4120: steng gi 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK066(chu)001:4123: me'i dbus su b+h+r+aum smug nag chad pa las 'phro 'du'i sgo nas gzhal yas khang bsgom pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4129: gru chad bzhis ni rnam par brgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4130: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4131: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i mtshon don dang /
NK066(chu)001:4132: de mtshon byed kyi mtshan mar gyur pa'i dbyibs phal cher zhi ba dang mtshungs shing /
NK066(chu)001:4133: kha dog gru chad ljang gu'i dbus su gser 'khor
NK066(chu)001:4134: rtsibs bzhi pa mu khyud dang lte ba mthing gar
NK066(chu)001:4135: gnas pa dang / khyad par du bden gnyis mtshan
NK066(chu)001:4136: pa'i 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes pa ni
NK066(chu)001:4137: gnas pa dang / dgos chos te / nang ma gser khyams dang /
NK066(chu)001:4139: glo 'bur dang sgo rnams phyogs mdog go //
NK066(chu)001:4142: phyi nang rgyu 'bras gdug pa dag /
NK066(chu)001:4143: 'dul phyir rta babs bzhir bshad do //
NK066(chu)001:4146: khyams phyi nang gnyis ka'i sgo bzhir rta babs brgyad kyis brgyan par bzhed kyang /
NK066(chu)001:4147: lung don ni der ma nges te /
NK066(chu)001:4148: phyi nang gi theg brgyad mtshon pa'i rgyu'i rta babs brgyad dang /
NK066(chu)001:4149: de'i yon tan rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu'i rta babs brgyad
NK066(chu)001:4150: brgyad sgo bzhi ka la ldan par bzhed pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:4151: ro // de bas na 'dir rang gi rje bla
NK066(chu)001:4152: ma'i dgongs pas nang sgo la rta babs mi byed
NK066(chu)001:4153: pa'i phyogs legs pa yin no //
NK066(chu)001:4156: gzhal yas khang phyi ma rin po che dang /
NK066(chu)001:4157: nang ma thod las grub par bzhed mod /
NK066(chu)001:4160: thod pa sna lnga sna gsum dang //
NK066(chu)001:4161: thod skam rtsig pa rim pa bzhin //
NK066(chu)001:4162: zhes phyi nang gnyis ka thod rtsigs su bzhed pas gnod do //
NK066(chu)001:4164: phyi ma thod rtsigs rim pa lnga dang /
NK066(chu)001:4165: nang ma skam rlon rnying gsum gyi brtsigs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4166: thod skam brtsigs pa zhes pa'i lung don ni /
NK066(chu)001:4167: rta ston gzi brjid bzhed pa ltar gru chad kyi rtsig pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4169: gru chad khyams las stegs bu gru bzhi pa'i rnam par thod rtsigs kyis 'phags pa yin gyi /
NK066(chu)001:4170: thog la thug pa'i brtsig par mi bsam ste /
NK066(chu)001:4171: de ltar na sgo sum sbrag tu 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:4176: rak+tasa spyin thabs su sbyar ba /
NK066(chu)001:4177: gnam lcags ngur mo'i gzer btab pa /
NK066(chu)001:4178: logs la tsit+ta'i pho long 'phyang ba /
NK066(chu)001:4180: lha chen brgyad kyi ka ba /
NK066(chu)001:4187: chu srin gyi thod pa'i rta babs la sogs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4189: tshangs dang lha dbang la brten pa //
NK066(chu)001:4190: mchog chen brgyad ka yin par 'dod //
NK066(chu)001:4191: lhag ma rnams ni thog phub ste //
NK066(chu)001:4192: gza' brgyad nyi zla'i glo skar ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4196: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi mas brjid //
NK066(chu)001:4198: rtsig steng thod pa sna tshogs kyi pha gu la
NK066(chu)001:4199: sbrul chen gyi zhags pas mgul nas drangs pa'i d+r+wa
NK066(chu)001:4200: ba 'phyang ba / mun par sbrul dang thod phreng
NK066(chu)001:4201: gi do shal dang do shal phyed pa dang de
NK066(chu)001:4202: dag gi bar nas nyi ma'i 'od zer 'phro bas
NK066(chu)001:4203: ba 'phyang ba / brjid cing / phyi'i 'gram stegs
NK066(chu)001:4204: la nang gi 'dod yon thogs bas bskor ba ste
NK066(chu)001:4205: ba 'phyang ba / brjid cing / / de las /
NK066(chu)001:4206: sbrul dang thod pa'i phreng ba nyid //
NK066(chu)001:4207: d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed rnam par spras //
NK066(chu)001:4209: khro bo sha lnga bdud rtsi dang //
NK066(chu)001:4212: steng rgyan ni pu shu dang rta babs kyi rtse'i phyogs kun tu zhing 'phan dang /
NK066(chu)001:4213: dbus 'phyur bu'i rtser lha chen po'i thod pa sbub pa'i steng na tsit+ta'i tog dang ldan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4214: de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK066(chu)001:4215: zhing 'phan phyogs mtshams brgyad dang ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4216: lha chen thod pa sbub steng na //
NK066(chu)001:4219: sgo bzhir rus sbal gyi ma them /
NK066(chu)001:4222: zhing gi sgo glegs sogs kyis brgyan cing /
NK066(chu)001:4223: zhing smug po'i ka bas btegs pa'i sgo khang gi steng na /
NK066(chu)001:4228: nyi zla'i phreng bas brgyan pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4230: sor phreng thod pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:4231: dbang po nyi zla'i phreng bas spras //
NK066(chu)001:4233: rta babs kyi rtser chos kyi 'khor lo'i g.yas g.yon na chu srin phru gu dang /
NK066(chu)001:4234: steng na zhing gi gdugs phub pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4237: skyes bu gsal shing phyogs mtshams brgyad //
NK066(chu)001:4240: srung 'khor gyi nang gi khor yug la dur khrod brgyad dang /
NK066(chu)001:4241: phyi nang thams cad du rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i
NK066(chu)001:4242: rnam pa can gyi me ri me dpung 'bar ba'i
NK066(chu)001:4243: klong nas sprul pa'i khro chung grangs med pa 'phro
NK066(chu)001:4245: khro bo rnams la dur khrod ni //
NK066(chu)001:4246: 'khor ba ma spangs gnas dag rtags //
NK066(chu)001:4252: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK066(chu)001:4254: de'ang yon tan gyi che bas rang snang ba'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:4255: lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir pad+ma zla nyi sum brtsegs
NK066(chu)001:4256: so // de'i steng na dregs pa can zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir dbus su ru dra /
NK066(chu)001:4260: byang du gnod sbyin pho mo'o //
NK066(chu)001:4261: de dag las nan tur du bstan pa'i phyir pho kha bub kyi sog phrag dang /
NK066(chu)001:4262: mo gan rkyal gyi nu phrag nas dug lnga gnas
NK066(chu)001:4263: su dag pa'i brdar dud 'gro gdug pa can rnams
NK066(chu)001:4264: kyi sbar bas bzung ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:4275: ste spar khab kyi lugs so //
NK066(chu)001:4276: 'grel pa nyi seng mar khyu mchog ni lha chen gyi zhon pa ste dbus /
NK066(chu)001:4277: ma he gshin rje'i zhon pa ste lho /
NK066(chu)001:4280: dom gnod sbyin gyi ste byang du 'god par bshad /
NK066(chu)001:4282: khyus 'gro zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir khyu mchog ni thugs kyi phyag rgya /
NK066(chu)001:4283: ma he gzi brjid che bas sku'i /
NK066(chu)001:4284: gzig gdug pa che bas mi gtong ba'i yon tan gyi /
NK066(chu)001:4285: stag dpa' brtul che bas thugs rje chen po'i mtshan nyid kyang mi mdzad pad+ma'i /
NK066(chu)001:4286: dom gtum pa'i phyir las rigs kyi phyag rgya'o gsungs pa las /
NK066(chu)001:4287: 'dir ni bla ma brgyud pa'i bka' srol gyis lugs deng po'i rjes su 'brang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:4288: yang khyu mchog gi ngos 'dzin la /
NK066(chu)001:4290: pin tar+thara bshad pa'i phyir seng ge'o zer /
NK066(chu)001:4291: gdan mchog gdul dka' mi 'jigs khyu mchog dang /
NK066(chu)001:4293: nyi khri las glang por bshad zer /
NK066(chu)001:4294: khyu mchog glang po che'i gnas su dam bca' /
NK066(chu)001:4296: nyang t+aika pa de gnyis rol pa las byung bar bzhed kyang /
NK066(chu)001:4298: glang khyu par bshad cing 'dul ba lung las kyang //
NK066(chu)001:4299: ba glang gi phru gu seng ge mo'i 'o mas gsos pa las byung ba'i rigs su bshad do //
NK066(chu)001:4302: lha chen po rnams kyi zhon pa phrogs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4303: zhes rgyas byed dpa' rtags kyi rtags su bshad cing /
NK066(chu)001:4305: gus pas rang gi gdan steng du phyung ste phul bar bshad /
NK066(chu)001:4306: don la smon lam gus pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:4307: thugs rje mthun 'jug gi gdan gnyis kar mi 'gal lo gsungs /
NK066(chu)001:4309: khro mo nyi shu'i gnas su ro dang nyi gdan /
NK066(chu)001:4310: dbang mo nyer brgyad la zhing skam gyi gdan re re'o //
NK066(chu)001:4311: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la /
NK066(chu)001:4312: ji ltar bskyed pa'i cho ga dang //
NK066(chu)001:4313: bskyed pa lha'i mtshan nyid gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:4315: khang pa grub nas bdag po bskyed pa pha drin can gyi tshul dang /
NK066(chu)001:4316: bdag po grub nas khang pa brtsigs pa sgo drag po'i tshul lo //
NK066(chu)001:4318: ting 'dzin gsum gyi rgyu ting h+aum gi khyad par las /
NK066(chu)001:4319: 'og gzhi dang gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i nang du
NK066(chu)001:4320: gtso bo cho ga gsum gyis badz+ra he ru kar
NK066(chu)001:4321: bskyed nas sras gnyis bskyed pa'i bya ba la 'jug
NK066(chu)001:4322: ste / 'grel pa spar khab kyi rjes su 'brangs nas rog pa sogs bzhed do //
NK066(chu)001:4324: sngar bshad pa ltar rang lugs te /
NK066(chu)001:4325: dam pa rgyan gyi rjes su 'brangs nas bla ma gong ma phal che ba'i dgongs bzhed do //
NK066(chu)001:4327: cho ga gsum gyis rgyu'i he ru kar bskyed pa'i rjes su /
NK066(chu)001:4328: 'og gzhi gzhal yas khang dang bcas pa bsgom zhing /
NK066(chu)001:4329: de nas bdag sras gzhan sras kyi cho ga la 'jug go //
NK066(chu)001:4333: rgyu'i he ru ka nyid dpal chen po yab yum
NK066(chu)001:4334: du bskyed nas snyoms par 'jug pa'i bya ba dang
NK066(chu)001:4335: / ngo mtshar sras kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4338: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK066(chu)001:4339: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK066(chu)001:4340: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:4343: de'i phyir rgyu'i he ru ka gdan thog tu babs
NK066(chu)001:4344: te dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka sku
NK066(chu)001:4345: smug nag cir yang 'gyur ba dbu phyag zhabs che
NK066(chu)001:4348: de'i rdul snyed dang mnyam pa mtshon cha sna tshogs 'dzin par bskyed la /
NK066(chu)001:4349: de'i thugs nas yum dbyings phyug ma phyung ste sbyor ba mdzad pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4351: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas ni //
NK066(chu)001:4352: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyung ste //
NK066(chu)001:4353: hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyi //
NK066(chu)001:4354: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mdzad de //
NK066(chu)001:4355: gnyis med 'khril bas dgyes par thim //
NK066(chu)001:4361: mkha' gsang byin rlabs dang sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba sogs mdzad /
NK066(chu)001:4362: de las mkhas pa dag na re /
NK066(chu)001:4365: rtsa ba las ma gsungs shing rgyud dang yang mi mthun no //
NK066(chu)001:4366: des na snar ston gyi bzhed pa ltar rgyu'i he
NK066(chu)001:4367: ru ka des tshig brjod pa tsam gyis rang bzhin
NK066(chu)001:4369: kho bo yang 'di legs par mngon no //
NK066(chu)001:4371: sngags kyis sprul pa spro ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:4372: de rigs lngar bsdu ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:4373: sras mo nyi shu bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4375: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa sogs brjod pa'i rkyen gyis
NK066(chu)001:4376: sbyor mtshams nas khro bo 'chol pa spros te gdug
NK066(chu)001:4377: pa can rnams btul bar bsgom pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4379: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka sogs brjod pas /
NK066(chu)001:4380: khroo bo de dag las chos dbyings ye shes las
NK066(chu)001:4381: 'phros pa'i khro bo thams cad 'dus nas gzhi'i he
NK066(chu)001:4382: ru ka la thim pas de nyid badz+ra he ru
NK066(chu)001:4383: ka yab yum du gyur pa ni 'bras bu'i he
NK066(chu)001:4384: ru ka'o // de bzhin du so so'i sngags brjod
NK066(chu)001:4385: pa'i rkyen gyis ye shes gzhan bzhi las 'phros pa'i
NK066(chu)001:4386: khro bo thams cad so sor 'dus pa las rigs
NK066(chu)001:4387: bzhi he ru kar gyur nas phyogs kyi 'khor lo'i
NK066(chu)001:4390: de nas rigs lnga'i khrag 'thung sbyor bas mdzad pa'i dgyes sgra las rim bzhin ha brgyad dang /
NK066(chu)001:4392: phata bzhi brjod pa'i rkyen gyis bskul nas /
NK066(chu)001:4393: rgyu byang chub kyi sems sprin las sbyor mtshams nas
NK066(chu)001:4394: gnas yul sgo ma nyi shu po rnams re re
NK066(chu)001:4395: yang lnga lngar ton pa rang rang gi rigs re
NK066(chu)001:4396: rer bsdus nas so so'i gnas su dgod pa ni
NK066(chu)001:4397: bdag sras so // 'dir rog gi mngon rtogs las /
NK066(chu)001:4398: sbyor mtshams nas byang sems kyi zeg ma las ha
NK066(chu)001:4399: he phata du gyur pa so so'i gdan khar bkod
NK066(chu)001:4400: nas / badz+ra goo r+ai ha sogs bskyed sngags kyis sku bskyed par mdzad na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:4401: rgyud dang dam pa rgyan gnyis ka nas gsungs pa ma mthong ngo //
NK066(chu)001:4402: yang ston pa bla skyabs na re /
NK066(chu)001:4403: rigs lnga ni mkha' nang nas byung ba'i phyir sprul pa bsdus pa'i sras yin la /
NK066(chu)001:4404: de las khro mo rnams bskyed pas bdag sras su mi 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:4405: tsha mor 'gro ba'i skyon yod pas gtso bo kho na las gdon par rigs so zer //
NK066(chu)001:4406: de'i lan du rta ston gyi zhal nas /
NK066(chu)001:4407: rigs lnga las byung yang ngo bo dbus kyi gtso
NK066(chu)001:4408: bo rgyu'i he ru ka dang gnyis su med pa
NK066(chu)001:4409: de nyid las byung ba'i phyir skyon med ces gsungs
NK066(chu)001:4410: so // gnyis pa gzhan sras ni bdag gtso bo'i thugs nas shar du thon te //
NK066(chu)001:4411: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK066(chu)001:4412: zhes sogs kyis gsol ba gdab pa sogs nas lha
NK066(chu)001:4413: tshogs thams cad 'od du zhu ste 'od phung gcig
NK066(chu)001:4414: tu gyur pa'i bar sngar ltar te bdag don chos
NK066(chu)001:4415: sku'i ting 'dzin gyis snang ba'i zhen pa sbyang ba'o
NK066(chu)001:4416: // de nas gzhan don gzugs sku'i ting 'dzin gyis stong par 'dzin pa'i zhen pa sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:4418: zhes dran pa tsam gyis gdan steng gi 'od phung
NK066(chu)001:4419: de h+aum yig zung du gyur pa las cho ga
NK066(chu)001:4420: gsum gyis badz+ra he ru ka yab yum du bskyed
NK066(chu)001:4421: nas / dam pa rgyan las gsungs pa'i go rim
NK066(chu)001:4422: ltar skabs 'dir dbang bskur dang byin rlobs bya ba'am
NK066(chu)001:4423: nas / / zhi ba ltar 'og tu bya ba'ang rung ste /
NK066(chu)001:4425: de nas mkha' gsang rlob pa sogs sngar ltar byas te /
NK066(chu)001:4426: yab yum gyi mkha' las khrag 'thung sum cu tham
NK066(chu)001:4427: pa so so'i sngags kyis bskyed pa phata dzahs phyir
NK066(chu)001:4428: bton nas / badz+ra he ru ka rang la bstim /
NK066(chu)001:4430: dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad ni /
NK066(chu)001:4431: sbyor ba'i byi mo yin gyi /
NK066(chu)001:4432: sras ma yin pa'i phyir sbyor mtshams nas mi gdon no //
NK066(chu)001:4433: 'o na ji ltar bskyed ce na /
NK066(chu)001:4435: b+h+yo nyer brgyad brjod pas phyi khyams la krong bskyed du mdzad /
NK066(chu)001:4439: rdo rje me long nas 'byung ba'i bskyed sngags kyis krong bskyed byed gsung /
NK066(chu)001:4443: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas b+h+yo nyer brgyad rang rang
NK066(chu)001:4444: gi gnas su spros te bskyed sngags kyis lhar bsgom
NK066(chu)001:4445: par bzhed do // gnyis pa la /
NK066(chu)001:4455: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang /
NK066(chu)001:4456: dmar nag ljang nag ces pas bstan te /
NK066(chu)001:4461: karma he ru ka lnga'i sku mdog rtsa zhal dang bcas pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4462: lho ma gtogs pa'i khro bo gzhan bzhi'i g.yas zhal dkar po dang /
NK066(chu)001:4464: dbus dang lho byang gi g.yon zhal dmar po /
NK066(chu)001:4465: shar nub gnyis kyi g.yon ser po sgyu 'phrul ser po sgyu 'phrul brgyad pa las gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:4466: de'ang dug lnga gnas su dag cing las bzhi lhun
NK066(chu)001:4467: grub kyi mdzad pa mtshon pa'i brdar rigs so so'i
NK066(chu)001:4468: kha dog dang / de dag kyang rigs mi 'gyur
NK066(chu)001:4469: zhing las bzhi'i gzhi dang mthar phyin pa ni drag
NK066(chu)001:4470: po kho nas mdzad pa'i phyir thams cad la nag
NK066(chu)001:4473: gdul bya gdug pa can 'dul ba'i phyir lnga ka'ang shin tu 'jigs pa'i sku ste /
NK066(chu)001:4474: rnam thar gsum dang ye shes drug mtshon pa'i dbu gsum phyag drug pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:4475: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi dang bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i zhabs bzhi dor stabs su bgrad pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4477: dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa chen po khyo shug gi gdan la brkyang bskum du bzhugs so //
NK066(chu)001:4479: 'di'i rgya dper brkyang bskum gyi skad dod la /
NK066(chu)001:4481: zhes yod pas zhabs g.yas brkyang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:4483: rngam pa'i sgra chen sogs kyis gsung gnyis las ma byung yang /
NK066(chu)001:4484: don la sku gsung thugs kyi nyams gsum gsum ste gar dgu dang ldan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4487: sgeg pa dpa' ba mi sdug pa //
NK066(chu)001:4488: rgod dang drag shul 'jigs su rung //
NK066(chu)001:4489: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:4490: gar dgu'i nyams dang ldan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4493: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK066(chu)001:4494: sbrul dang thod phreng nyi zla'i chas //
NK066(chu)001:4495: zhes pa'i skabs su rgyan la /
NK066(chu)001:4500: rgyal byed dpa' rtags kyi rgyan te /
NK066(chu)001:4501: de la'ang bgo ba'i gos gsum /
NK066(chu)001:4503: byug pa'i rdzas gsum ste brgyad las /
NK066(chu)001:4505: zhing glang gi stod g.yogs dang /
NK066(chu)001:4508: zhing chen g.yang gzhi byang chub sems kyi rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4509: glang chen ko rlon stobs chen mchog gi rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4510: stag gi sham thabs dpa' brtul za byed rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4512: gdags pa'i rgyan la sbrul dang /
NK066(chu)001:4523: se mo do dang mgur chu /
NK066(chu)001:4528: sbrul nag chun po mnyen lcug 'khril ba'i rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4535: thod pa tshar gsum sku gsum brnyes pa'i rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4538: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu //
NK066(chu)001:4539: smin mtshams su rak+ta'i thig le //
NK066(chu)001:4540: os ko la zhag gi zo ris te /
NK066(chu)001:4542: rak+ta thugs rje chags pa'i rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4543: thal ba 'dul byed phrin las rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4544: zhag chen don dam bcud kyi rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4547: dpal chen po'i sku la ye nas rang chas su gnas pa'i phyir dpal gyi chas te /
NK066(chu)001:4548: dbu skra gyen bardzesa 'khor ba ru bzlog chas //
NK066(chu)001:4549: rdo rje'i khyung gshog thabs dang shes rab chas //
NK066(chu)001:4550: mthing dmar cod pan rtag chad zil gnon chas //
NK066(chu)001:4551: spyi gtsug rdo rje lhag pa rig pa'i chas //
NK066(chu)001:4552: dbang gi bse khrab gzi 'bar bgrod pa'i chas //
NK066(chu)001:4553: gnyis med sbyor ba shes rab yum gyi chas //
NK066(chu)001:4554: gnod gdug zlog byed dpa' bo ljags kyi chas //
NK066(chu)001:4555: nyon mongs sreg byed rdo rje me yi chas //
NK066(chu)001:4558: byang sems brtan pa nyid kyi snyan gong g.yas g.yon nyi zlas brgyan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4560: nyi zla'i phreng ba se ral khar byas par bzhed do //
NK066(chu)001:4562: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug bcas //
NK066(chu)001:4565: rdo rje khro bo khrag 'thung mthing //
NK066(chu)001:4567: dkar dmar zhal du nyon mongs 'dren //
NK066(chu)001:4568: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra dang //
NK066(chu)001:4570: shes rab 'khyud pas chags pa ston //
NK066(chu)001:4572: dkar ser smug nag gti mug 'dren //
NK066(chu)001:4573: 'khor lo rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK066(chu)001:4574: dril bu dung dmar tri sh+aul 'chang //
NK066(chu)001:4576: sngo dmar ser nag nga rgyal gsol //
NK066(chu)001:4577: rin chen rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK066(chu)001:4578: dril bu dung dmar dgra s+t+wa rol //
NK066(chu)001:4580: dkar ser dmar nag brjid pa las //
NK066(chu)001:4581: pad+ma rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK066(chu)001:4582: dril bu dung dmar rnge'u chung 'chang //
NK066(chu)001:4583: las rab khrag 'thung yum dang rol //
NK066(chu)001:4584: dkar dmar ljang nag 'bar ba la //
NK066(chu)001:4585: rgya gram rdo rje ti ra dang //
NK066(chu)001:4586: dril bu dung dmar thong gshol rol //
NK066(chu)001:4587: zhes pa ni gar mchod dang mthun zhing bka' mchims phu ba'i phyag bzhes so //
NK066(chu)001:4588: gzhan du sgyu 'phrul rdo rje dang bla ma la
NK066(chu)001:4589: sogs par sku mdog dang phyag mtshan 'di dang cung
NK066(chu)001:4590: zad mi mthun par byung na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:4591: thugs rje dang mdzad pa la phyogs ris med par gdul bya ji ltar mos pa ltar snang ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:4592: 'o na gcig tu ma nges pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:4593: gang zag gis nyams su blang mi btub pa'i skyon du 'gyur ro zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:4595: rgyud gzhung re re'i dbang du nges pa can du gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:4596: de ltar nyams su len zhes gong ma rnams gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:4600: thams cad kyang sku mdog yab dang mthun zhing gzig sham can /
NK066(chu)001:4601: g.yas shes rab kyi rtags dril bus yab la 'khyud cing /
NK066(chu)001:4602: g.yon dung khrag zhal du stob pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4603: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la brten //
NK066(chu)001:4604: g.yon du dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK066(chu)001:4606: gnyis pa 'khor gyi bkod pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:4607: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK066(chu)001:4608: zhes pa'i skabs gnas yul gyi ma mo brgyad brgyad las /
NK066(chu)001:4609: gnas zhes pa ni dur khrod kyi gnas brgyad las btags pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4610: de la phyi nang gsang gsum las /
NK066(chu)001:4612: bsil ba'i tshal la sogs pa brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:4614: yul gyi ming ni rgya gar ma ga d+ha'o //
NK066(chu)001:4616: dur khrod chen po bsil ba tshal //
NK066(chu)001:4618: yul gyi ming ni sing+g+ha'i yul //
NK066(chu)001:4620: dur khrod chen po sku la rdzogs //
NK066(chu)001:4622: yul gyi ming ni kha che'i yul //
NK066(chu)001:4624: dur khrod chen po he chen rol //
NK066(chu)001:4626: yul gyi ming ni tho gar yul //
NK066(chu)001:4628: dur khrod chen po gsang chen rol //
NK066(chu)001:4630: yul gyi ming ni o rgyan yul //
NK066(chu)001:4632: dur khrod chen po pad+ma brtsegs /
NK066(chu)001:4634: yul gyi ming ni bal po'i yul /
NK066(chu)001:4636: dur khrod chen po ya ma kha //
NK066(chu)001:4638: yul gyi ming ni za hor yul //
NK066(chu)001:4640: dur khrod chen po khyu byug klong //
NK066(chu)001:4642: yul gyi ming ni li yi yul //
NK066(chu)001:4644: dur khrod chen po mngon rdzogs yin //
NK066(chu)001:4647: nang gi dur khrod brgyad ni /
NK066(chu)001:4649: snying khog pa dang bcas pa /
NK066(chu)001:4663: gong gi dur khrod brgyad dang 'brel ba'i ma ga d+ha la sogs pa'i yul brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:4664: yang na rnam shes tshogs brgyad kyi yul brgyad de /
NK066(chu)001:4665: kun gzhi la yul don sems /
NK066(chu)001:4667: yid yul 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi chos /
NK066(chu)001:4669: nyon yid kyi yul kun gzhi /
NK066(chu)001:4682: de ltar na yul dang rnam shes ma spangs gnas su dag pa las /
NK066(chu)001:4683: goo r+ai dang phra men ma ste /
NK066(chu)001:4687: nang khyams kyi phyogs bzhir mche ba can bzhi dang /
NK066(chu)001:4688: mtshams bzhir gshog pa can bzhi bzhugs so //
NK066(chu)001:4689: de dag gi sku mdog dang phyag mtshan ni /
NK066(chu)001:4690: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK066(chu)001:4692: sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK066(chu)001:4694: sgo bzhi phyag rgya zhes sogs ni /
NK066(chu)001:4695: rtag chad bdag mtshan te phyin ci log gi sgo
NK066(chu)001:4696: bzhi la ye shes kyi phyag rgyas 'debs par byed
NK066(chu)001:4697: pa'i lcags kyu ma la sogs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4698: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK066(chu)001:4700: slas dang byi mo sogs kyis dbang phyug ma ni /
NK066(chu)001:4701: grangs nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang /
NK066(chu)001:4702: gdan zhing skam re re dang /
NK066(chu)001:4703: sku mdog dang lag cha ni //
NK066(chu)001:4704: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK066(chu)001:4706: 'dir sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa las /
NK066(chu)001:4707: phyi yi mkha' 'gro rang rgyud ma //
NK066(chu)001:4708: nang gi mkha' 'gro khro mor ston //
NK066(chu)001:4709: gsang ba'i sprul pa mgo brnyan ma //
NK066(chu)001:4710: bka' rtags rdo rje rang rtags 'chang //
NK066(chu)001:4712: gal te gang du dbang dang byin rlabs ma byas na /
NK066(chu)001:4713: skabs 'dir zhi ba ltar ye shes sems dpa' bskyed nas dbang bskur byin gyis rlob cing /
NK066(chu)001:4714: rigs bdag ni rigs lnga yab la yab lnga dang /
NK066(chu)001:4716: khro mo nyi shu la ye shes lnga dang /
NK066(chu)001:4717: ldan pa'i rtags su gser gyi rdo rje rtse lnga pa re re dang /
NK066(chu)001:4718: dbang mo rnams la drag po'i las mdzad pa'i rtags
NK066(chu)001:4719: su lcags kyi rdo rje rtse gsum pa re res
NK066(chu)001:4721: yan lag gi lha 'di dag kyang //
NK066(chu)001:4722: gong ma phal cher khro bo kho na bskyed par mdzad //
NK066(chu)001:4724: rtsa lha khro bo yin pas ye shes sems dpa'
NK066(chu)001:4725: sogs yan lag gi lha rnams zhi ba bsgoms kyang
NK066(chu)001:4727: 'di ltar zhi ba la khro bo'i rgyan rnams gang du'ang mi tshud la /
NK066(chu)001:4728: khro bo la zhi ba'i rgyan rnams ma bkag pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:4729: zhi khro gnyis gang mos su bskyed pas chog cing /
NK066(chu)001:4730: zhi ba ltar na rin po che'i dbu rgyan /
NK066(chu)001:4731: khro bo la thod pa'i dbu rgyan gyi khang bu la brten par bsgom mo gsungs /
NK066(chu)001:4732: rje bla ma thams cad mkhyen pas mdzad pa'i dong sprugs dkyil chog tu'ang /
NK066(chu)001:4733: ye shes sems dpa' ma gtogs pa'i yan lag gi
NK066(chu)001:4734: lha gzhan brgyad po zhi khro thun mong du zhi
NK066(chu)001:4735: bas mdzad do // gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting 'dzin ni /
NK066(chu)001:4738: rig pa'i me tog dor ba /
NK066(chu)001:4739: dngos grub bskul te bstim pa /
NK066(chu)001:4749: dkyil 'khor bsdu ba rnams te las gzhung las shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:4750: spyir dkyil 'khor spros pa'i skabs 'dir zhi khro gnyis ka la rgyas bsdus gsum las /
NK066(chu)001:4751: zhi ba zhe gnyis ni 'bring po dang /
NK066(chu)001:4752: khro bo nga brgyad ni bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK066(chu)001:4753: gzhan du zhi ba rgyas pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:4754: sngar bris pa dang mthun par lte ba'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dbus dang lngar /
NK066(chu)001:4755: mi bskyod pa yab yum la rang gi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK066(chu)001:4756: de bzhin du shar rtsibs kyi 'khor lo la rnam snang gis gtso bo byas pa bcu /
NK066(chu)001:4757: lho rtsibs kyi 'khor lo la rin 'byung gis gtso bo byas pa bcu /
NK066(chu)001:4758: nub rtsibs kyi 'khor lo la mtha' yas kyis gtso bo byas pa bcu /
NK066(chu)001:4759: byang rtsibs kyi 'khor lo la don grub kyis gtso bo byas pa bcu ste /
NK066(chu)001:4761: 'khor lo dbus lngar rgyal po yum //
NK066(chu)001:4762: mdun rgyab g.yas g.yon phyogs bzhi ru //
NK066(chu)001:4763: sems dpa' sems ma rim bzhin bsam //
NK066(chu)001:4765: de ltar lnga bcu'i steng du sems dpa' sems ma bcu drug /
NK066(chu)001:4768: thub drug ste brgyad cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK066(chu)001:4769: de'ang rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum bzhi bcu'i mtshan gyi sdom ni /
NK066(chu)001:4770: dbus kyi rigs chung sems dpa' rdo rje dang //
NK066(chu)001:4771: de bzhin rin chen chos dang las bzhi'i yum //
NK066(chu)001:4772: rim bzhin brtan 'bar sdud bskyod bzhi po sbyar //
NK066(chu)001:4773: sems dpa' rgyal po chags pa legs bzhi sbyar //
NK066(chu)001:4774: yum ni sgeg mo bdug pa lcags kyu sgron //
NK066(chu)001:4775: rin chen nyi ma rgyal mtshan bzhad bzhi lho //
NK066(chu)001:4776: yum ni m+aa le me tog zhags bde ma //
NK066(chu)001:4777: chos dang rnon po 'khor lo smra ba nub //
NK066(chu)001:4778: yum ni glu sgron lcags sgrog gsal bkra ma //
NK066(chu)001:4779: las dang bsrung ba gnod sbyin khu tshur byang //
NK066(chu)001:4780: gar byug dril 'khrol 'bebs ma yum bzhi ste //
NK066(chu)001:4781: dang gcig ma gtogs yab yum thams cad kyi //
NK066(chu)001:4782: mtshan gyi thog mar rdo rje re re sbyar //
NK066(chu)001:4785: rigs lnga yab yum bcu dang /
NK066(chu)001:4786: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de lha tshogs bco brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:4788: khrag 'thung lnga bcu nga brgyad kyi steng du khro
NK066(chu)001:4789: bcu yab yum bsnan pas lha bdun cu rtsa brgyad
NK066(chu)001:4791: rigs lnga'i khrag 'thung yab yum zung re la rigs
NK066(chu)001:4792: chung gi khrag 'thung yab yum brgyad brgyad kyis bskor
NK066(chu)001:4794: 'bring po'i skabs kyi 'khor drug cu re brgyad po bsnan pas brgyad dang bco brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:4797: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4798: zhes sogs kyi skabs su rnam grangs spros pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4799: snang ba rnam 'byed kyi ting nge 'dzin la bslab pa'i thabs bstan no //
NK066(chu)001:4802: nyi khri bzhi stong gi dang /
NK066(chu)001:4803: bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor la bslab pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4806: shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu /
NK066(chu)001:4807: sku gsung thugs kyi lha brgya dang nyi shu /
NK066(chu)001:4808: dbu rgyan gyi lha brgyad bargya'o //
NK066(chu)001:4810: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4811: zhes pas rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis la yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu bsgom pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4812: yab kyi rtog pa'i gnas su yab bcu bdun dang thub pa dang drug ste nyer gsum /
NK066(chu)001:4813: yum la yum bcu bdun dgod do //
NK066(chu)001:4815: bdag nyid mi bskyod par gsal btab pa'i dbu la rnam snang /
NK066(chu)001:4820: mig rna ba sna lce bzhi'i g.yas kyi rtsa nang du sa snying /
NK066(chu)001:4824: g.yon gyi rtsa'i phyi rol du rim par /
NK066(chu)001:4829: lag mthil g.yas su gshin rje /
NK066(chu)001:4838: gsang gnas su dmyal ba'i thub pa rnams dgod do //
NK066(chu)001:4839: de bzhin du yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma la
NK066(chu)001:4840: yum bcu bdun 'god pa'i rim pa yab dang mtshungs
NK066(chu)001:4841: so // de ltar yan lag gi lha bzhi bcu
NK066(chu)001:4842: po ni rags pa 'i cha nas thabs kyi lhar
NK066(chu)001:4843: so // bzhag go // gnyis pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:4844: thabs lha bzhi bcu po'i thugs kar rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa' re re bsgom pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:4845: yan lag spros pa ste phra ba'i cha nas shes rab kyi lhar bzhag go //
NK066(chu)001:4848: zhes pas rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la bkod pa'i
NK066(chu)001:4849: thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu po re re'i yang gnas
NK066(chu)001:4850: gsum du sku gsung thugs kyi lha re re 'god
NK066(chu)001:4851: pa ni / sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i lha brgya nyi shu'o //
NK066(chu)001:4855: de ltar brgya nyi shu po'i steng du thabs kyi
NK066(chu)001:4856: lha bzhi bcu bsnan te brgya drug cu po de
NK066(chu)001:4857: dag la so so'i rigs bdag gis gtso byas pa'i
NK066(chu)001:4858: dbu rgyan gyi lha lnga lnga ste brgyad bargya'o //
NK066(chu)001:4859: des na thabs shes byin rlobs dbu rgyan gyi lha
NK066(chu)001:4860: rnams kun dril bas rtsa lha yab yum gnyis la
NK066(chu)001:4861: yan lag dang lhag pa'i lha stong bsgom pa yin
NK066(chu)001:4862: no // 'dir snga rabs kyi mkhas pa 'ga' zhig /
NK066(chu)001:4867: shes rab kyi lha bzhi bcu /
NK066(chu)001:4868: sku gsung thugs kyi lha re re zhing bzhi bcu re ste nyis brgya ni grangs kyi gzhi ma'o //
NK066(chu)001:4869: nyis brgya po re re la dbu rgyan lnga lnga
NK066(chu)001:4870: bsnan pas lnga tshan nyis brgya la stong yod de
NK066(chu)001:4871: // dbu rgyan kho na'i grangs yin la //
NK066(chu)001:4872: de'i steng du gzhi'i lha nyis brgya bsnan pas rnam grangs byung tshogs su lha stong nyis bargya'o //
NK066(chu)001:4876: stangs dpyal gnyis kyi phyag rgya dang //
NK066(chu)001:4877: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor yang //
NK066(chu)001:4878: ri rab til 'bru'i tshul bzhin du //
NK066(chu)001:4879: dpe byad mtshan gyis spras pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4880: zhes rtsa ba'i lha la sangs rgyas stong bsgom par gsungs pa'i grangs 'jig pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:4881: gzhan yang thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu ni shes rab kyi lha yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:4882: rgyan spangs pa'i phyir dbu rgyan bcing ba'ang rigs pa ma yin no //
NK066(chu)001:4883: yang dkyil 'khor spros pa'i skabs su rin chen d+r+wa ba las /
NK066(chu)001:4884: dbang bskur byin rlabs tshul bzhin bya //
NK066(chu)001:4885: zhes pa'i go rim ltar mdzad mod kyi //
NK066(chu)001:4886: 'on kyang rnam grangs spros pa'i skabs 'dir /
NK066(chu)001:4888: byin rlabs rdo rje gsum du bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:4889: dbu yi gnas lngar ye shes lnga //
NK066(chu)001:4890: zhes gsungs pa ltar dbang gi gong du byin rlabs bya dgos te /
NK066(chu)001:4891: sku gsung thugs kyi lha brgya nyi shu la'ang dbu rgyan gyi lha bsgom dgos pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:4893: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gi //
NK066(chu)001:4895: gtso bo mi bskyod pa yab yum la ji ltar
NK066(chu)001:4896: bkod pa bzhin du lha gzhan rnams la'ang rigs 'gre
NK066(chu)001:4898: gang rtsa lhar song ba'i yab yum gyi rtog pa'i
NK066(chu)001:4899: gnas su kun bzang yab yum 'god pa tsam khyad
NK066(chu)001:4900: par ro // de ltar na rgyal ba rigs lnga
NK066(chu)001:4901: rgyal mchog kun bzang ste yab yum zung drug la
NK066(chu)001:4902: par ro // stong tsho drug / sems dpa' yab
NK066(chu)001:4903: yum bcu drug sgo ba yab yum brgyad de nyi
NK066(chu)001:4904: shu rtsa bzhi zung bcu gnyis yod pas stong tsho
NK066(chu)001:4905: par ro // stong tsho drug / bcu gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:4906: thub drug la yum med pa kha cig na re
NK066(chu)001:4907: par ro // stong tsho drug / bcu gnyis / / don gyi yum chos kyi dbyings la /
NK066(chu)001:4908: rtags kyi yum pad+ma yin pas gdan pad+ma la 'god zer na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:4909: 'dir bla ma rnams rje sgro phug pa sogs /
NK066(chu)001:4910: shes rab mtshon byed g.yon yin pas //
NK066(chu)001:4911: g.yon phyogs su 'god ces gsungs pa ltar /
NK066(chu)001:4912: rkang lag gi rigs bzhi dang /
NK066(chu)001:4913: sgo ba yab yum rnams g.yas g.yon gyi cha 'dzin pa'i rim pa'i rtsa'i mdun rgyab dang /
NK066(chu)001:4914: phyi nang gi sems dpa' rnams dbang rtsa'i phyi dang
NK066(chu)001:4915: nang du 'god tshul shes par byas nas thub drug
NK066(chu)001:4916: re re la'ang stong tshang bar bsgoms pas stong tsho
NK066(chu)001:4917: drug ste / mdor na stong tsho nyi shu rtsa
NK066(chu)001:4918: bzhi bsgom pa ni nyi khri bzhi stong gi dkyil
NK066(chu)001:4920: de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK066(chu)001:4921: de ltar gtso mchog ldan byas nas //
NK066(chu)001:4922: bya byed rigs bzhi'ang stong bsgom bya //
NK066(chu)001:4924: nyi khri bzhi stong dus gcig gsal //
NK066(chu)001:4927: de la sogs pa bsam mi khyab //
NK066(chu)001:4929: stong dang nyi khri bzhi stong po de dag la goms pa las su rung nas /
NK066(chu)001:4930: dngos po thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK066(chu)001:4931: 'khor du bsgom pa ni bsam yas lhun grub kyi
NK066(chu)001:4934: phyogs bcu ma lus gzhal yas khang //
NK066(chu)001:4935: nyi zla gza' skar gdan dang rgyan //
NK066(chu)001:4936: bde gshegs dkyil 'khor ma lus bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:4937: bsam yas lhun grub nyid la bslab //
NK066(chu)001:4940: rgyud 'dir rnam grangs spros pa tshig zin la dngos su ma byung na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:4941: zhi ba'i shugs kyis shes par 'gyur ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4943: 'adi'ang gsum ste stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:4944: bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu'i dang //
NK066(chu)001:4945: bsam yas lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor la bslab pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4948: shes rab kyi lha nga brgyad /
NK066(chu)001:4949: sku gsung thugs kyi gnas gsum du byin rlabs kyi lha nga brgyad po re re ste /
NK066(chu)001:4950: nga brgyad pa cha lnga po'i grangs bsdoms na nyis brgya dang dgu bcu /
NK066(chu)001:4951: de las shes rab kyi lha nga brgyad ma gtogs
NK066(chu)001:4952: pa'i lha nyis brgya so gnyis la re re zhing
NK066(chu)001:4953: dbang bskur gyi lha lnga lnga'i yan lag dang ldan
NK066(chu)001:4954: pa'i phyir dbu rgyan gyi lha stong chig brgya drug
NK066(chu)001:4955: cu'o // de nyid sngar gyi nyis brgya dgu bcu
NK066(chu)001:4956: la bsnan pas stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu ste gtso
NK066(chu)001:4957: bo yab yum gnyis la tshang bar bsgom pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:4959: yan lag bkong ba lnga bcu brgyad //
NK066(chu)001:4960: cha lnga'i grangs na nyis brgya dang //
NK066(chu)001:4961: dgu bcu'i lha rnams yan lag ldan //
NK066(chu)001:4963: de la thabs kyi lha nga brgyad ni /
NK066(chu)001:4964: badz+ra he ru ka'i dbu la bud+d+ha /
NK066(chu)001:4968: g.yon pa pad+ma he ru ka /
NK066(chu)001:4969: tshogs brgyad kyi dbang rten nang rtsar goo r+ai ma brgyad /
NK066(chu)001:4971: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK066(chu)001:4972: sgal tshigs nyer brgyad la dbang mo ste lha lnga bcu nga gsum dang /
NK066(chu)001:4973: yum badz+ra kro d+h+ai ma'i yan lag lnga la rigs kyi yum lnga dgod cing /
NK066(chu)001:4974: shes rab byin dbang gsum gyi lha'i 'god tshul ni go sla ba nyid do //
NK066(chu)001:4976: gang rtsa lhar song ba'i shul du badz+ra he ru ka 'god pa'i tshul gyis /
NK066(chu)001:4977: gtso bo yab yum la yan lag gi lha bkod pa bzhin du gzhan rnams la'ang sbyor te /
NK066(chu)001:4978: khrag 'thung rigs lnga zung re re dang /
NK066(chu)001:4979: 'khor gnas yul sgo dbang ste lha mo ya zhe
NK066(chu)001:4980: brgyad po re re la stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu
NK066(chu)001:4982: mdor na stong bzhi brgya lnga bcu pa tsho nga
NK066(chu)001:4983: gsum la bdun khri drug stong brgyad brgya lnga bcu'o
NK066(chu)001:4984: // de ltar na'ang 'khor gyi lha mo rnams la khrag 'thung yab lnga gang du 'god ce na /
NK066(chu)001:4985: lus kyi g.yas phyogs su yab lnga dang lha gzhan
NK066(chu)001:4986: rnams g.yon phyogs su dgong pa tsam khyad par te
NK066(chu)001:4987: / dper na mgo bo'i g.yas su bud+d+ha khrag 'thung dang /
NK066(chu)001:4988: g.yon du bud+d+ha kro d+h+ai ma /
NK066(chu)001:4989: lag g.yas kyi rtsa'i mdun du badz+ra dang rgyab tu rat+na he ru ka /
NK066(chu)001:4990: g.yon gyi mdun rgyab tu de gnyis kyi yum dgod pa sogs rigs 'gre shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:4991: gsum pa bsam yas lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor ni zhi ba ltar ro //
NK066(chu)001:4992: drug pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK066(chu)001:4993: gang rtsa rlung thig le la brten te byang chub
NK066(chu)001:4994: kyi sems bde ba chen po nyid rtogs pa dang
NK066(chu)001:4995: bsgom pa'i thabs ston pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:4997: byang sems phyi nang gsang ba yang //
NK066(chu)001:4998: gnas bzhi khams gsum ye shes che //
NK066(chu)001:4999: zhes pas phyi byang chub kyi sems rtsa rlung /
NK066(chu)001:5000: nang byang chub kyi sems thig le //
NK066(chu)001:5001: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems bde ba'i ye shes so //
NK066(chu)001:5002: de dag kyang snga ma snga ma rten dang phyi ma phyi ma brten pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5004: zab phyir byang sems dkyil 'khor ni //
NK066(chu)001:5005: rten dang brten can tha snyad gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:5006: dbye bas phyi nang mthar thug 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:5008: de la dang po phyi byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor la rtsa dang rlung gnyis kyi /
NK066(chu)001:5010: sgyu 'phrul snying po bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:5011: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK066(chu)001:5012: srog shing gsum dang 'khor lo bzhi //
NK066(chu)001:5017: lus kyi dbus gsang gnas nas gtsug tor gyi bar
NK066(chu)001:5018: du rtsa a ba d+h+au t+ai srog shing gi tshul
NK066(chu)001:5019: du yar sna smin mtshams su zug pa /
NK066(chu)001:5020: de'i g.yas na ro ma dang /
NK066(chu)001:5021: g.yon na rkyang ma gnyis yar sna sna sbug tu
NK066(chu)001:5022: zug ste smin mtshams nas sum gshibs kyi tshul du
NK066(chu)001:5023: song ba'i 'khor lo bzhi'i lte bar so sor mdud
NK066(chu)001:5024: pa'i tshul gyis nang khong 'brel bar gnas pa /
NK066(chu)001:5025: lte ba spu na gu me 'khor gyi thad nas rtsa gsum 'dres shing /
NK066(chu)001:5026: dbu ma ni g.yas ngos su song ste khu ba /
NK066(chu)001:5027: rkyang ma dbus su song ste dri chu /
NK066(chu)001:5028: ro ma g.yon du song ste khrag dang dri chen 'byin sdom byed par bshad do //
NK066(chu)001:5031: cha rkyen gnyis dang bcas pa drug ste /
NK066(chu)001:5034: zhes gsungs pa'i phyir de'ang spyi mgrin snying lte ba'i
NK066(chu)001:5035: 'khor lo bzhi ka'i dbus nas phyogs bzhir rtsa bzhi
NK066(chu)001:5036: bzhi gyes pa / snying gar de bzhi las gnyis re gyes pas brgyad /
NK066(chu)001:5037: mgrin par de las gnyis gnyis gyes pas bcu drug /
NK066(chu)001:5038: spyi bor de las gnyis gnyis gyes pas so gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:5039: lte bar snying ga ltar gyes pa brgyad kyi bzhi
NK066(chu)001:5040: las gnyis re gyes pas 'pho ba'i rtsa bcu gnyis
NK066(chu)001:5041: dang / de'i sngar gyes pa brgyad las lnga lnga dang /
NK066(chu)001:5042: ma gyes pa bzhi las drug re gyes pas drug cu rtsa bzhi'o //
NK066(chu)001:5043: de dag kyang dka' ba gcod pa man ngag snying
NK066(chu)001:5044: po zhes bya ba khro bo stobs kyi rgyud rgyal
NK066(chu)001:5045: las / sum cu gnyis dang bcu drug dang //
NK066(chu)001:5046: brgyad dang drug cu rtsa bzhi yi //
NK066(chu)001:5049: de'ang spyi bo'i 'khor lo la sku'i 'khor lo'am bde
NK066(chu)001:5050: ba chen po'i rten ham yig bzhugs pas bde chen
NK066(chu)001:5053: rang byung 'khor lo rgyu yi bdag /
NK066(chu)001:5054: ka sogs sum cu rtsa gnyis ni //
NK066(chu)001:5055: ma lus kun gyi dngos gzhi ste //
NK066(chu)001:5056: sku yi 'khor lo rang snang ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:5059: bcu tshan gsum nyag ma gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK066(chu)001:5060: bde ba'i thig le mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK066(chu)001:5062: mgrin pa'i rtsa 'dab la gsung gi 'khor lo'am ro
NK066(chu)001:5063: drug myong ba'i phyir longs spyod 'khor lor grags te
NK066(chu)001:5065: sgra dbyangs gsung gi 'khor lo ni //
NK066(chu)001:5066: brjod pa'i sgra ni sna tshogs pa //
NK066(chu)001:5067: ma lus par nas rang snang bas //
NK066(chu)001:5068: gsung gi phyag rgyar nges pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5071: lnga gnyis drug gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK066(chu)001:5072: bde ba chen po'i ro yis ni //
NK066(chu)001:5073: dgyes pa chen po stob par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5075: snying ga'i rtsa 'dab thugs sam chos kyi 'khor lor grags te /
NK066(chu)001:5077: rig pa thugs kyi 'khor lo ni //
NK066(chu)001:5078: zag med ye shes drug ldan zhing //
NK066(chu)001:5079: sde tshan brgyad kyis brgyan pa ni //
NK066(chu)001:5080: snying po dwangs ma lngar snang ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:5083: rtsa bzhi 'od bzhi sa bon drug /
NK066(chu)001:5084: mdor bsdus snying po chos kyi sku //
NK066(chu)001:5087: lte ba'i 'khor lo ni lus thog mar bskyed pa
NK066(chu)001:5088: dang sprul pa'i gnas sam khams gsum la khyab pas
NK066(chu)001:5091: bcu tshan drug pa gcig dang bzhir gyes pa //
NK066(chu)001:5092: khams gsum khyab pas sprul sku'o //
NK066(chu)001:5095: de dag lte ba nas spros te 'dus kyang der 'dus te /
NK066(chu)001:5098: sems gzugs med pa'i khams gsum la khyab pas sprul pa'i 'khor lo ste /
NK066(chu)001:5101: lte 'og sor bzhi spu na gu'i thad na me'i
NK066(chu)001:5102: 'khor lo dbyibs gru gsum pa ram gyis mtshan pa
NK066(chu)001:5104: me dang rdo rje dbyings phyug gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:5105: mnyam du gnas pas drag por bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5107: de'i 'grel pa mi 'jigs pa'i phreng ba las /
NK066(chu)001:5108: gnas ni sprul pa'i 'og sor bzhi na'o //
NK066(chu)001:5109: dbyings phyug ma'i rtsa dang mnyam por gnas pas las kyi mkha' 'gro ma spor ma zhes bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:5110: de'ang dbyibs a las logs dang zur dang mtha' dbus kyis phye bas spor ma brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:5112: de 'og bshang kha rlung gi 'khor lo gzhu'i dbyibs can yam gyis mtshan pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:5114: rlung ni dgug pa gzhu dbyibs te //
NK066(chu)001:5115: sa bon yam gyis g.yo byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:5117: de rnams la 'khor lo zhes brjod pa'i nges pa yang /
NK066(chu)001:5118: rtsibs la sogs pa dbyibs mtshungs pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5119: de dang der byed pa bcings pa las rtog pa
NK066(chu)001:5120: gcod pa'i phyir 'khor lo dang byed las mtshungs pas
NK066(chu)001:5122: rtsa de dag las kyang phye na mngal du lus
NK066(chu)001:5123: chags te bdun phrag bzhi 'das nas mngal zla brgyad
NK066(chu)001:5124: dang phyi rol gyi bzhi ste /
NK066(chu)001:5125: zla ba bcu gnyis kyi bar zhag re zhing rtsa
NK066(chu)001:5126: nyis brgya re chags pas ro rkyang dbu gsum gyi
NK066(chu)001:5127: rigs 'dzin pa'i rtsa stong phrag nyi shu rtsa bzhi
NK066(chu)001:5128: pa tsho gsum la stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis
NK066(chu)001:5130: lus kyi rjes su 'gro ba'i rtsa //
NK066(chu)001:5131: stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis brjod //
NK066(chu)001:5133: de rnams las gyes pa ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5134: ba spu'i grangs ji snyed pa'i rtsa'i grangs kyang de snyed do //
NK066(chu)001:5136: dbu ma'i yar snar gtsug tor dang /
NK066(chu)001:5137: 'og tu gsang ba'i 'khor lo bsnan pa sogs mang nyung mtha' gcig tu ma nges par gsungs shing /
NK066(chu)001:5138: mdor na rnal 'byor pas shes par bya ba'i rtsa stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK066(chu)001:5139: de rnams kyi gtso bor gyur pa 'khor lo'i rtsa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5140: de rnams las kyang gtso bor gyur pa'i rtsa sum cu rtsa gnyis la sogs pa bshad la /
NK066(chu)001:5141: 'khor lo drug gi rlung sems kyi dwangs ma 'dzin cing snyigs mas nad skyed par byed de /
NK066(chu)001:5142: gtsug tor dang dpral bas bad kan //
NK066(chu)001:5144: lte gsang gi phyi skor gyis rlung nad /
NK066(chu)001:5145: gsang ba'i nang skor gyis 'dus pa'i nad bskyed do zhes 'byung ngo //
NK066(chu)001:5146: de yang lus la rags phra shin tu phra ba gsum las 'di ni phra ba'i lus te /
NK066(chu)001:5147: shin phra'i lus ni rtsa thams cad kyi gshis zung
NK066(chu)001:5148: 'jug ye shes kyi dbu ma zhes grags pa gang
NK066(chu)001:5149: yin pa de'o // de rnams su rgyu ba'i rlung la /
NK066(chu)001:5151: ye shes kyi rlung gnyis las /
NK066(chu)001:5157: thur sel lnga ni rtsa ba phung po'i rlung ste /
NK066(chu)001:5163: 'gro 'dug bshang gci khu gsum 'byin sdom dang bcas pa'i bya ba byed la /
NK066(chu)001:5165: brgyal smyo shi ba sogs dang /
NK066(chu)001:5169: smad kyi nad rnams bskyed cing /
NK066(chu)001:5170: de dag lus kyi dbus dang /
NK066(chu)001:5172: pags pa'i mthar thug pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5174: lte ba man chad na gnas so zhes kha cig nas bshad /
NK066(chu)001:5178: lus kyi tshigs thams cad dang /
NK066(chu)001:5180: gsang gnas rnams su gnas par gsang ba'i snying po khro bo stobs kyi rgyud rgyal las gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:5182: tshigs la khyab byed rlung gnas pa //
NK066(chu)001:5183: gzugs kyi phung po rnam snang sku //
NK066(chu)001:5185: rgyu ba sogs yan lag gi rlung lnga ni /
NK066(chu)001:5186: dbang po lnga la gnas shing bskyed pa sogs kyi bya ba byed pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5188: rgyu ba'i gnas ni spyan yin te //
NK066(chu)001:5189: rnam par rgyu ba rna ba la //
NK066(chu)001:5190: yang dag rgyu ba sna dang ni //
NK066(chu)001:5191: rab tu rgyu ba lce la gnas //
NK066(chu)001:5192: nges par rgyu ba lus nyid do //
NK066(chu)001:5193: mig dang rna ba sna dang lce //
NK066(chu)001:5194: sa snying la sogs sems dpa' brgyad //
NK066(chu)001:5195: rnam shes dbang po phyi nang phye //
NK066(chu)001:5196: zhes sogs rgya cher gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:5197: bye brag tu snar rgyu ba'i rlung ni /
NK066(chu)001:5198: khro bo stobs kyi rnal 'byor dbang phyug sgrub pa
NK066(chu)001:5199: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyud las gyen du g.yas g.yon
NK066(chu)001:5200: gnyis ka nas dkyil 'khor rim par rgyu ba ni
NK066(chu)001:5201: / khri phrag gnyis dang stong phrag dang //
NK066(chu)001:5202: drug brgya nyin mtshan 'byung byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:5203: zhes pas nyin zhag phrugs re la rlung nyi khri chig stong drug brgya rgyu la /
NK066(chu)001:5204: de yang 'pho ba bcu gnyis pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK066(chu)001:5205: lte ba'i rtsa 'dab drug cu re bzhi las /
NK066(chu)001:5206: sngar drug tu gyes pa'i ya gyal bzhi po dbu ma'i 'pho ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:5207: dkyil 'khor mi 'bab pas stong pa'i rtsa bzhi zhes bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:5208: de lhag drug cu po nas rgyu tshul ni /
NK066(chu)001:5209: ba spu'i mthar thug pa'i rtsa lam nas rtsa 'khor
NK066(chu)001:5210: gyi rlung rnams lte ba'i rlung dang 'dres te ro
NK066(chu)001:5211: rkyang gi lam las sna sgor 'bab la /
NK066(chu)001:5212: de yang 'byung ba lnga g.yas g.yon sdud bskyed kyi
NK066(chu)001:5213: rim pas 'pho ba re la dbyug gu lnga re
NK066(chu)001:5214: / dbyug gu re la dbugs sum brgya drug cu ste /
NK066(chu)001:5215: 'pho ba re la dbugs stong brgyad brgya pa re rgyu na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:5216: de'i steng na stong pa'i rtsa bzhi'i dbye bas dbugs
NK066(chu)001:5217: gcig gi phyed bcas so gnyis cha re ye shes
NK066(chu)001:5219: de bsags pas dbyug gu re la dbugs bcu gcig dang bzhi cha gcig /
NK066(chu)001:5220: 'pho ba re la nga drug rkang bcas /
NK066(chu)001:5221: nyin zhag gcig la drug brgya don lnga rnams rgyu zhing de chu tshod du dril na /
NK066(chu)001:5225: de zla ba gcig tu bsags pas chu tshod nga drug dang /
NK066(chu)001:5227: de bcu gnyis su zlos pas zhag bcu gcig dang /
NK066(chu)001:5228: chu tshod bco lnga rnams lo gcig gi ye rlung
NK066(chu)001:5229: gi grangs te phyi rol du zla bshol gyi rgyur
NK066(chu)001:5230: 'gyur la / skyes bu lo brgya pa'i ye rlung
NK066(chu)001:5231: bsdoms pas lo gsum tu longs pa sogs rgyud gzhan
NK066(chu)001:5239: tshad kyang lte 'og sor bzhi nas brgyad de sna
NK066(chu)001:5240: rtse las sor bcu gnyis nas bcu drug gi bar
NK066(chu)001:5242: yang 'pho ba bcu drug pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK066(chu)001:5244: sa yi rlung dang chu dang me //
NK066(chu)001:5245: rlung dag rim bzhin 'byung byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:5246: gyen dang mthur du 'byung bar byed //
NK066(chu)001:5247: gyen du g.yas g.yon gnyis ka nas //
NK066(chu)001:5248: dkyil 'khor rim par rgyu ba ni //
NK066(chu)001:5249: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i phyir rgyu ba'i rlung sa chu me rlung bzhi ste /
NK066(chu)001:5250: de nyid kyang g.yas g.yon gyi dbye bas zhag gcig
NK066(chu)001:5251: la nyi khri chig stong drug bargya'ang thun brgyad du
NK066(chu)001:5252: 'gyur ro // 'byung chen bzhi po re re la
NK066(chu)001:5253: 'byung chung bzhi bzhi yod pas 'pho ba bcu drug
NK066(chu)001:5254: 'gyur ro // / de yang g.yas g.yon gyi dbye bas chu tshod so gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:5255: 'pho ba las cha bzhir phye bas dbyug gu re bzhi'o //
NK066(chu)001:5257: 'dir skyes bu'i dbugs drug gi chu chung gcig dang /
NK066(chu)001:5258: bzhi cha gcig dang bcas pa'i chu srang ngang drug ni dbyug gu ste /
NK066(chu)001:5259: de re bzhi la zhag gcig go //
NK066(chu)001:5260: de yang zhag gcig gi ye rlung drug brgya don lnga las /
NK066(chu)001:5261: 'pho ba bcu drug gi thob skal brtsis pas 'pho
NK066(chu)001:5262: ba re la ye rlung bzhi bcu zhe gnyis dang
NK066(chu)001:5265: chu tshod so gnyis kyi gcig gis ye rlung nyer gcig dang /
NK066(chu)001:5268: dbyug gu gcig gis ye rlung phyed dang bcu gcig dang /
NK066(chu)001:5270: go gnyis cha gcig thob bo /
NK066(chu)001:5271: de phyir dbugs so gnyis phyi nang du rgyu ba'i
NK066(chu)001:5272: bar nas ye shes kyi dbugs gcig dbu ma la
NK066(chu)001:5274: de lta bu'i ye shes rlung de ni /
NK066(chu)001:5275: lus can rnams kyi ngag gi chos dang phyi rol
NK066(chu)001:5276: du dus kyi chos rnams kyi rten nam 'char gzhi
NK066(chu)001:5277: dang / rgyu rgyud kyi rten du gyur pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5278: chos thams cad kyi gshis la rgyun mi 'chad par
NK066(chu)001:5279: gnas pa'i srog chen po'i rlung zhes bya ba de
NK066(chu)001:5280: nyid do // de yang 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa las /
NK066(chu)001:5281: srog chen po ste skye ba med //
NK066(chu)001:5282: tshig tu brjod pa spangs pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:5283: brjod pa kun gyi rgyu yi mchog /
NK066(chu)001:5284: tshig kun rab tu gsal bar byed //
NK066(chu)001:5286: des na rlung bcings pa las rags pa'i las rlung nyid kyang ye shes kyi rlung du 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:5288: lta stangs la brten te rgya yan la bslab pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5290: 'byung rlung gi dbyibs mdog la bslab pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5291: dgag pa'i sbyor bas bum can bsgom pa la sogs
NK066(chu)001:5292: pa'i thabs kyis dbu mar brtan pa las yon tan
NK066(chu)001:5294: rtog rlung g.yo ba rlung bzung la //
NK066(chu)001:5295: zhi ba bum pa drag po sogs //
NK066(chu)001:5296: sgrol ma bzung ba'i thabs rnams kyis //
NK066(chu)001:5297: dmigs pas rig pa phur la gdab //
NK066(chu)001:5300: rlung ni khri phrag gnyis dag dang //
NK066(chu)001:5301: brgya phrag bcu drug dus zhes bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5302: dbu ma'i rtsa yi nang du ni //
NK066(chu)001:5303: de bsdus pas ni dus zhes bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5306: de re re la gsum du phye bas nyer bzhi dang /
NK066(chu)001:5307: de dag la 'byung bzhi rim pas dus kyi lha mo bzhi bzhi ste /
NK066(chu)001:5308: lha mo dgu bcu rtsa drug la sogs pa'i cha bzung nas brtsi bar gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:5309: khro bo stobs kyi sgrub rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:5310: thun gcig thun gnyis thun phran dang //
NK066(chu)001:5311: dbyug gu lha mo'i nus pa gang //
NK066(chu)001:5312: nus pas dbugs bgrang grangs bzung nas //
NK066(chu)001:5313: ngal ba med par dbugs la brten //
NK066(chu)001:5316: g.yas par me rlung dmar zhing 'tsher //
NK066(chu)001:5317: g.yon pa rlung 'byung gnag la dwangs //
NK066(chu)001:5318: gnyis kar dkyil rgyu chu rlung dkar //
NK066(chu)001:5319: gnyis kar mthur rngub sa rlung ser //
NK066(chu)001:5320: lha mo bdag po dang ldan pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:5321: ye shes bzhi nyid 'byung bar byed //
NK066(chu)001:5324: sna gnyis kyi dbus nas mkha' rlung dang /
NK066(chu)001:5327: ka ba'i ngos gnyis nas chu /
NK066(chu)001:5328: 'og gi cha nas sa rlung ste /
NK066(chu)001:5329: phyogs bzhi dbus dang bcas pa las 'byung lnga'i rlung 'bab par bshad do //
NK066(chu)001:5330: de dag ni phyi byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK066(chu)001:5331: rtsa rlung thams cad kyi bskyed sdud kyi gnas snying ga'i rtsa rlung gi dwangs ma ni dkyil dang /
NK066(chu)001:5332: yan lag gi rtsa rlung rnams ni 'khor ro //
NK066(chu)001:5333: gnyis pa nang byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK066(chu)001:5337: thig le thams cad kyi rtsa ba rgyu rgyud kyi
NK066(chu)001:5338: rten du gyur pa ye shes snying po'i thig le'am
NK066(chu)001:5339: mi shigs pa'i thig le zhes bshad pa gang yin
NK066(chu)001:5340: pa ste / stong gsal 'gag med kyi ngo bor bzhugs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5342: rgyud gzhan gyi lugs kyis go don spyir bstan pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5343: rgyud 'di'i dgos chos kyi nges pa bshad pa gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:5345: rlung sngags rdzas kyi thig le gsum gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:5346: snying ga'i mi shigs pa'i thig le'i nges pas /
NK066(chu)001:5347: rlung gi byed bcings las gzung 'dzin gyi snang ba rang grol du gyur pa ni rlung thig /
NK066(chu)001:5348: sna rtser thig le la lha'i mtshan ma bsgoms pas
NK066(chu)001:5349: tha mal gyi snang zhen las yid skyob pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:5350: sngags thig / 'og gi sna rtser thig le bsgom
NK066(chu)001:5351: pa las bde ba 'char ba sogs rdzas thig go
NK066(chu)001:5352: sngags thig / // de'ang phyi ma cung zad bshad na /
NK066(chu)001:5353: khams dkar dmar gnyis las dwangs snyigs gnyis su gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:5354: spyi bor pha las thob pa'i dkar cha ham gi rang bzhin dang /
NK066(chu)001:5355: lte 'og rtsa gsum 'dus mdor ma las thob pa'i dmar cha a thung gi rang bzhin te /
NK066(chu)001:5356: lus kyi dkar cha dang dmar cha thams cad kyi bdag por gyur pa /
NK066(chu)001:5357: dbu ma'i cha la brten pa /
NK066(chu)001:5358: rnam shes kyi rten byed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5359: de las kyang dwangs snyigs gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:5360: mngal du ma'i rtsa dang 'brel bas bskyed cing /
NK066(chu)001:5361: btsas nas bza' btung rnams 'pho bar bad kan gyis myags par byed /
NK066(chu)001:5363: rlung me mnyam ste me drod gsum gyis spar bzhu myags par byas pas /
NK066(chu)001:5364: dwangs ma mchin par khrag tu gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:5371: des stobs dang mdangs su 'gyur la /
NK066(chu)001:5372: de rnams kyi snyigs ma ni rim bzhin du /
NK066(chu)001:5378: sbubs kyi dri ma mchil snabs la sogs pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5380: lus zungs bdun zhes grags shing /
NK066(chu)001:5381: de dag gi rnam dbye yang /
NK066(chu)001:5382: spyi bo mi phyed ma nas so sen 'bab pa sogs khams nyi shu rtsa bzhi /
NK066(chu)001:5383: de re re la'ang thim longs bdag po gsum du phye bas khams bdun cu rtsa gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:5384: de stong gis phye bas stong phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:5385: de stong gis phye bas bye ba phrag bdun cu rtsa gnyis sogs rtsa ji snyed par rlung /
NK066(chu)001:5386: rlung ji snyed par thig les khyab par gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:5387: rnal 'byor ma'i rgyud las khams nyer bzhi'i steng du rtsa'i gtso mo gsum dang /
NK066(chu)001:5388: sum sgril ma la sogs te lnga bsnan nas so gnyis su gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:5389: he ru ka gal po las /
NK066(chu)001:5390: lus la byang chub sems rgyu ba'i //
NK066(chu)001:5391: rtsa ni sum cu rtsa gnyis te //
NK066(chu)001:5393: de'i steng du rtsa ba' rlung lnga rgyu ba'i srog
NK066(chu)001:5394: chen po ma gtogs pa'i bzhi bsnan nas sum cu
NK066(chu)001:5395: rtsa drug tu bshad pa'ang snang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:5396: de dag kyang 'khor lo bzhir dga' bzhi'i 'gros kyis
NK066(chu)001:5397: ye shes dang rjes su 'brel bar 'pho ba dang
NK066(chu)001:5398: / lus la zungs sam nus pa'am gnad kyi ngo
NK066(chu)001:5399: bo nyid du rnam shes dang rjes su 'brel bar
NK066(chu)001:5400: 'pho ba bla gnas zhes grags pa dag ste go
NK066(chu)001:5404: rlung sngags rdzas kyi thig le gsum don la tshang mod kyi /
NK066(chu)001:5405: 'on kyang tha snyad 'brel chags su gsungs pa mi snang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:5406: des na 'dir thig le 'ching ba'i gnyen po'i man
NK066(chu)001:5407: ngag dang 'brel bar che long tsam gsungs pa las
NK066(chu)001:5408: khyad par gyi sgos chos dag 'chad par 'dod do
NK066(chu)001:5409: // de yang snying lte mgrin pa spyi bo'i thig le bzhi las /
NK066(chu)001:5410: thog mar ye shes kyi thig le'i nges pa las
NK066(chu)001:5411: snying gar dwangs ma lnga'i dbus na ye shes snying
NK066(chu)001:5412: po'i thig le yi ge wam gyi rang bzhin du
NK066(chu)001:5414: dwangs ma lnga gang zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:5416: rtsa bzhi 'od bzhir sa bon drug /
NK066(chu)001:5417: mdor bsdus snying po chos kyi sku //
NK066(chu)001:5418: zhes pa'i rtsa bzhi ni gsang thig gi 'grel pa las /
NK066(chu)001:5423: de ltar brgyad du shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:5424: zhes snying dbus kyi rtsa brgyad po rtsa bzhir 'du zhing /
NK066(chu)001:5425: de dag 'od bzhi dang dbyibs bzhir gnas pa la /
NK066(chu)001:5427: sbyang bya rigs drug gi yi ge sbyong byed 'bru gsum gyis mnan nas gnas par bshad de /
NK066(chu)001:5429: chos nyid lha min dud 'gro zlum //
NK066(chu)001:5430: kun gzhi gi snying por ldan //
NK066(chu)001:5431: ye shes lha mi gru bzhi yid //
NK066(chu)001:5432: snying po h+aum ni bde gshegs thugs //
NK066(chu)001:5433: yon tan dmyal ba yi dwags +aah /
NK066(chu)001:5434: zla gam gsung gi rang bzhin yin //
NK066(chu)001:5435: dmar nag gdong la lkog zhol dbyibs //
NK066(chu)001:5436: de ni blun rmugs snod yin te //
NK066(chu)001:5437: shes pa gsum la snyoms par 'gengs //
NK066(chu)001:5438: drag po nyid du'ang bshad par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5441: chos nya da ye shes yon tan dang //
NK066(chu)001:5442: rang rgyud bzhi la yan lag brgyad //
NK066(chu)001:5443: ces pas dang po mdun na yod de /
NK066(chu)001:5444: skye ba med par rang snang ba'i las byed do //
NK066(chu)001:5445: gnyis pa g.yas na yod de /
NK066(chu)001:5446: ye shes 'char ba'i las byed do //
NK066(chu)001:5447: gsum pa g.yon na yod de /
NK066(chu)001:5448: des mngon par shes pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5450: bzhi pa rgyab na yod de /
NK066(chu)001:5451: shes pa rnams rmongs shing 'joms pa'i las byed do //
NK066(chu)001:5453: 'od bzhi'ang dbyibs dang bstun nas rim par sbyor te /
NK066(chu)001:5460: rtsa bzhi'i dbus na 'byung ba sa 1chu 2rlung 3me
NK066(chu)001:5465: nyi ldan me long ngad dag ni //
NK066(chu)001:5466: 'byung ba bzhi yi dwangs ma ste //
NK066(chu)001:5467: bde ba'i dwangs 5ma nam mkha'i khams //
NK066(chu)001:5469: de ltar dwangs ma lnga 'dus kyi dbus na ye
NK066(chu)001:5470: shes snying po'i thig le ye nas gnas pa de
NK066(chu)001:5471: / yum lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor ye nas rang chas su ldan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5472: de'ang gsal sgron mi 'jigs phreng ba las /
NK066(chu)001:5473: de dbus spros med thig le ni //
NK066(chu)001:5474: ngo bo nyid sku de tshul ni //
NK066(chu)001:5475: gser sbubs rin chen ze'u bcug ltar //
NK066(chu)001:5476: phyi nang med gsal rang byung ste //
NK066(chu)001:5478: yang lte ba'i rtsa 'dab re bzhi'i dbus na dbyings
NK066(chu)001:5479: phyug lnga'i thig le zhes bya ba kun tu bzang
NK066(chu)001:5480: mo'i rang bzhin yi ge a'i rnam par bzhugs te
NK066(chu)001:5482: gsang ba'i shes rab thig le'i dbyings //
NK066(chu)001:5483: bcu drug bzhi yi dkyil na bzhugs //
NK066(chu)001:5485: mgrin pa'i 'khor lo'i dbus na mkha' 'gro ma rngam
NK066(chu)001:5486: ma zhes bya ba yi ge am gi dbyibs su
NK066(chu)001:5487: gnas pa ste / dbang gi gal po'i rang 'grel las /
NK066(chu)001:5488: rang bzhin gyi mkha' 'gro ma rngam ma zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:5489: cir yang gnas pa med par longs spyod thams cad la rol pa ni lce ste /
NK066(chu)001:5490: phyi nang kun brda' sprod par byed pas khyab ma zhes kyang gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:5492: spyi bo'i 'khor lo'i dbus na kun tu bzang po'i
NK066(chu)001:5493: thig le ham yig dkar po mgo mthur bstan gyis
NK066(chu)001:5494: gnas pa ste / thal rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:5495: mi 'gyur brtan pa'i thig le nyid //
NK066(chu)001:5496: ham yig snying po byang chub sems //
NK066(chu)001:5498: lte 'og na gtum mo me'i rang bzhin ram dang /
NK066(chu)001:5499: sbar byed rlung 'khor la yam yig dang bcas pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5501: zab phyir byang sems dkyil 'khor ni //
NK066(chu)001:5503: ngo bo gsang ba'i khams gsum mo //
NK066(chu)001:5506: bco brgyad khams gsum snying po nyid //
NK066(chu)001:5507: zhes pas khams bco brgyad dang /
NK066(chu)001:5508: gsang ba'i khams gsum ste nyi shu rtsa gcig go //
NK066(chu)001:5511: yul dang dbang po rnam par shes //
NK066(chu)001:5512: thams cad gsum drug 'dra du phye ba yis //
NK066(chu)001:5513: khams ni bco brgyad dag tu bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5516: yab yum gyi gsang ba'i snying po dang /
NK066(chu)001:5517: gnyis su med pa'i lhag pa byang chub kyi sems gsum ni /
NK066(chu)001:5518: 'khor 'das kyi chos kun gyi gzhir ldan te /
NK066(chu)001:5519: de yang zag pa dang bcas pa'i sems ni lus kyi sa bon can yin la /
NK066(chu)001:5520: lus kyi zag pa sa bon byang chub kyi sems yin te //
NK066(chu)001:5521: de'i phyir khu ba'i zag pa dang bral ba'i nyon mongs pa'i zag pa can ni mi srid de /
NK066(chu)001:5523: 'byung chen lnga dang 'dod yon lnga'i zag pa'i nang nas /
NK066(chu)001:5524: stong pa dang sgra'i zag pa gnyis mngon gyur dang /
NK066(chu)001:5525: lhag rnams sa bon du yod par bshad pa'i 'khor ba'i gzhi dang /
NK066(chu)001:5527: gnyis med kyi ye shes skye ba'i gzhir gyur pas
NK066(chu)001:5528: 'das chos kyis yon tan thams cad rdzogs su rung
NK066(chu)001:5529: ba'i phyir ro // de'ang spyan 'grel las /
NK066(chu)001:5530: gsang sngags phyi pa gsum dang /
NK066(chu)001:5531: bstan bcos kyi gtsug lag las yul dbang po shes
NK066(chu)001:5532: pa drug gsum bco brgyad du bstan nas che ba
NK066(chu)001:5533: 'don pa'i phyir gtan tshigs gnyis kyis khams nyi shu
NK066(chu)001:5534: rtsa gcig tu bstan pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:5536: zhes dang bco brgyad kyi rtsa ba phyag rgya'i yon
NK066(chu)001:5537: tan ril dang bar byed pa'i rten gyi las can
NK066(chu)001:5538: rdo rje dang / yon tan gyi tshogs dang ldan pa'i pad+ma dang /
NK066(chu)001:5539: rlung gi thabs mnyam du gyur pa las skyes pa'i ye shes ni /
NK066(chu)001:5540: rten dang brten can gyi sgo nas nang dang gsang ba'i byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK066(chu)001:5542: de dag la nang byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor zhes grags te /
NK066(chu)001:5543: sngar phyi'i skabs su bshad pa ltar dang /
NK066(chu)001:5544: khams gsum snying po dang bco brgyad 'khor du las rim las gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:5545: gsum pa gsang ba byang sems bde ba'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor ni //
NK066(chu)001:5547: 'og sgo thig le drod dbab kyi gnad kyis 'pho
NK066(chu)001:5548: med du bcings pa las bde ba'i ye shes nyams
NK066(chu)001:5549: su myong ba'o // de yang dgyes pa rdo rje las /
NK066(chu)001:5550: dkyil ni snying po zhes brjod de //
NK066(chu)001:5551: byang chub sems ni bde chen no //
NK066(chu)001:5552: len par byed pas dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK066(chu)001:5555: bdun pa tshom bu tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK066(chu)001:5556: gang zhig rten dang gang zag dang yo byad khyad par can tshogs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5558: tshogs ni 'byor pa rnam pa gsum //
NK066(chu)001:5559: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5560: de re re'ang skabs kyi gsum gsum ste /
NK066(chu)001:5561: skal ldan mi dang dgyes ldan lha //
NK066(chu)001:5562: 'byor ldan yo byad lnga sogs so //
NK066(chu)001:5563: zhes pas dbye na skal ldan mi'i //
NK066(chu)001:5565: dgyes ldan lha'i tshogs gsum gyi steng du tshogs chen po bsnan pas bzhi'o //
NK066(chu)001:5567: gang thabs shes zung du 'brel ba'i skye bo dam pa 'dus pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5569: skye bo mdza' ba kun tshogs pa //
NK066(chu)001:5573: khyad par gyi yo byad lnga la sogs pa tshogs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5575: rnal 'byor yo byad tshang bas na //
NK066(chu)001:5576: bde ba longs spyod tshogs su bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5579: rten dang brten par bcas pa'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor srung ma dang bcas pa /
NK066(chu)001:5580: dngos grub kyi rten du gzugs brnyan bkod cing bsgom pa la sogs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5582: lha dang dam can kun 'dus pa //
NK066(chu)001:5583: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5586: de dag la ma 'gags par spyad pas bsod nams dang /
NK066(chu)001:5587: spyod bzhin du mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis zin
NK066(chu)001:5588: pas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pa ni tshogs chen
NK066(chu)001:5590: thams cad spyod pa la mi 'dzin pa //
NK066(chu)001:5591: tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs pas //
NK066(chu)001:5592: tshogs chen po ru nges par bshad //
