NK066(chu)001:5594: de dag gi las kyi rim pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:5596: gzhi dang gzhung gis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:5597: phun sum tshogs pa lnga bzhi la //
NK066(chu)001:5598: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yi gzhung bsrang ba'ang //
NK066(chu)001:5599: gang dag mos pa ji bzhin du //
NK066(chu)001:5600: zhi dang khro bos bsgrub par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5602: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK066(chu)001:5603: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba /
NK066(chu)001:5604: 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bshad pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5607: de yang snga ma gnas dang dus //
NK066(chu)001:5608: yo byad ston 'khor sgrub pa po //
NK066(chu)001:5609: sgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK066(chu)001:5610: gzhi dang sbyar bas gzhung rdzogs bya //
NK066(chu)001:5613: gang gi tshe sgrub pa'i dus /
NK066(chu)001:5614: gang la brten nas sgrub pa'i yo byad /
NK066(chu)001:5615: gang gis sgrub pa'i sgrub pa po //
NK066(chu)001:5616: gang bsgrub par bya ba'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5619: rnyed nas gnas khang bca' ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:5622: sde dpung chen pos mi tshugs shing //
NK066(chu)001:5623: sa dang bar snang shis pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:5624: lo rgyus rnam gnyis ldan pa yi //
NK066(chu)001:5625: yid 'ong sa btsal rgyas par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5629: rnyed nas tshom bu'i grangs bzhin du //
NK066(chu)001:5630: che chung rkyen du 'tshams par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5631: bskor khang phyi nang bar ldan pa //
NK066(chu)001:5633: der khang pa sum thog phyi nang rim pa gsum brtsigs pa'i phyir g.yos sbyor /
NK066(chu)001:5635: nang du sbyor sgrol byed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5638: bsgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes grangs ni //
NK066(chu)001:5639: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK066(chu)001:5641: de yang sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i dus ni /
NK066(chu)001:5643: tshes grangs yar gyi brgyad la brtsam //
NK066(chu)001:5644: shin tu skar ma rgyal rnams la //
NK066(chu)001:5645: byang chub spyad pa cher spyod pa //
NK066(chu)001:5646: gsang mchog dngos grub myur ba'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:5647: gza' skar shis pa blang bar bya //
NK066(chu)001:5650: rig byed dag gi yan lag las //
NK066(chu)001:5651: dus rnams shes par bya ba ni //
NK066(chu)001:5652: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK066(chu)001:5653: 'byor dang dus tshod bzang ba ni //
NK066(chu)001:5654: mtshan ma'i rtog pa yin mod kyang //
NK066(chu)001:5655: brtags na dngos grub mtshan ma 'byung //
NK066(chu)001:5659: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK066(chu)001:5660: zhes sogs te 'og tu ston no //
NK066(chu)001:5662: khyed kyi gsang ba snying po 'di rgyud ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:5663: rgyud la kha 'phangs pas so zer /
NK066(chu)001:5664: de ltar na khyed rang rgyud du 'dod pa'i 'jam dpal sgyu d+r+wa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5666: mkha' 'gro ma kun spyod kyi rgyud la sogs pa'ang rgyud ma yin par 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:5668: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las //
NK066(chu)001:5670: ji ltar de nyid bsdus pa yi //
NK066(chu)001:5671: dkyil 'khor cho ga bzhin du bya //
NK066(chu)001:5673: rgyud du sbas pa 'dir bshad bya //
NK066(chu)001:5674: zhes rgyud gzhan la kha 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:5679: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad rnams tshang bar bsog pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5681: gos rgyan bza' btung gsang ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:5682: sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga rnams dang //
NK066(chu)001:5683: dkyil 'khor yo byad mchod pa'i rdzas //
NK066(chu)001:5684: dngos grub brten dang bar chad bzlog /
NK066(chu)001:5685: yo byad dag pa bsdu bya ste //
NK066(chu)001:5687: de yang yo byad tsho gsum du bcad de /
NK066(chu)001:5688: cha gcig gis sngon du mchod sbyiin bya //
NK066(chu)001:5689: cha gcig mjug tu dga' ston gyi phyir bzhag /
NK066(chu)001:5690: cha gcig ram yam kham gis sbyangs la t+r+aam las
NK066(chu)001:5691: 'dod yon du byin gyis rlobs te sgrub pa'i cha
NK066(chu)001:5694: tsho gsum bcad la byin gyis rlobs //
NK066(chu)001:5697: gang gis sgrub pa'i ston pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:5698: gang du lhan cig tu sgrub pa'i 'khor gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:5701: ston pa mdzod ldan chu bo rdzogs //
NK066(chu)001:5702: gnyer ldan rgyud dang las la mkhas //
NK066(chu)001:5704: rnal 'byor mthar ldan shin tu bsten //
NK066(chu)001:5705: zhes pa'i rang bzhin brgyad ldan no //
NK066(chu)001:5707: spyir yon tan drug dang ldan pa'i 'khor te /
NK066(chu)001:5710: mchod brtson rtogs pa ni lta ba bsgom pa /
NK066(chu)001:5712: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK066(chu)001:5713: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK066(chu)001:5715: khyad par slob dpon dang dgongs pa mnyam pa'i rdo rje rgyal tshab dang /
NK066(chu)001:5716: skad gdangs che zhing las khrigs mkhas pa'i rdo rje las mkhan dang /
NK066(chu)001:5717: sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa'i las bzhi'i gzungs ma dang /
NK066(chu)001:5718: mi ma yin mthong ba'i mig rnon gyis nyul le
NK066(chu)001:5719: shes shing bzlog nus pa'i rdo rje spyan pa dang
NK066(chu)001:5720: / drod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje bya rog dang /
NK066(chu)001:5721: sgrol ba'i las la mkhas pa'i ging ka ra dang /
NK066(chu)001:5722: g.yos la mkhas pa'i byan po dang /
NK066(chu)001:5723: phyi nang gi brda sbyor mkhas pa'i rdul phyags skyes
NK066(chu)001:5724: bu sogs tshom bur 'brel ba'i 'khor phun sum tshogs
NK066(chu)001:5726: rgyal tshab rgyal por mtshungs pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:5727: karma gdangs chen phreng bar ldan //
NK066(chu)001:5728: ljon lcug sdong reg gcig mes kyang /
NK066(chu)001:5730: rnal 'byor ming sring brtse gdung ldan //
NK066(chu)001:5731: tshom bu lnga'am zung gis sgrub //
NK066(chu)001:5733: tshogs kyi 'khor lo thugs kyi sgrub pa las /
NK066(chu)001:5734: mdor na tshab kar phyag rgya dang //
NK066(chu)001:5735: nyul dang bya rog spyan pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:5736: rdul phyags la sogs yon tan ldan //
NK066(chu)001:5738: spyir ji tsam 'tshogs pa'i tshad ni //
NK066(chu)001:5739: rnal 'byor pa lha grangs dang mthun par 'du na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:5740: grangs gcig tu ma nges te /
NK066(chu)001:5742: 'dus pa chung la gnyis drug bcu //
NK066(chu)001:5744: chen po rab tu mang po'o //
NK066(chu)001:5745: zhes pas 'dus pa chung du'i tshe tshom bu gcig
NK066(chu)001:5746: gsum lnga ba'i gtso bo yab yum tsam 'tshogs pa
NK066(chu)001:5750: 'bring la lha grangs dang mnyam pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5755: de yan chad rab tu mang po 'dus pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5757: tshom bu lnga bcu stong dang bcas //
NK066(chu)001:5761: sgrub thabs yan lag bzhi sbyar la //
NK066(chu)001:5763: bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i sgo nas sgrub pa'i thabs phun sum tshogs pa shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:5764: des na sgrub pa'i mthun rkyen gyi yan lag thams
NK066(chu)001:5765: cad tshogs par byas nas bsgrubs na gdon mi za
NK066(chu)001:5768: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK066(chu)001:5769: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK066(chu)001:5770: dang por dam nos bzhin du bya //
NK066(chu)001:5771: le lo sgyid snyoms med pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:5772: the tshom med par bsgrub byas na //
NK066(chu)001:5774: rdo rje gsang mchog dam pa thob //
NK066(chu)001:5776: gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba ni //
NK066(chu)001:5777: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen dang //
NK066(chu)001:5778: sgrub pa dang ni sgrub chen po //
NK066(chu)001:5781: 'di yang lam sgrub sbyor ba yi //
NK066(chu)001:5785: bsgrub pa'i dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhi'o //
NK066(chu)001:5787: lta ba rtogs nas stong chen dang kun ting la gnas pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK066(chu)001:5788: phyag rgya gcig spros ni nye bsnyen /
NK066(chu)001:5789: yo byad lngas tshogs sgrub pa ni sgrub pa /
NK066(chu)001:5790: de 'bras zag med kyi rig 'dzin thob ma rag pa'i ni sgrub chen te /
NK066(chu)001:5792: byang chub sems rtogs 'grus pa ni //
NK066(chu)001:5793: bsnyen pa'i dam pa yin pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:5794: sems chas snying rje man chad do //
NK066(chu)001:5795: phyag rgya gsal ba nye bsnyen pa //
NK066(chu)001:5796: de phyir gcig dang spros pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5797: sgrub pa nyid ni bar chad med //
NK066(chu)001:5798: dus kyi tshogs mthas sgrub chen len //
NK066(chu)001:5801: yum btsal te chas su bcug pa bsnyen pa /
NK066(chu)001:5802: de byin gyis rlob pa ni nye bsnyen /
NK066(chu)001:5803: rol nas dbab bzung gi dgongs pa ni sgrub pa /
NK066(chu)001:5804: nyi zla rdo rje'i lces lon te ldog dgram gyi
NK066(chu)001:5805: dgongs pa ni sgrub chen te lag len sbyor mchod
NK066(chu)001:5806: bzhin no // de'ang lam rim las /
NK066(chu)001:5807: gsum pa mchod pa'i skabs bzhin shes //
NK066(chu)001:5810: zla ba gcig la sgrub pa rdzogs pa ma yin
NK066(chu)001:5811: pas zla drug la sogs pa ji tsam byed pa
NK066(chu)001:5812: la cha brtsi ba yin mod kyi /
NK066(chu)001:5813: 'on kyang 'dir zla ba gcig lta bu la dper byas te brtsi na /
NK066(chu)001:5815: zla phyed phyed zhal nye bsnyen pa //
NK066(chu)001:5817: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:5819: zhag grangs tshang nas rtags byung na //
NK066(chu)001:5820: dngos grub bzlas blang sgrub chen po //
NK066(chu)001:5821: zhes pas cha rkyen rnams tshogs nas sgrub pa la 'jug par ma thogs pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK066(chu)001:5822: zhugs nas zla ba phyed yan chad ni nye bsnyen /
NK066(chu)001:5823: tha ma'i zhag gcig ma gtogs pa'i phyed man chad ni sgrub pa /
NK066(chu)001:5824: nub tha ma la dngos grub len pa ni sgrub pa chen po ste /
NK066(chu)001:5826: rim pa shom dang 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:5827: bsnyen pa zhes su brjod pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:5828: gsang sgor zhugs nas byin ldan pa //
NK066(chu)001:5829: nye ba'i bsnyen pa zhes su brjod //
NK066(chu)001:5830: gang yang bar chad mi g.yel bar //
NK066(chu)001:5831: dam pa'i gzhung gnyis 'dzin pas na //
NK066(chu)001:5832: sgrub pa zhes su brjod pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:5834: sgrub pa chen por de brjod do //
NK066(chu)001:5836: de ltar lam sgrub sbyor ba gsum las /
NK066(chu)001:5837: 'dir sgrub pa dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'o //
NK066(chu)001:5841: bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5843: tshogs bsgrub kyi sngon du zhi khro gang byed kyi bsnyen pa byed pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:5844: 'dir lam mos bsgom ma yin nges rdzogs pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:5845: dang por lta ba gtan la phebs par byas nas
NK066(chu)001:5846: tshogs lam gyi rnal 'byor bzhi la brtan pa thob
NK066(chu)001:5849: de la spros pa mthar phyin pa //
NK066(chu)001:5850: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK066(chu)001:5851: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK066(chu)001:5852: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:5854: nges par legs pa'i dgos pa 'grub //
NK066(chu)001:5861: tshom bu gcig gsum lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring
NK066(chu)001:5862: bsdus gsum gang rung la brtan pa thob par bya
NK066(chu)001:5863: ba ste / phyag rgya gcig pa la phra rags gnyis su phye bas cho ga lnga'o //
NK066(chu)001:5866: dam tshig lta ba ting 'dzin dang //
NK066(chu)001:5867: byang chub sems dang snying rje ste //
NK066(chu)001:5868: lhag pa'i yo byad lnga rdzogs bya //
NK066(chu)001:5869: zhes lam gyi yo byad lnga'am /
NK066(chu)001:5875: glu tshig sgra ste sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad lnga'o //
NK066(chu)001:5876: yan lag gi lha dgu'i dbu rgyan ni rigs kyi
NK066(chu)001:5877: bdag po gcig gis bsdus pa'i phyir gcig tu brtsis
NK066(chu)001:5878: pas sngags kyi yan lag lnga ste /
NK066(chu)001:5880: yid skyob pa dang byin gyis rlob pa'i phyir sngags te lha'o //
NK066(chu)001:5882: gal te phyag rgya spros bcas la brtan pa thob dgos pa ltar na /
NK066(chu)001:5884: mkha' dkyil dwangs pa'i dbyings nyi zla //
NK066(chu)001:5885: zhes sogs phyag rgya gcig pa bsgom pa la sngon
NK066(chu)001:5886: du bya ba'i bsnyen par bshad pa dang 'gal lo
NK066(chu)001:5887: zhe na / de ni spar khab las /
NK066(chu)001:5889: nye ba'i lha bsgom pa rnams kyi dbang du gsungs
NK066(chu)001:5890: zhes pas bskyed rdzogs gnyis ka'i bsdus don lta bur
NK066(chu)001:5891: ston pa ste / bskyed rim ltar na /
NK066(chu)001:5892: lha yab yum zung 'brel du bsgoms pas sangs rgyas
NK066(chu)001:5893: kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad ma lus par bsgom par
NK066(chu)001:5894: 'gyur te rgyal ba thams cad gcig dang du ma'i
NK066(chu)001:5896: de skad du'ang rdzogs chen gyi rgyud bkra shis brtsegs pa'i dpal las /
NK066(chu)001:5897: bde gshegs gcig bsgom rgyal ba kun gyi ngang //
NK066(chu)001:5900: dbyings ye zung 'brel du bsgoms pas rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa bsgoms par 'gyur ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:5901: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa der 'dus pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:5903: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK066(chu)001:5904: zhes sogs rkang pa drug gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:5905: des na sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa kho na 'chad byed kyi gzhung yin par ma nges kyang /
NK066(chu)001:5906: t+aika rnams su skabs 'dir 'chad pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:5907: snying rje sgyu ma nas thod rgal 'byung mi srid
NK066(chu)001:5908: pa tshogs sgrub kyi sngon du phyag rgya gcig pa
NK066(chu)001:5910: 'chad bde ba la dgongs nas go rim bsdebs pa yin nam snyam du sems te /
NK066(chu)001:5911: snga rabs pa dag gis dpyad pa ma mthong ngo //
NK066(chu)001:5912: gnyis pa la bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:5913: lnga dang lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK066(chu)001:5914: zhes sogs kyis bstan par bzhed do //
NK066(chu)001:5915: de yang sgrub pa phyag bzhes kyis 'chad dgos pa'i phyir 'dir las khrigs cung zad bshad na /
NK066(chu)001:5916: he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:5917: dang po sa yi cho ga ste //
NK066(chu)001:5918: gnyis pa la ni sta gon gnas //
NK066(chu)001:5919: gsum pa 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK066(chu)001:5921: zhes pas phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pa'i sgrub pa pos /
NK066(chu)001:5922: nub dang por sa gzhi mnyam pa'i cho ga las sa bsrung ba yan chad bya /
NK066(chu)001:5924: bum pa la sogs pa'i yan lag rab gnas dang /
NK066(chu)001:5925: sgrub chen dang 'brel bar slob ma la dbang bskur na de'i lhag gnas dang /
NK066(chu)001:5926: rdo rje las rim dus bzung ba zhes tha snyad
NK066(chu)001:5927: mdzad pa'i lha sta gon gyi cho ga rnams bya'o
NK066(chu)001:5929: bshags pa bya zhing mtshams gcod pa /
NK066(chu)001:5931: dkyil 'khor bri zhing rgyan dgram pa /
NK066(chu)001:5932: nub dang po bsnyen pa'i bya ba la 'jug pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5933: dang po la bshags skong bya ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:5936: phyi bshags su dkon mchog mchod pa /
NK066(chu)001:5937: 'bum ste lnga'am dpang sdud sogs bka' klog pa /
NK066(chu)001:5941: lam 'phrang gso ba sogs rgyab rim ci 'grub bya /
NK066(chu)001:5943: nang bshags su ru chen bzhi'i bshags pa rnams byed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5946: phyi rol mchod pa'i las rdzogs te //
NK066(chu)001:5947: phyi bcad bsrung sgo rim bzhin bya //
NK066(chu)001:5949: yang dag rtsa ba las kyang /
NK066(chu)001:5950: 'byung po'i gtor ma btang nas kyang //
NK066(chu)001:5951: gsang ba'i don gyi las rnams bya //
NK066(chu)001:5952: zhes pas 'byung po rnams la gtor ma byed te bskrad nas mtshams gcad par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:5953: de yang phyag bzhes rgyas pa'i tshe mtshams dgu phrugs su gcod par mdzad kyang /
NK066(chu)001:5954: 'dir bsdus pa'i dbang du byas te /
NK066(chu)001:5959: sgrub khang gi phyi rol gom pa bdun cu'i sar
NK066(chu)001:5960: rgyal chen bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu'i tho gzug pas
NK066(chu)001:5961: phyogs so so'i gnas nas bar mtshams med par bsrung
NK066(chu)001:5962: bar bsam pa'o // de ltar yang he ru ka gal po las /
NK066(chu)001:5963: phyogs bzhir tho bzhi btsugs nas kyang //
NK066(chu)001:5964: rgyal po chen po sde bzhi la //
NK066(chu)001:5965: phyi mtshams gcad pa'i phrin las bcol //
NK066(chu)001:5966: phyi mtshams bsrung bar zhal bzhes pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:5967: mthu chen phyogs skyong 'khor bcas la //
NK066(chu)001:5968: gtor ma cha re byin nas kyang //
NK066(chu)001:5969: phyi mtshams bsrung ba'i phrin las bcol //
NK066(chu)001:5974: khro bcus bgegs la phur bu gdab pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5976: sngon gsang kyi sgor zhugs kyang bka' bsgo log pas
NK066(chu)001:5977: dam tshig can la gnod pa'i dam srir gyur pa
NK066(chu)001:5978: ste / de sngon dam 'dres zin pa'i phyir mtshams kyi sbyor ba gzhan gyis mi thub pas /
NK066(chu)001:5979: ra sog la ling+ga bris te sgrub khang gi them
NK066(chu)001:5980: pa'i phyi rol du mnan cing bro brdungs pas bskal
NK066(chu)001:5981: mtha'i bar du ldang mi nus par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5983: rkyen gyi bar chad bsal ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:5984: gsang ba'i man ngag spyad pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:5985: 'jug sred dam sri gnan par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5988: ra sog la bris pa'i bgegs ling gi snying gar
NK066(chu)001:5989: phur bu btab ste gshin rje'i gnas su bskrad par
NK066(chu)001:5990: bsam zhing / sgo'i 'og tu mgo mthur bstan gyis gdags so //
NK066(chu)001:5991: de dang thad ka'i sgo gong du ye shes lha'i sgo byang ni /
NK066(chu)001:5992: lug gam rkyang gi sog pa la /
NK066(chu)001:5993: gshin rje gshed kyi sku bris pa gdags pas ji
NK066(chu)001:5994: srid sgrub pa ma thon gyi bar du phyi'i bar
NK066(chu)001:5995: gcod nang dang / nang gi dngos grub phyir mi gtong ba'i phrin las byed par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:5996: 'dir he ru ka gal po las /
NK066(chu)001:5997: chos kyi rgyal po bdud rtsi yi //
NK066(chu)001:5998: phyi nang sgo byang gdags par bya //
NK066(chu)001:5999: zhes gsungs pa ltar 'khyil ba'i sgo byang btags kyang 'gal bar ma mthong ngo //
NK066(chu)001:6001: rgyal po btson du bcug pas dmangs cham la phebs pa ltar /
NK066(chu)001:6002: bgegs phran rnams ldang mi nus pa'i ched du bgegs
NK066(chu)001:6003: kyi gtso bo phyogs skyong bcu la phur bu gdab
NK066(chu)001:6004: par bya ste / byug bdug gis phur bu gzi byin bskyed nas /
NK066(chu)001:6005: bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje'i nga rgyal gyis phur bu rnams khro bcu yab yum du bskyed la /
NK066(chu)001:6006: ta ki r+aa dzas phyogs skyong bcu bkug nas gdan
NK066(chu)001:6007: du bting ba la bgegs mthar byed kyis phur bu
NK066(chu)001:6008: btab pas gser gyi sa gzhi la sbrags par bsam
NK066(chu)001:6009: zhing ye shes kyi khro bcu phab nas mchod bstod
NK066(chu)001:6011: de ltar yang lam rim las /
NK066(chu)001:6012: 'jigs byed dbang du bdag zhugs nas //
NK066(chu)001:6013: khro bo khro mo 'khor du bya //
NK066(chu)001:6014: gdan du gzir zhing phur bus gdab //
NK066(chu)001:6015: rang bzhin phab la mchod bstod de //
NK066(chu)001:6016: bar chad ting 'dzin mchog gis bzlog /
NK066(chu)001:6018: gal te sa bsrung ba'i tshe phyogs skyong phur gdab byas grub pa zhig na /
NK066(chu)001:6019: 'dir sngar btab pa'i phur bu rnams la phrin las
NK066(chu)001:6020: bskul ba rigs bar mthong zhes rje bla mas gsung
NK066(chu)001:6021: ba ltar legs pas bskyar nas gdab mi dgos so
NK066(chu)001:6023: mtshan med rnam par mi rtog pa'i mtshams te /
NK066(chu)001:6025: mtshams med pa la mtshams bcad pa //
NK066(chu)001:6029: phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshams gcod tshar ba'i rjes thog tu /
NK066(chu)001:6032: phyi nang gsang ba bsrung bya ste //
NK066(chu)001:6033: srin po'i rgyal po tshul bzhin mnan //
NK066(chu)001:6035: de yang ma tram r+au dra'i gzugs bcas te /
NK066(chu)001:6036: dgug bsgral spar la rol pa'i bros mnan cing sbyangs
NK066(chu)001:6037: te khog pa gzhal yas khang du byin gyis rlob
NK066(chu)001:6038: pa'o // 'di nyid mtshams kyi don du'ang 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:6039: r+au dra ni bgegs kyi rgyal po yin la /
NK066(chu)001:6040: de bsgral bas bgegs phran gzhan rnams kyis bar gcod bya bar mi nus pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6041: gsum pa dkyil 'khor bri zhing rgyan dgram pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:6042: thig tshon gyi cho ga dang ldan pas dkyil 'khor
NK066(chu)001:6043: tshom bu gang bsgom gyi gzhung bzhin du bris nas
NK066(chu)001:6044: rab gnas dang / sbyin sreg bya /
NK066(chu)001:6045: de nas yo byad rnams byin gyis rlobs te sgrub rdzas dang /
NK066(chu)001:6047: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dgod rnams bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6049: so sor 'tshams pa'i gzugs brnyan bri //
NK066(chu)001:6050: rgyan dang mchod sogs 'khor ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:6053: thog mar gral phyag dang tshul phyag btsal nas khro bcu rol bas mtshams gcod de /
NK066(chu)001:6055: thun mong srung ba'i 'khor lo bya //
NK066(chu)001:6057: 'dir gang dang thun mong zhe na //
NK066(chu)001:6058: rje sgro phug pa ni bsnyen bsgrub bzhi ka'i thun mong dang /
NK066(chu)001:6059: lha rje glan tshom bu gsum ka'i thun mong gi mtshams su bzhed /
NK066(chu)001:6060: 'dir zhi khro gnyis ka'i thun mong gi mtshams su bshad kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK066(chu)001:6061: de nas brda sgo dbye ba sogs bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6063: snod bcud gzhal yas khang lha'i rang bzhin du gsal btab ste /
NK066(chu)001:6064: ye shes bzhi'i sgo nas zhugs par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6066: lha dang gzhal yas khang de yang yul gud na yod pa ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:6067: rang gi rig pa nyid dkyil 'khor du shar ba
NK066(chu)001:6068: la yul rig gnyis su med par mjal ba brda'i
NK066(chu)001:6069: phyag gis mtshon cing ngo mtshar bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6073: bdag nyid ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyis dpung
NK066(chu)001:6074: gi ru dar ltar rang gi sde tshan du shes
NK066(chu)001:6075: par 'gyur pa la sogs pa'i dgos pas sgrub pa
NK066(chu)001:6076: po thams cad la byugs rtsi gsum gyi rtags gdab
NK066(chu)001:6079: dang po ting nge 'dzin gsum bsgom /
NK066(chu)001:6080: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor tshom bu gang bsgom dang bstun pa la bsgom /
NK066(chu)001:6083: rnal 'byor thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK066(chu)001:6084: de bzhin gshegs dang yum du bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:6085: sems dpa' sems ma nyid du bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:6086: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK066(chu)001:6087: ting 'dzin yang dag so sor gsal //
NK066(chu)001:6089: rnal 'byor pho mo dang lha yab yum brang sprad de bye brag tu bsgom pa'am /
NK066(chu)001:6090: yang na rnal 'byor pa spyis tshom bu spyir bsgom pa gang mos su bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:6093: spyi'am yang na re re zhing //
NK066(chu)001:6094: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:6098: ye shes pa dbab drang bstim la mchod cing bstod nas bsnyen pa bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6100: byin rlob dbang dang ldan byas nas //
NK066(chu)001:6101: rang bzhin gnas nas dbab bya ste //
NK066(chu)001:6102: gzhug cing brtan byas rim par mchod //
NK066(chu)001:6103: rdzogs nas bstod de bsnyen pa bya /
NK066(chu)001:6105: de'ang nub dang po'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:6107: ye shes mdun du lhag pa la //
NK066(chu)001:6108: bzlas pa gsal ba gsum gyis bya //
NK066(chu)001:6112: bar gyi 'phro 'du ste gsal ba gsum gyi sgo nas man ngag bzhin bzla ba ste //
NK066(chu)001:6114: 'od zer dkar po phar 'phros pas sgrib pa sbyong zhig bar bskul /
NK066(chu)001:6115: tshur 'dus nas bdag gi sgrib pa sbyangs nas dngos
NK066(chu)001:6116: grub kyi snod rung du byas par bsam la 'dzab
NK066(chu)001:6117: bzla zhing / mjug tu dkyil 'khor phye ba de nyid rang la bstim pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6118: de ltar yang snga ma las /
NK066(chu)001:6120: 'dun par bskul dang snod byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:6128: mchod pa phyi ma dang mtshams sbyar stan byin gyis brlabs te 'dug /
NK066(chu)001:6129: 'gro na phreng ba khro zhal du byin gyis rlobs la gdan bsrung /
NK066(chu)001:6130: dus drug tu bar chad kyi nyul le brtags la /
NK066(chu)001:6131: de dag so so'i gnyen po bskul ba la sogs pas bzlog cing /
NK066(chu)001:6132: dus rtag tu lha'i nga rgyal dang ma bral ba bya ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:6134: zin nas sdud de rnal 'byor tshogs //
NK066(chu)001:6135: tshul bzhin mchod pa'i phrin las bya //
NK066(chu)001:6136: nang nub mkha' 'gro lhag ma sbyin //
NK066(chu)001:6137: bar chad bzlog cing bsnyen pa bya //
NK066(chu)001:6139: 'dir sgrol g.yung gnyis kyi t+ai kar /
NK066(chu)001:6140: shom yan lag dang 'brel ba tsam la bsnyen par
NK066(chu)001:6141: mdzad nas nub dang po'i bsnyen pa mi bzhed kyang
NK066(chu)001:6143: 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:6144: zhes pa'i lung ltar mkhas pa rog sogs /
NK066(chu)001:6145: snga rabs dag gi las tho las 'byung ba ltar byas pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6146: gzhan du sgrub pa ji tsam byed pa'i 'go 'dzin
NK066(chu)001:6147: gyi nub dang po nas nye bsnyen la bzhed pa'i
NK066(chu)001:6148: phyogs kyang mi rigs pa ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:6149: lam rim gyi khro bo'i skabs su /
NK066(chu)001:6150: de nas gnyis par rgyan rnams dang //
NK066(chu)001:6153: rim pa shom dang 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:6154: zhes sogs kyis 'grub bam snyam ste dpyad par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:6156: cho ga'i rnam gzhag gzhan rnams sngar dang mthun pa las /
NK066(chu)001:6157: khyad par dus drug gam bzhir tshogs dang gtor ma gtong /
NK066(chu)001:6160: dkar po phar spros pas bskul ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6161: dmar po tshur bsdu bas dngos grub kyi snod rung du bya ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6162: dus ni ji tsam bsgrub pa'i phyed do //
NK066(chu)001:6164: cho ga gzhan nye bsnyen ltar las /
NK066(chu)001:6165: 'dzab kyi 'phro 'du'i dus su 'od zer dmar po
NK066(chu)001:6166: spros pas dngos grub bskul ba dang 'dus pas sku
NK066(chu)001:6167: gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam ste /
NK066(chu)001:6169: de ltar bsnyen bsgrub kyi dus su tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor sgom thabs la /
NK066(chu)001:6174: rdo rje'i rigs su thams cad dkyil //
NK066(chu)001:6176: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la rang gi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum bzhi dang /
NK066(chu)001:6177: sgo ba yab yum bzhi ste lha tshogs zung dgu ya bco brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:6178: de ltar na dkyil 'khor bsdus pa dang khyad par med par thal lo zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:6179: lha grangs la khyad par med kyang lha ngo la khyad par yod pa'i phyir skyon med de /
NK066(chu)001:6180: dkyil 'khor bsdus pa ni rdor sems yab yum la rgyal ba rigs bzhis bskor ba yin la /
NK066(chu)001:6181: 'dir ni rigs chung gi sems dpa' bzhis bskor ba'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:6183: yang na sku gsung thugs nyid de //
NK066(chu)001:6184: zhes sogs kyis dbus su rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK066(chu)001:6186: nub tu mtha' yas te gtso bo yab yum zung gsum la /
NK066(chu)001:6187: rang rang gi rigs chung gi sems dpa' yab yum
NK066(chu)001:6188: zung bzhi bzhis bskor bas zung lnga tshan gsum la
NK066(chu)001:6189: ya sum cu / de'i steng du mngon rtogs las /
NK066(chu)001:6190: sgo ba yab yum brgyad bsnan te so brgyad du bshad /
NK066(chu)001:6191: spar khab las zhi ba sum cu'i steng du steng
NK066(chu)001:6192: 'og ma gtogs pa'i khro bo yab yum zung brgyad
NK066(chu)001:6193: bsnan te zhe drug tu bshad do //
NK066(chu)001:6195: sngags 'chang dngos grub yang dag ni //
NK066(chu)001:6197: gtso bo rigs lnga yab yum la so so'i rigs
NK066(chu)001:6198: chung gi sems dpa' yab yum brgyad brgyad kyis bskor
NK066(chu)001:6200: khro bcu yab yum nyi shu ste bdun cu'o //
NK066(chu)001:6202: khro bo khro mo'i tshogs chen po //
NK066(chu)001:6203: zhes sogs kyi skabs su khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la'ang tshom bu gsum bsgres nas ston te /
NK066(chu)001:6206: gsum dang lnga ru bsgom par bya //
NK066(chu)001:6208: de yang tshom bu gcig pa la lha bdun cu rtsa brgyad de /
NK066(chu)001:6209: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum la rigs chung gi khro bo yab yum brgyad kyis bskor ba bcu /
NK066(chu)001:6210: pho nya goo r+ai ma brgyad /
NK066(chu)001:6212: bka' nyan sgo ma bzhi ste /
NK066(chu)001:6214: ci bgyi'i dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK066(chu)001:6215: sogs khongs nas khro bcu yab yum nyi shu rnams so //
NK066(chu)001:6216: tshom bu gsum pa la sngar gyi steng du //
NK066(chu)001:6217: shar du bud+d+ha he ru ka dang /
NK066(chu)001:6218: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka gnyis la rang rang
NK066(chu)001:6219: gi rigs chung dang bcas pas bcu bcu ste nyi
NK066(chu)001:6220: shu bsnan pas go brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:6222: de dag gi khar lho byang du rat+na dang /
NK066(chu)001:6223: karma he ru ka rigs chung dang bcas pa nyi shu bsnan pas lha brgya dang bco brgyad do //
NK066(chu)001:6225: 'dir bstan gyi tshom bu dang sngar smos pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi khyad par gang zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:6226: bzhed pa mi mthun te zur tsho snga rabs pa phal cher na re /
NK066(chu)001:6227: mi grangs nges med kyi lha grangs nges pa bsgom pa dkyil 'khor /
NK066(chu)001:6228: mi grangs nges can gyis lha grangs nges can bsgom pa tshom bu'o gsungs pa mi 'thad de /
NK066(chu)001:6229: tshom bu gcig pa la brtan pa thob nas gsum
NK066(chu)001:6230: pa bsgom pa'i tshe mi grangs mang du ma song
NK066(chu)001:6231: la lha grangs mang du song ba'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6232: yang dam pa sh+aaka rgyal na re //
NK066(chu)001:6233: rigs chung gis rgyas pa'ang yod la /
NK066(chu)001:6234: ma rgyas pa'ang yod pa dkyil 'khor /
NK066(chu)001:6235: rang rang gi rigs chung gis rgyas pa tshom bu'o gsungs /
NK066(chu)001:6237: rigs chung gis rgyas pa yod pa'i dkyil 'khor rgyas pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6238: tshom bu lnga pa gnyis khyad par mi phyed do //
NK066(chu)001:6240: gnas skabs su gtso bo nges pa tshom bu /
NK066(chu)001:6241: ma nges pa dkyil 'khor ro gsung /
NK066(chu)001:6242: de ltar na tshom bu gcig pa nya da dkyil 'khor du thal /
NK066(chu)001:6243: gnas skabs su gtso bo nges pa rdo rje'i rigs kyis byed pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6244: yang rje sgro phug pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:6246: bsgom bya lha'i khyad par gnyis su bzhed /
NK066(chu)001:6248: lha dang rnal 'byor pa brang sprad de bsgom pa'i tshom bu //
NK066(chu)001:6249: rnal 'byor pa pho mo gang rung gcig gis lha'i
NK066(chu)001:6250: dkyil 'khor byung tshogs su bsgom pa dkyil 'khor ro
NK066(chu)001:6252: tshom bu gcig na gtso bo gcig yin pa sogs gtso bo dbri bsnan du ston pa tshom bu /
NK066(chu)001:6253: rnam grangs byung tshogs su ston pa 'khor ro //
NK066(chu)001:6254: yang na rigs 'gyur kyang ye shes mi 'gyur ba tshom bu /
NK066(chu)001:6255: rigs dang ye shes gnyis ka 'gyur ba dkyil 'khor ro //
NK066(chu)001:6256: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyang phyogs re nas gzhag tu btub mod kyi /
NK066(chu)001:6258: gnyal sangs rgyas grags kyi bzhed pa ltar /
NK066(chu)001:6259: gtso bo rigs chung dang bcas pa rang gi rigs su nges pa tshom bu /
NK066(chu)001:6260: gtso bo rigs chung yang spyi'i rigs su nges pa
NK066(chu)001:6261: dkyil 'khor zhes gsungs pa nyid legs par mngon te
NK066(chu)001:6262: / dkyil 'khor ni rnam snang sogs rigs bzhi'i gtso
NK066(chu)001:6263: bo rdo rje'i rigs gcig gis bsdus pas rigs tha
NK066(chu)001:6264: dad kyi gtso bo gcig tu gyur pa'i phyir dang
NK066(chu)001:6265: / / tshom bu ni rang gi rigs chung gis
NK066(chu)001:6266: bye brag tu bskor bas rigs tha mi dad kyi
NK066(chu)001:6267: gtso bo so sos byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:6268: 'o na rang gi rigs chung gis bye brag tu bskor ba yod pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6269: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa yang tshom bur thal zhe na khyab pa med de /
NK066(chu)001:6270: dkyil 'khor rgyas pa la so so'i rigs chung gis
NK066(chu)001:6271: bskor kyang spyi'i gtso bo gcig gis byed pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:6273: rdo rje sems dpa' dkyil nyid de //
NK066(chu)001:6274: rigs bzhi lha dang lha mo 'khor //
NK066(chu)001:6277: de ltar bsgrubs pa'i zhag grangs ji skad bshad pa ltar tshang nas /
NK066(chu)001:6280: rdzas zhag tu khol ba sogs grub pa'i rtags mtshan yid ches pa byung ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6281: nub tha ma la dngos grub blang ba'i cho ga bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6283: phyir rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg bya //
NK066(chu)001:6288: 'dzab kyi dus su 'od zer phar mi spro bar tshur sdud pa kho na ste /
NK066(chu)001:6289: 'od zer mthing ga dngos grub kyi rang bzhin du
NK066(chu)001:6290: bsdus nas dngos grub kyi rdzas dang sgrub pa po
NK066(chu)001:6291: rnams kyi rgyud la bstim pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6294: de yang dngos grub blang ba dngos la /
NK066(chu)001:6297: yum gyi mkha' nas blang ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6299: lha spyi dang bye brag so sor bskul ba'i sgo
NK066(chu)001:6300: nas stong tshig gi mchod pa dang 'brel bar len
NK066(chu)001:6301: pa ste / lha rnams spyan drangs nas mchod la dngos grub bdag la bstim pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6303: bskul tshig gi sgo nas blang zhing dngos grub kyi rdzas la rol pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6305: sbyor mchod dang 'brel bar bla ma'i man ngag gis blang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:6308: phyi rol du gtor ma btang /
NK066(chu)001:6310: spyod lam rgyun ting gis rgyas gdab /
NK066(chu)001:6313: zhib par bla ma dam pa'i zhal dang sgrub byang las shes par 'gyur la /
NK066(chu)001:6314: 'dir gzhung 'chad pa'i dbang du byas te sbyor sgrol
NK066(chu)001:6315: gyi mchod pa gnyis cung zad bshad na gsum ste
NK066(chu)001:6317: k+aa li sgrol ba'i mchod pa /
NK066(chu)001:6318: de gnyis spyad byar sgrub pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6319: dang po la'ang gang la sbyor ba'i yul /
NK066(chu)001:6321: ci'i phyir sbyor ba'i dgos pa dang gsum /
NK066(chu)001:6326: rnal 'byor pa dgongs spyod stobs chen dang po gnyis dngos dang /
NK066(chu)001:6328: mi'i bu mo yin la stobs chung na gsum ka mi'i bu mo'o //
NK066(chu)001:6329: de gsum gyi khyad par rim pa ltar /
NK066(chu)001:6334: rtsa'i sgo nas rtsa dung can ma dang /
NK066(chu)001:6338: nyi zla gnyis ka 'dzag pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6344: rang bde ba'i sbyor thabs shes pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6345: bye brag tu slob dpon sgeg pas rigs brgyad du bshad de /
NK066(chu)001:6347: pad can dung can ri mo can //
NK066(chu)001:6348: ba glang can dang lcug phran dang //
NK066(chu)001:6349: sdong gcig mes reg phyal pa brgyad //
NK066(chu)001:6351: de rnams kyi mtshan kyang spyi tsam du snga ma las /
NK066(chu)001:6352: mnyen drang sked ring stod smad phyed //
NK066(chu)001:6353: yan lag phra 'jam tshigs mig zlum //
NK066(chu)001:6354: dpral ba'i dbyes phyed smin dkyus ring //
NK066(chu)001:6356: mchu zheng gnyis ka'i 'bring du bshad //
NK066(chu)001:6357: lus la chu klung ga bur dri //
NK066(chu)001:6358: gsang thub shes rab spyod pa dal //
NK066(chu)001:6359: dad ldan 'grogs shing dang ba che //
NK066(chu)001:6360: gsang ba'i gnas su spyad par bya //
NK066(chu)001:6362: 'o na mtshan bzang ngan phye ste /
NK066(chu)001:6363: ngan pa ni rnam pa kun tu spang bya kho na'o snyam na ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:6364: dabye'am yang na mi dbye bar /
NK066(chu)001:6365: zhes pas rnal 'byor pa nus pa chung na dbye la che na mi dbye bar rol /
NK066(chu)001:6369: dbye ba'am dbang drag mi dbye bar //
NK066(chu)001:6370: zhes las bzhi'i gzungs ma'i khyad par du bshad /
NK066(chu)001:6371: don la sgrub pa dang phrin las kyi gzungs ma ji ltar bshad pa ltar rigs dbye ba'am /
NK066(chu)001:6372: yang na ma phye yang rung ste dang pas chags
NK066(chu)001:6373: na bud med thams cad snying rje'i yul du mnyam
NK066(chu)001:6374: par gzung bya yin pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6375: shes rab kyi rang bzhin dang gnas su'ang mnyam par gzhag pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6378: dbang bskur dam 'bog chos gsum bshad //
NK066(chu)001:6379: lus la rigs lnga'i rdul tshon dgye //
NK066(chu)001:6380: thabs la mkhas pas skabs kyis sbyar //
NK066(chu)001:6381: zhes pa'i don sbyor ba dus kyi bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i sgo nas nyams su blang ste /
NK066(chu)001:6382: rdo rje slob dpon gyis yum mtshan ldan de 'khor khang nang mar khrid la /
NK066(chu)001:6387: 'dod pa'i bstan bcos kyis bde ba rgyas par byed pa ni bsnyen pa /
NK066(chu)001:6388: yab yum lhar bskyed la mkha' gsang rdo rje dang pad+mora byin gyis rlob /
NK066(chu)001:6389: yum gyi pad+ma'i dbus su tshom bu gang yin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK066(chu)001:6390: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba ni nye bsnyen /
NK066(chu)001:6391: de nas phyag rgya bzhis gnyis med du rol /
NK066(chu)001:6392: 'khor lo bzhir ye shes ngos bzung //
NK066(chu)001:6393: rtog tshogs sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor du gnas pa nyid bde ba'i ros tshim par bya /
NK066(chu)001:6394: bde ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu'i bde gshegs ma lus pa mchod cing spyan drangs /
NK066(chu)001:6395: de rnams kyi sbyor mtshams nas babs pa'i byang sems bdag gi spyi bo nas zhugs /
NK066(chu)001:6396: 'khor lo bzhi brgyud de yum gyi mkha' la 'bebs pa ni sgrub pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6398: zhes sogs sh+lo ka gcig gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:6399: de la bla ma'i man ngag gis dngos grub blang ste /
NK066(chu)001:6400: sgrub pa nyi zla snying po de //
NK066(chu)001:6401: dkyil 'khor rdo rje lce yis blang //
NK066(chu)001:6402: zhes pas nub tha ma'i tho rengs kyi dus su
NK066(chu)001:6403: yab kyi rdo rje'i lces blangs te ldog dgram gyi
NK066(chu)001:6404: thabs kyis rang gnas su sleb pas zag med rig
NK066(chu)001:6405: 'dzin la sbyor ba sgrub chen no //
NK066(chu)001:6409: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:6410: zhes pas mchog gi dngos grub 'grub par bstan no //
NK066(chu)001:6411: de ganya sa kyi khyad par la spar khab tu /
NK066(chu)001:6412: snga ma lce rdo rje rtse lnga par bsgoms nas blangs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK066(chu)001:6413: phyi ma gsang ba'i rdo rjes blangs pa'i yon tan du gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:6414: gnyis pa sgrol ba la gang bsgral ba'i yul /
NK066(chu)001:6416: gang gis sgrol ba'i gang zag /
NK066(chu)001:6417: gang gi tshe sgrol ba'i dus /
NK066(chu)001:6419: ci'i phyir bsgral ba'i dgos ched do //
NK066(chu)001:6421: zhing gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK066(chu)001:6422: zhes pa ste de la gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:6423: mchog bkra shis dag pa'i zhing dang /
NK066(chu)001:6424: mchog phran thugs rjes bzung ba'i zhing ngo //
NK066(chu)001:6426: bram ze skye ba bdun pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6427: de'i lus de dngos grub kyi rdzas khyad par can yin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6428: gzhan phan gyi blos gtong ba la bskul ba lta bu'o //
NK066(chu)001:6431: dkon mchog slob dpon sku dgra gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:6432: dam nyams log dang 'khus pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:6434: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can //
NK066(chu)001:6435: ngan song gsum dang bcu po ni //
NK066(chu)001:6436: rnal 'byor kun gyis dang du blang //
NK066(chu)001:6437: zhes pa'i bsgral bya bcu ni snying rje'i zhing ste /
NK066(chu)001:6438: rje bla ma'i gter byon 'joms byed las /
NK066(chu)001:6439: e ma khams gsum sems can rnamasah ma rtogs 'khrul
NK066(chu)001:6440: pa snying re rjeh snying rjes bsgral ba'i dam tshig
NK066(chu)001:6441: nih gsad cing mnan pa ma yin teh zhes so
NK066(chu)001:6442: // yang na mchog ni zhing bcu las mi bdun dang /
NK066(chu)001:6443: mchog phran ni ngan song gsum mo //
NK066(chu)001:6444: yang mchog ni bsgral bya gang yin dang /
NK066(chu)001:6445: mchog phran ni tsa ra dang shel chen la bkug nas sgrol ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6448: mchog phran ni bam la sogs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6451: 'khor khang nang mar chos 'byung gi dbus su nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor la bzhag nas bsgral te /
NK066(chu)001:6452: he ru ka gal po las /
NK066(chu)001:6453: kha t+w+aam brgyab pas e nang du //
NK066(chu)001:6454: nyi zla'i steng du gan rkyal bsgyel //
NK066(chu)001:6457: sgrol ba mkhas pa'i slob dpon dang king gis so //
NK066(chu)001:6459: rang bzhin gyis sgrol ba'i lta ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6460: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol ba'i nyams dang /
NK066(chu)001:6461: dbang po yul dus kyis sgrol ba'i spyod pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6462: thabs chen pos sgrol ba'i gdams ngag dang /
NK066(chu)001:6463: mngon du phyung bas sgrol ba'i mdzad spyod la mkhas pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6464: king ka ra la gsum ste /
NK066(chu)001:6468: de gsum rim pa ltar bsgral bya 'dzin pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6472: tshogs bsgrub kyi nub mtha' ma'i nam gung gi dus su'o //
NK066(chu)001:6474: nga rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:6479: las gzhung gi 'dzab yan chad grub pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:6480: 'dzin king gis lag par dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod nas bsgral bya bzung ste /
NK066(chu)001:6481: 'khor khang nang mar slob dpon gyi drung du khrid nas las phrin gdags /
NK066(chu)001:6483: bi shwa'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad /
NK066(chu)001:6484: bsgral bya'i spyi bor ngan song sbyong ba'i lha bskyed /
NK066(chu)001:6485: de'i sngags kyis btab pa'i yungs kar gyis spyi bo nas mar brabs pas sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK066(chu)001:6486: b+ha ga ba ti'i sngags kyis 'gro drug tu skye ba'i sgo dgag go //
NK066(chu)001:6487: gnyis pa bsgral ba dngos la /
NK066(chu)001:6490: shes pa chos nyid du dang /
NK066(chu)001:6492: rdo rje sems dpa' mtshan yongs su rdzogs pa'i sa la dang /
NK066(chu)001:6494: phung po dur khrod du bsgral ba dang bdun /
NK066(chu)001:6496: bdag nyid dpal chen po'i nga rgyal gyis /
NK066(chu)001:6497: bsgral bya'i lus de 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtshor
NK066(chu)001:6498: dmigs la thod rlon gyin rgya dang ma h+aa rak+ta'i
NK066(chu)001:6499: sngags kyis lhag med du gsol bar bsam pa ste
NK066(chu)001:6500: / 'khor ba skye ba'i rgyu spyir dug lnga dang khyad par 'dod chags yin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6502: rigs drug gi sa bon dang /
NK066(chu)001:6503: gnyen po bkod la 'ju 'dul gyis ngan 'gro'i sgo bkag pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6504: gnas lngar rigs drug gi sa bon spyi bor gnyis dang gzhan rnams su re re dgod /
NK066(chu)001:6505: de'ang pho mo'i dbang gi sa bon re re'ang gnyis gnyis so //
NK066(chu)001:6508: +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa lnga po re re'ang gnyis gnyis sa bon so so'i steng du bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6510: mas nas yar zhu ste rkang mthil gnyis kyi duh'i steng gi h+aa gnyis mer 'bar bas duhbasrega /
NK066(chu)001:6511: de'i 'od kyis dmyal ba'i 'jig rten khyab pas /
NK066(chu)001:6512: der gnas pa'i sems can rnams kyi ngag sgrib sbyangs /
NK066(chu)001:6513: tshur 'dus pa las ral gri dang dril bur gyur /
NK066(chu)001:6514: de'i 'od kyis yid sgrib sbyangs nas kyis dmya 'dus
NK066(chu)001:6515: pas don grub yab yum gyi sku phra mor gyur
NK066(chu)001:6516: / de las kyang 'phros pa'i 'od dmya la ba pa'i lus sgrib sbyangs /
NK066(chu)001:6517: slar 'dus pa las sku che zhing gzi brjid dang ldan par bsams la /
NK066(chu)001:6522: las rigs kyi thugs dam bskangs shing /
NK066(chu)001:6523: dngos grub thob par mos la /
NK066(chu)001:6524: don grub yab yum 'od du zhu ste lte ba'i s+w+aa la thim par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6525: de bzhin du bsreg sbyang gi bya ba gzhan rnams la'ang 'gre shes par byas te /
NK066(chu)001:6526: lte bar rin 'byung gis yi dwags /
NK066(chu)001:6527: snying gar mi bskyod pas mi /
NK066(chu)001:6528: mgrin par mtha' yas kyis byol song //
NK066(chu)001:6529: spyi bor rnam snang gis lha dang lha min sbyang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:6531: king gis bsgral bya la bdud rtsi blud /
NK066(chu)001:6533: dkyil 'khor gyi lho phyogs su thal chen gyis drag po'i dkyil 'khor gru gsum pa bri /
NK066(chu)001:6534: e ram gyis drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed de /
NK066(chu)001:6535: a ma las nyi zla'i gdan la /
NK066(chu)001:6536: kha t+w+aam ka'i rgyas 'khor ba ru bzlog gi tshul du /
NK066(chu)001:6538: rkang pa byang shar mtshams su bstan te gan rkyal
NK066(chu)001:6539: du bsgyel ba'i snying gar rdo rje gnan la bzhag
NK066(chu)001:6540: / de nas kun rtags kyi rtog pa zil gyis
NK066(chu)001:6541: gnon pa'i phyir sgrol byed slob dpon dpal chen po
NK066(chu)001:6542: / / bdag 'dzin gsum rtsad nas gcod pa'i phyir bsgral bya r+au dra /
NK066(chu)001:6543: 'khor ba'i ru bzlog pa'i phyir sgrol king t+aak+ki r+aa dzar nga rgyal byas la /
NK066(chu)001:6544: king gis gri 'jam dpal rnon por bskyed pas khog
NK066(chu)001:6545: pa gshags te ma rig pa'i rgya dral bar bsam
NK066(chu)001:6546: / lag sor la dpa' bo 'bru lnga bkod de
NK066(chu)001:6547: snying tshir gyis bzung bas rtsa chen bzhi la gnas
NK066(chu)001:6548: pa'i sa bon drug gnyid dang bcas pa 'bru lnga'i
NK066(chu)001:6549: 'od kyis bsregs pas sgrib pa dag ste h+aum yig
NK066(chu)001:6550: / drug tu bsgyur / de yang rang rig pa'i
NK066(chu)001:6551: ye shes su gcig pa'i phyir h+aum dkar po gcig
NK066(chu)001:6552: tu gyur pa bsgom pa ni shes pa chos nyid
NK066(chu)001:6553: / drug tu bsgyur / du bsgral ba'o // bzhi pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:6554: de dung phor du bcug nas slob dpon la gtad pas /
NK066(chu)001:6555: dpal chen po'i shangs bug g.yon nas rngubs te drangs /
NK066(chu)001:6557: rdo rje'i lam nas yum gyi mkha' la phab pas gsang ba'ii dbyings su thim par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6559: h+aum yig de las cho ga gsum gyis rdor sems su bskyed la /
NK066(chu)001:6560: rigs bdag gis dbu brgyan par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6562: de a las zla dkyil gyi steng du bzhag la /
NK066(chu)001:6563: yam las rlung dkyil gyis btegs te 'og min du
NK066(chu)001:6564: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams su
NK066(chu)001:6565: phata kyis 'phangs la byang sems kyi dbang bskur nas
NK066(chu)001:6566: rigs nges pa'i sras su bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6568: phung po cha bzhir bgos la bdud rtsis bkru //
NK066(chu)001:6569: de nas pags par bsdus la dkyil 'khor gyi steng
NK066(chu)001:6570: du bzhag ste t+r+aam las rin po che'i mchod sdong
NK066(chu)001:6571: du rlob / stob king gis btegs nas zhi khro'i lha tshogs la stob pa dang bskang gso bya /
NK066(chu)001:6572: de nas bam la thig btab ste //
NK066(chu)001:6573: lha'i mchod rdzas dang sman gyi rtsa ba sogs bsres la phung po bshig /
NK066(chu)001:6575: slob dpon gyis smon lam gdab /
NK066(chu)001:6578: mched byings la gsang ste spyad par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:6581: ting 'dzin sngags dang phyag rgya rnams //
NK066(chu)001:6582: shin tu goms par dbang bskur te //
NK066(chu)001:6583: byang chub zhing du dgod par bya //
NK066(chu)001:6584: ting 'dzin sngags rgyas bag chags sbyangs //
NK066(chu)001:6585: rnam shes lhar bskyed dbang bskur 'phang //
NK066(chu)001:6586: ye shes tshogs kyang rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:6587: phung po byin rlob mchod par bsngo //
NK066(chu)001:6590: 'joms byed kyi lung snga ma'i 'phros kyang /
NK066(chu)001:6591: thugs rje thabs kyi sbyor ba yih phung po bsgral
NK066(chu)001:6592: ba'i zhing du byah rnam shes yul gyi mkha' la
NK066(chu)001:6593: sbah ye shes dpa' bor byin brlabs teh rig pa
NK066(chu)001:6594: chos kyi dbyings su 'aphangh khyod ni rgyal ba'i sras
NK066(chu)001:6597: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar pa'i thabs //
NK066(chu)001:6598: zhes pas bsgral bya las ngan gyi 'bras bus ngan
NK066(chu)001:6599: song du 'gro nges shing der gnas pa rnams bde
NK066(chu)001:6600: blag tu de las sgrol ba'i thabs rmad du byung
NK066(chu)001:6603: byang chub spyod 'phel sems can bde //
NK066(chu)001:6604: lha mnyes bdag gi dam skongs shing //
NK066(chu)001:6605: las ngan bar chad sdug yun thung //
NK066(chu)001:6606: rang gis bsag med ngan song las //
NK066(chu)001:6607: bde lam 'di las gzhan med do //
NK066(chu)001:6609: gal te ma bsgral ba'i nyes dmigs kyang 'joms byed las /
NK066(chu)001:6610: gang tshe 'di dag ma bsgral nah log rtog mun
NK066(chu)001:6611: pa 'phel ba dang bde gshegs bstan pa nyams par
NK066(chu)001:6612: 'agyurah zhes so // gsum pa sbyor sgrol gnyis spyad byar sgrub pa la /
NK066(chu)001:6614: de la rtsod pa spang ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6616: spyad bya sbyor sgrol gyi bya ba chos can /
NK066(chu)001:6617: spyad kyang spyod dus nyid nas nyes pas gos par mi 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:6618: rtogs goms kyi blo la ltos te don la rdul tsam yang byas pa med pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6620: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med de /
NK066(chu)001:6621: chos thams cad ye nas dag cing sgyu ma'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK066(chu)001:6622: 'dir de mngon du gyur pas 'dzin zhen med par spyad pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:6623: dper na sgyu ma'i skyes bus mig yor gyi gang
NK066(chu)001:6624: zag la sbyor sgrol gyi las brtsams pa bzhin no
NK066(chu)001:6626: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK066(chu)001:6627: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK066(chu)001:6628: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK066(chu)001:6629: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK066(chu)001:6631: ye shes rgyas pa las kyang /
NK066(chu)001:6632: ji ltar sgyu ma'i mkhan po dag /
NK066(chu)001:6633: rang gi sprul pa'i sgyu ma la //
NK066(chu)001:6634: dge dang mi dge 'du byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:6635: nyes pa gang gis mi gos ltar //
NK066(chu)001:6636: thabs la mkhas pas rnam par spyod //
NK066(chu)001:6641: spyad bya ma yin par thal /
NK066(chu)001:6642: 'khor bar 'ching zhing ngan 'gror ltung byed yin pa'i phyir te /
NK066(chu)001:6643: sbyor ba'i rnam smin gyis ro myags kyi dmyal ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6644: rgyu mthun mngal gyi srin bu /
NK066(chu)001:6645: sgrol ba'i rnam smin gyis yang sos dang rgyu mthun
NK066(chu)001:6646: las kyi srin por skye bar bshad pa'i phyir zhe
NK066(chu)001:6647: na / thams cad kyis thams cad du spyad bya
NK066(chu)001:6648: ma yin pa'am 'ga' zhig gi tshe spyad bya ma
NK066(chu)001:6649: na / yin te / 'khor bar lhung byed yin pa'i phyir zer /
NK066(chu)001:6651: byang chub sems dpa' rngon dang smad 'tshong du sprul pa'i thabs mkhas kyi mdzad pa'ang der thal /
NK066(chu)001:6655: byang chub sems dpa' 'dul dbang gis //
NK066(chu)001:6656: rngon dang smad 'tshong bstan pa'ang ltung //
NK066(chu)001:6658: gal te sems dpa' gzhan don du de spyod kyang mi ltung na ci 'gal te /
NK066(chu)001:6659: khyab pa ma grub zer na /
NK066(chu)001:6660: thams cad kyis thams cad du spyad bya ma yin pa'i dam bca' nyams so //
NK066(chu)001:6662: thabs kyis ma zin pas gsod sbyor tha mal du
NK066(chu)001:6663: spyod dam spyod du bcug na 'bras bu de ltar
NK066(chu)001:6664: 'byung ba bden kyang 'dir thabs kyis zin pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:6666: khe dregs spyod pas de min te //
NK066(chu)001:6667: thabs chen lam la gnas pa yi //
NK066(chu)001:6668: skyes bu kun gyis bya bar gsungs //
NK066(chu)001:6671: 'dzin zhen med par ji ltar spyad kyang /
NK066(chu)001:6672: las kyis gos par mi 'gyur ba ni rgyal ba'i bstan pa spyi'i phyag rgya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6674: rmi lam ni med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK066(chu)001:6675: de'i 'bras bu ni ma byas pa nyid do //
NK066(chu)001:6678: skye bo phal cher mgo mang bye ba gcod byed kyang //
NK066(chu)001:6679: 'gro kun sprul 'drar rab shes de la 'jigs pa med //
NK066(chu)001:6681: spyir sbyor sgrol la cha lngar gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:6683: 'dis ni rang bzhin sbyor sgrol dang //
NK066(chu)001:6684: dbang po yul dus sbyor sgrol dang //
NK066(chu)001:6685: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor sgrol dang //
NK066(chu)001:6686: thabs chen po yi sbyor sgrol dang //
NK066(chu)001:6691: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gnyis su med par rtogs pa ni sbyor ba /
NK066(chu)001:6692: des gnyis 'dzin gyi rtog pa las sgrol ba ni sgrol ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:6694: gnyis med dbyings su sbyor ba yin //
NK066(chu)001:6696: bdag nyid chen po rtogs pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:6697: dbyings su yang ni bsgral bar bya //
NK066(chu)001:6701: dbang po nang nas 'char ba yab ste /
NK066(chu)001:6702: lha yab yum gnyis med du sbyor ba ni sbyor ba /
NK066(chu)001:6703: des tha mal gyi rtog tshogs rang sar dag pas sgrol ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:6705: dbang po yul dus rig pa rnams //
NK066(chu)001:6706: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK066(chu)001:6709: bskyed rim pas bsgom bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6710: lha yab yum du bskyed nas rol pa ni sbyor ba /
NK066(chu)001:6711: bsgral bya'i rnam shes 'og min du spor ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni sgrol ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6713: rnam shes h+aum gis bsdus rngubs te //
NK066(chu)001:6714: 'og min bla med gnas mchog tu //
NK066(chu)001:6715: gtso bo dang ni gtso mo dang //
NK066(chu)001:6716: sems dpa' dang ni sems ma rnams //
NK066(chu)001:6717: sbyor ba'i lhums su phata kyis 'phang //
NK066(chu)001:6720: 'di'i le'u bco lnga par gsungs pa ltar sngon byung dpal chen po'i thabs kyi mdzad spyod de /
NK066(chu)001:6722: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NK066(chu)001:6723: pho bsgral dur khrod brgyad du byas //
NK066(chu)001:6724: mo rnams sbyar te slas su byas //
NK066(chu)001:6725: de bzhin thabs kyi mdzad spyod do //
NK066(chu)001:6728: tshogs bsgrub kyi dus su sbyor sgrol dngos su byed pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6729: lag len sngar bshad grub bo //
NK066(chu)001:6730: de gang zag ji lta bus bya zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:6731: lta ba rtogs shing snang byed kyi ting 'dzin dang
NK066(chu)001:6732: rlung sems la dbang thob pa'i rnal 'byor pas bya
NK066(chu)001:6736: de ltar tshogs bsgrub kyi tshe spyad bya'i yo byad lnga las /
NK066(chu)001:6737: bshad ma thag pa'i +aa li k+aa li dang //
NK066(chu)001:6738: gzhan yang zhi khro'i gos rgyan dang //
NK066(chu)001:6741: bro gar 'du 'phro'i yo byad rnams rang rig pa'i
NK066(chu)001:6742: ye shes kyi rang bzhin du shes par byas nas
NK066(chu)001:6743: ma chags pa'i tshul gyis lha mchod pa dang spyod
NK066(chu)001:6744: lam gyi dus thams cad du spyod pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6746: gsang sogs yo byad lnga po rnams //
NK066(chu)001:6747: rig phyir ma skyes ye shes gsal //
NK066(chu)001:6748: chos nyid ye shes rol bar bsgom //
NK066(chu)001:6750: mchod pa'am spyod lam thams cad du //
NK066(chu)001:6751: chas brgyad rgyan rnams bgo bya ste //
NK066(chu)001:6752: bza' btung rjes su mthun par spyad //
NK066(chu)001:6753: bro gar glu tshig ldan par bya //
NK066(chu)001:6755: gsum pa 'bras bu rig 'dzin 'grub pa'i dus bshad pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:6756: yang rab kyis zla ba drug /
NK066(chu)001:6758: 'bring lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:6759: tha mas kyang lo gcig dang zla ba bzhi na /
NK066(chu)001:6760: dbang po rno na tshe dbang dang /
NK066(chu)001:6761: rtul na rnam smin la sbyor te /
NK066(chu)001:6763: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK066(chu)001:6764: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK066(chu)001:6765: dbang bsgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK066(chu)001:6767: zhi ba'i tshogs bsgrub kyi dus so //
NK066(chu)001:6768: khro bo ni de las sgrub thag nye bas rab kyis zla ba gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:6769: 'bring gis zla ba gsum dang zhag drug /
NK066(chu)001:6770: tha mas kyang zla ba drug na 'grub ste //
NK066(chu)001:6772: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK066(chu)001:6773: drug cu dgu bcu rtsa drug tu //
NK066(chu)001:6776: 'dir zhi ba las khro bo 'grub thag nye ba ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:6778: khro bo bar chad nyung zhing spyod pa rlabs che bas dus myur ba yin gsungs /
NK066(chu)001:6780: zhib 'dzab 'thor zhing bar chod mang bas 'gor la
NK066(chu)001:6781: khro bo 'dzab 'dril ba dang bar chod nyung bas
NK066(chu)001:6783: de dag ni bar chad med pa'i lam du tshogs sgrub pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6784: smin par slob pa'i tshul lo //
NK066(chu)001:6785: gzhan du mos sgrub tsam byed par spro na //
NK066(chu)001:6786: zhag bcu gcig gi dbang du byas te /
NK066(chu)001:6789: gsum pa la phyi nang gi bshags pa dang mtshams gcod nas bzung /
NK066(chu)001:6790: dkyil 'khor rab gnas yan chad tshar ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6791: las gzhung bsrangs te bsnyen pa'i 'phro 'du bya /
NK066(chu)001:6792: de nas zhag drug gi dang po gsum la nya bsnyen dang /
NK066(chu)001:6793: phyi ma gsum la sgrub pa'i 'phro 'dus bzlas brjod bya /
NK066(chu)001:6794: zhag bdun pa la dngos grub len pa'i las la 'bad cing /
NK066(chu)001:6795: nam langs pa dang dbang bskur ba ni sgrub chen te /
NK066(chu)001:6796: cho ga'i rnam bzhag gzhan rnams sngar bshad ltar shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:6797: de yang dkyil 'khor ni lam gyi cha rkyen gyi
NK066(chu)001:6798: gtso bor gyur pa'i phyir 'dir rgyas par bshad pa
NK066(chu)001:6799: yin no // lnga pa skyon ni 'chad 'gyur gyi yon tan las bzlog pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:6801: de las bzlog pa'i skyon can bzhi //
NK066(chu)001:6804: dkyil 'khor brten pas rtogs pa'i ye shes 'phel ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6805: sdig sgrib 'byang zhing mtshan rtog 'grib pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6806: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i phan yon khyad par can gyi thabs su gyur pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6807: mthar thug 'bras bu 'grub pa'i rten du 'gyur ba'i phyir te /
NK066(chu)001:6811: bzhi pa rim pa bgrod pa dbang la drug las /
NK066(chu)001:6813: chos kyi rgyal po'i go 'phang rgyud la thob pa'i ched du ste /
NK066(chu)001:6814: de thob pa la sgrib pa 'joms shing nus pa
NK066(chu)001:6815: 'jog pa'i thabs 'dis rim par bgrod dgos pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:6816: / de ltar yang thugs thig las /
NK066(chu)001:6817: bdag gzhan don nus tshogs las 'grub //
NK066(chu)001:6818: byang dang chub par gyur pa sgyur //
NK066(chu)001:6819: de la de yod phyir nod bya //
NK066(chu)001:6822: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi'i yan lag gis thob bya'i nus
NK066(chu)001:6823: pa khyad par can te de nyid rgyud la 'jog
NK066(chu)001:6824: pa'i las kyi bdag nyid de /
NK066(chu)001:6826: rgyu gnyis rkyen bzhi yan lag bsnyad //
NK066(chu)001:6827: drug la gnas pa'i thob bya de //
NK066(chu)001:6828: ngo bo nyid ces rnam par bshad //
NK066(chu)001:6830: dper na 'jig rten du 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal
NK066(chu)001:6831: po byung ba'i tshe glang che nas srung gi bus
NK066(chu)001:6832: bum chu'i rgya rtags kyi dbang bskur ba bzhin no
NK066(chu)001:6834: a b+hi shiny+tsa'i sgra las mngon par gtor ba zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:6835: dngos su dri ma 'khrud pa tsam la 'jug cing /
NK066(chu)001:6836: brgyud nas des 'bras bu ye shes kyi nus pa khyad par can 'jog pas na dbang ste /
NK066(chu)001:6838: gang gis gang la gang bskur bas //
NK066(chu)001:6839: rgyud dag nus pa thob phyir dbang //
NK066(chu)001:6846: rten gyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgo nas dang /
NK066(chu)001:6847: gang gi tshe bskur ba dus kyi sgo nas dang /
NK066(chu)001:6848: mos pa tha dad pa'i sgo nas dbye ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6850: zag bcas kyi lam du dbang gsum gyi nus pa tsam 'jog pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6851: bar chad med pa'i lam du phal cher 'jog pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6852: zag med kyi lam du dngos su 'jog cing bskur ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:6853: lam gyi rim par bzhed pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6855: gang du dad dang brtson 'grus dang //
NK066(chu)001:6856: brtul zhugs gsum du ldan pa la //
NK066(chu)001:6857: sa bon 'jug dang nus bskyed nas //
NK066(chu)001:6858: bde ba'i dbang ni rim bzhin sbyin //
NK066(chu)001:6859: zhes pas nus pa 'jog tshul gsum po phan nus
NK066(chu)001:6860: zab dbang gsum gyi rim par bzhed pa'ang yod de
NK066(chu)001:6861: / gang ltar yang 'gal bar ma mthong ngo //
NK066(chu)001:6863: rgyud tshod dang sbyar ba'i dkyil 'khor bzhir 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:6864: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dang /
NK066(chu)001:6865: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dang /
NK066(chu)001:6867: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:6869: slob dpon rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis slob bu mthar
NK066(chu)001:6870: phyin pa'i lam pa la dbang bskur ba'i tshe ye
NK066(chu)001:6871: shes kyi snang ba las grub pa'i rang bzhin gyi
NK066(chu)001:6872: dkyil 'khor dang ye shes kyi lha mo la brten
NK066(chu)001:6873: par mdzad de / sngar le'u gnyis par bstan pa'i sngon byung gi dbang bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:6874: de ltar yang sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las /
NK066(chu)001:6875: rgyal ba kun gyi spyi gzugs des //
NK066(chu)001:6876: 'khor tshogs ye shes rgya mtsho la //
NK066(chu)001:6877: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor lhan cig tu //
NK066(chu)001:6878: ye shes lha mo la brten nas //
NK066(chu)001:6879: ye shes chen po'i dbang bskur bas //
NK066(chu)001:6880: gsang bdag rdo rje 'chang chen gyur //
NK066(chu)001:6883: slob dpon mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa la nye
NK066(chu)001:6884: ba lhun grub rig 'dzin gyis slob ma mthong bsgom
NK066(chu)001:6885: gnyis kyi rig 'dzin la lhag pa ting 'dzin dang
NK066(chu)001:6886: rig pa'i lha mo la brten nas dbang bskur te
NK066(chu)001:6888: dang po nas bzung bcu pa'i bar //
NK066(chu)001:6890: rig pa'i lha mo la brten nas //
NK066(chu)001:6891: ting 'dzin chu bos dbang bskur bas //
NK066(chu)001:6892: sa dang ye shes zhing khams dang //
NK066(chu)001:6895: sngon slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang bas mtsho ma pham
NK066(chu)001:6896: la thig btab nas rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK066(chu)001:6897: bstan te / dbas many+dzu sh+r+ai sogs la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:6898: slob dpon chen po pad+mas stag tshang seng phug tu
NK066(chu)001:6899: mtsho rgyal la phur pa'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha' dang
NK066(chu)001:6900: mnyam pa bstan nas dbang bskur ba lta bu'o //
NK066(chu)001:6901: de 'dra ba'i dkyil 'khor de la gzhan du sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes grags shing /
NK066(chu)001:6902: 'dir lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi gzugs brnyan zhes gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:6904: slob dpon mthar nye lam gnas pas //
NK066(chu)001:6905: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sum 'phro zhing //
NK066(chu)001:6906: sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor sogs //
NK066(chu)001:6907: rdo rje'i thig tshad dor tsam gyis //
NK066(chu)001:6908: rgyang grags la sogs mtshan ma yi //
NK066(chu)001:6909: dkyil 'khor phyag rgya gsal ldan pa //
NK066(chu)001:6910: ru'i dbang du lhag pa ting 'dzin lhag pa'i bu'i dbang du gzugs brnyan yin //
NK066(chu)001:6913: slob dpon mthong lam pas slob ma gcig spros las
NK066(chu)001:6914: su rung ba'i lam brod pa can la rig pa
NK066(chu)001:6916: rig pa rtsal gyi gzungs ma la brten nas dbang bskur te /
NK066(chu)001:6918: mthong lam rdo rje'i sku thob pas //
NK066(chu)001:6920: rig pa nyams kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK066(chu)001:6921: rig pa rtsal gyi gzungs brten nas //
NK066(chu)001:6922: zag med rdo rje'i sku la sbyor //
NK066(chu)001:6925: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa thob pa'i slob dpon
NK066(chu)001:6926: gyis skal ba dang ldan pa'i slob ma la lhag
NK066(chu)001:6927: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang las rgya mtshan
NK066(chu)001:6928: ldan la brten nas dbang bskur te /
NK066(chu)001:6930: rig pa brtan thob rnal 'byor pas //
NK066(chu)001:6931: las dang skal ldan rnal 'byor la //
NK066(chu)001:6932: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor du //
NK066(chu)001:6933: rig ma phyag rgya mdzes ma la //
NK066(chu)001:6934: dbang bskur byin rlob brtan byas nas //
NK066(chu)001:6935: cho ga thabs kyis dbang bskur zhing //
NK066(chu)001:6936: brgyud pa dbang gi man ngag gis //
NK066(chu)001:6939: de las lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du dbang bskur ba'i don 'chad pa'i tshe /
NK066(chu)001:6941: da lta gang zag rab 'bring kun dbang gi dkyil
NK066(chu)001:6942: 'khor rdul tshon kho na la brten dgos so zer
NK066(chu)001:6944: bi ma las thig gi bin tar+thara /
NK066(chu)001:6945: brtan zhing ngos 'jam khang bu dang //
NK066(chu)001:6946: ras sam gro ga'am shing shun nam //
NK066(chu)001:6947: t+aa la'i lo ma'am dur khrod ras //
NK066(chu)001:6948: zhing chen ras la sogs pa la //
NK066(chu)001:6949: phyag rgya mnyam rdzogs bris pa ni //
NK066(chu)001:6950: mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten yin no //
NK066(chu)001:6951: zhes khang bu'i ldebs ris dang ras bris la sogs pa gsungs pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:6952: khyad par +aa tsar+ya rgyal ba'i sdes /
NK066(chu)001:6953: rdul tshon bri bar ma nus na //
NK066(chu)001:6954: dkyil 'khor dang mnyam ras la ni //
NK066(chu)001:6955: nges par bcom ldan he ru ka /
NK066(chu)001:6956: phyag rgya'i gzugs dang bcas pa bri //
NK066(chu)001:6957: zhes ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor gsungs shing /
NK066(chu)001:6958: sngon gyi slob dpon grub pa'i dbang phyug rnams der dbang bskur ba nyid bzhed pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:6959: des na dman pa rnams ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug rung bar ma zad /
NK066(chu)001:6960: las dang po ba yin kyang dbang po'i khyad par gyis /
NK066(chu)001:6963: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor gsungs pa'i dbye bas rab me
NK066(chu)001:6964: tog gi tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor lta bu dmigs rten
NK066(chu)001:6965: cung zad tsam la bsten nas bskur rung ba yod
NK066(chu)001:6966: pa'i phyir te / bde 'dus dbang gi rtsa ba las /
NK066(chu)001:6967: dkyil 'khor gang du dbang bskur na //
NK066(chu)001:6968: rab 'bring tha mar gsungs pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:6969: me tog bris sku rdul tshon gsum //
NK066(chu)001:6970: dkyil 'khor gsum du dbang bskur ro //
NK066(chu)001:6972: de las kyang skal ldan mchog kha cig rdo rje
NK066(chu)001:6973: slob dpon gyi lus dkyil du thog ma nas 'jug
NK066(chu)001:6975: lus dkyil la dkyil 'khor du 'du shes pa'i gang
NK066(chu)001:6976: zag mkhas pa des phyi dkyil la brten dgos pa'i
NK066(chu)001:6978: de ltar yang slob dpon dril bu bas /
NK066(chu)001:6979: bcos ma gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor gang //
NK066(chu)001:6980: de ni gdul bya'i dbang las 'dod //
NK066(chu)001:6981: mkhas pa'i bsgrub bya de ma yin //
NK066(chu)001:6983: de lta bu'i mkhas pa des ni snga ma las /
NK066(chu)001:6985: grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis med pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:6988: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK066(chu)001:6989: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK066(chu)001:6990: brjod med brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK066(chu)001:6992: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK066(chu)001:6993: gnyis med lhun grub dkyil 'khor na //
NK066(chu)001:6994: thams cad bdag nyid rtag pa ra bzhugs //
NK066(chu)001:6996: dong sprugs kyi dbang gi me tog dor ba'i skabs su'ang /
NK066(chu)001:6997: slob dpon sku yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK066(chu)001:6998: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi dkyil 'khor
NK066(chu)001:6999: la brten nas bsgrub cing dbang len par bya ba
NK066(chu)001:7001: bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK066(chu)001:7002: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK066(chu)001:7003: byas te dad ldan rab zhugs na //
NK066(chu)001:7005: zhes pas mchog bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor yab yum gnyis kyi lus dkyil lam /
NK066(chu)001:7006: de las blo dman na rdul tshon rigs lnga'i dkyil
NK066(chu)001:7007: 'khor tsam byas la zhugs na'ang sngon gzhan gyis thob
NK066(chu)001:7008: pa dang mnyam pa'i dngos grub dang /
NK066(chu)001:7009: yang na dkyil 'khor rgyas pa dang mnyam pa'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur zhes bzhed pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:7010: gzhan yang phyi dkyil du ma zhugs par thog ma
NK066(chu)001:7011: nas lus dkyil du 'jug rung ba'i skal ldan yod
NK066(chu)001:7012: de dbang gsum pa'i ye shes kyi dpe tsam la
NK066(chu)001:7013: ltos mi dgos pa'i dbang gi snod ldan des /
NK066(chu)001:7014: thog ma nas don dam byang chub kyi dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa yod pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:7015: dper na man ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i rtsal dbang bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:7016: de 'dra ba'i skal ldan de la dbang logs su ma bskur kyang /
NK066(chu)001:7017: gdams ngag btab pa nyid kyis dbang dang go chu rug tu 'gyur ba yod pa la dgongs te /
NK066(chu)001:7019: dkyil 'khor du ni ma zhugs shing //
NK066(chu)001:7020: dbang rnams bskur bar ma byas kyang //
NK066(chu)001:7021: de kho nyid la 'bad ldan na //
NK066(chu)001:7023: zhes gsungs pa lta bu dang /
NK066(chu)001:7024: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi 'jam dpal sgyu
NK066(chu)001:7025: d+r+wa'i khog don du dbang la zab pa don dang
NK066(chu)001:7026: rgya che ba rtags gnyis su phye ba'i dang po'i
NK066(chu)001:7028: zab pa don gyi dbang mchog ni //
NK066(chu)001:7029: rig pa'i rtsal dbang thob pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:7030: chos nyid rtogs pas dbang zhes bya //
NK066(chu)001:7031: ye shes dbang bskur cod pan can //
NK066(chu)001:7033: de'ang spyir gang zag gi khyad par gyis ltos nas 'jug tshul gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:7034: rkyen sad tshul la ltos nas gang la mos pa der thog ma nas 'jug cing /
NK066(chu)001:7035: de dang mthun pa'i lam bsgom pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7036: rgyud smin tshul la ltos nas gang zag thams cad rim gyis ba yin la /
NK066(chu)001:7037: de yang tshe 'dir dbang gong mar mos tshe snga
NK066(chu)001:7038: mar dbang 'og ma thob cing de'i lam bsgoms pas
NK066(chu)001:7039: khyab pa'i phyir / rim gyis pa de'ang tshe 'di
NK066(chu)001:7040: kho na la brtseg dgos pa'i nges pa mi snang
NK066(chu)001:7041: khyab pa'i phyir / yang / 'dir skal dman rim
NK066(chu)001:7042: 'jug gi gang zag sngar rgyud ma smin pa gsar
NK066(chu)001:7043: du smin byed kyi dbang du byas na /
NK066(chu)001:7044: dkyil 'khor snga ma snga mar ma zhugs par phyi ma phyi mar mi 'jug ste /
NK066(chu)001:7045: lam gyi drod rtags kyang snga ma ma thob par
NK066(chu)001:7046: phyi mar mos shing 'jug pa mi srid pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:7047: ro // de la dgongs nas dbang gi gal po las /
NK066(chu)001:7048: dad brtson ldan pa'i slob ma yis //
NK066(chu)001:7049: ri mo'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK066(chu)001:7050: nus dang phan pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK066(chu)001:7051: brtul zhugs ldan pa'i bu mchog la //
NK066(chu)001:7054: phyi nang dkyil 'khor rnam gsum du //
NK066(chu)001:7056: ces sogs 'jug pa'i rim pa gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:7059: 'di ltar rgyu dus kyi dbang thog mar bskur te /
NK066(chu)001:7060: ma smin pa smin byed kyi dbang yin pas lam
NK066(chu)001:7061: gyi sngon du 'gro dgos pa'i phyir de grub ste
NK066(chu)001:7062: / smin byed kyi go don sgrib pa spang rung
NK066(chu)001:7063: dang 'bras bu thob rung la bzhag dgos pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:7064: / ro // lam dus kyi dbang ni dus la nam babs pa'i tshe bskur te /
NK066(chu)001:7065: lam gyi bogs 'don yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:7066: 'bras dus kyi dbang ni thog mar bskur te /
NK066(chu)001:7067: lam mthar phyin nas mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi sa la sbyor byed yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:7068: des na phyi ma gnyis ni grol byed lam gyi dbang yin no //
NK066(chu)001:7074: rtsa ba rnam lnga bco brgyad dang //
NK066(chu)001:7075: zhes pa'i rtsa ba lnga ni /
NK066(chu)001:7077: dang po sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:7078: gnyis pa nus pa bskyed pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:7079: gsum pa nyams myong bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7080: bzhi pa de nyid brtan par byed //
NK066(chu)001:7081: lnga pa brtan pas nyams blangs pas //
NK066(chu)001:7083: ces pas phan nus gnyis re re dang /
NK066(chu)001:7084: zab dbang gsum so sor bgrangs pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7087: nus dbang la lngar phye zhing /
NK066(chu)001:7088: zab dbang gsum dang bcas pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7091: bsgyur ba lnga la sum cu drug /
NK066(chu)001:7093: rtsa ba'i grangs zhi ba dang mtshungs la /
NK066(chu)001:7094: de'i yan lag so drug la bzhed pa mi mthun te /
NK066(chu)001:7095: sgrol ma ba'i rin chen 'bar ba'i gur du /
NK066(chu)001:7097: phyi yi dbang ni bcu dang gcig /
NK066(chu)001:7098: nang gi dbang ni bcu dang gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:7099: gsang dbang bcu dang sgrub dbang gsum //
NK066(chu)001:7104: sgrub dbang gsum du bzhed par mngon no //
NK066(chu)001:7106: dbye gzhi rtsa ba lnga las dbye chos so drug tu dbye ba byar med pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7107: lung gi dgongs pa 'di las lugs gzhan yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:7112: zab dbang gnyis te so drug tu 'byed pa'ang mi rigs te /
NK066(chu)001:7113: de mdo dbang gi lugs yin la /
NK066(chu)001:7114: de 'dir bkab ba la shes byed med cing /
NK066(chu)001:7115: lugs thams cad 'dres par 'gyur ba'i skyon gnas so //
NK066(chu)001:7116: de ci'i phyir mdo dbang gi lugs su 'gyur zhe na de yod de /
NK066(chu)001:7117: rtsa ba'i rgyud kun 'dus rig pa las /
NK066(chu)001:7119: srid pa gsum gyis phyag byasapa'i //
NK066(chu)001:7120: dbang phyug sum cu rtsa drug yin //
NK066(chu)001:7121: phyi yi dbang dang nang gi dbang //
NK066(chu)001:7122: sgrub pa'i dbang dang gsang ba'i dbang //
NK066(chu)001:7123: bcu dang bcu gcig bcu gsum dang //
NK066(chu)001:7124: rnam pa gnyis kyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:7126: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi dbang don rgya cher 'gyed pa las /
NK066(chu)001:7127: chu bo bzhi yi dbang gi rim pa la //
NK066(chu)001:7128: dang po rgyud kyi chu bo'i rnam grangs bcu //
NK066(chu)001:7132: lha dbang phyag mtshan rgyan chas dang //
NK066(chu)001:7133: nus dbang lnga dang gdan gyi dbang //
NK066(chu)001:7134: sgrub rdzas gsang ba rnam gsum mo //
NK066(chu)001:7135: zhes pa'i nang gses kyi grangs so drug ste /
NK066(chu)001:7138: bsnams pa phyag mtshan gyi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7139: dregs pa gdan gyi dbang gsum ni re re dang /
NK066(chu)001:7140: de las gzhan rnams kyi bye brag bgrangs pa'i sdom tshig ni /
NK066(chu)001:7141: rgyan chas rtags la bcu yin te /
NK066(chu)001:7146: nus pa'i dbang ni lngar nges te //
NK066(chu)001:7148: sgrub pa'i dbang la bco lnga ste //
NK066(chu)001:7153: rdo rje tshe dang 13bza' btung 14ming dbang 15ngo //
NK066(chu)001:7154: zab dbang gsum ste gsang ba 1dang //
NK066(chu)001:7157: de ltar na sngar gyi dbang chog 'gar rtags gsum gyi rjes su rdo rje'i gshog pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7158: rdor dril gyi rjes su mar me'i dbang 'byung ba'i phyir grangs 'jig go zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:7159: 'dir de gnyis ma bgrangs ba ni chad par mi sems te /
NK066(chu)001:7160: yan lag gi dbang sogs las kha bskang bar mngon gyi //
NK066(chu)001:7161: 'di nyid kyi dbang bar ma gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:7164: gdugs gsum kyang rtsa bar ma gsungs la /
NK066(chu)001:7168: phreng ba bzhi'i dbang tshig kyang mi 'byung ba'i phyir mtshungs so zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:7170: dang po gsum ni phan dbang gi nang tshan du
NK066(chu)001:7171: rgyud las gsungs pa'i phyir bskur dgos par ma zad
NK066(chu)001:7172: / khro bo las rim las bskur dus dkyus gsum gsungs na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:7173: gong du dbang gi rgyu 'chad pa'i tshe /
NK066(chu)001:7174: phyag rgya dbu rgyan snying po dang //
NK066(chu)001:7175: cod pan go cha rus pa'i phreng //
NK066(chu)001:7176: gzi mdangs rgyal mtshan zhing gis gdugs //
NK066(chu)001:7178: phyi ma bzhi ni bskur tshig ma gsungs kyang ming dkyus su smos pa'i phyir bskur dgos te /
NK066(chu)001:7179: gzhan yang rnga dang yungs kar dang //
NK066(chu)001:7180: gzungs dang phreng bas dbang bskur te //
NK066(chu)001:7183: de ltar na yan lag so drug po rtsa ba'i dbang lngar 'dus sam ma 'dus /
NK066(chu)001:7184: gnyis pa ltar na 'dir yang dbye gzhi dang dbye chos kha gam par 'gyur la /
NK066(chu)001:7185: dang po ltar na ji ltar bsdu zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:7186: khro bo las rim gyi go rim rnams 'khrugs bsdebs ji dgongs par bla ma rnams bzhed pas /
NK066(chu)001:7187: de'i phyir nus dbang lnga dang zab dbang gsum ma
NK066(chu)001:7188: gtogs pa'i dbang nyi shu rtsa brgyad po thams cad
NK066(chu)001:7189: phan dbang du bsdu bar bya ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:7191: rgyan chas las dang po drug dang /
NK066(chu)001:7192: sgrub rdzas las bzhi pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7194: bcu bzhi pa rnams ni dngos dang /
NK066(chu)001:7195: gzhan rnams lha dbang la sogs pa'i yan lag tu bsdu tshul du shes par byas la /
NK066(chu)001:7197: gdan dang lha dbang phyag mtshan dang //
NK066(chu)001:7198: chas bcu sgrub rdzas bco lnga ste //
NK066(chu)001:7199: phyi dbang nyer brgyad phan pa'i dbang //
NK066(chu)001:7200: nang gi nus pa'i dbang lnga ste //
NK066(chu)001:7201: gsang ba zab dbang rnam gsum mo //
NK066(chu)001:7212: de'i rab gnas yan chad tshar ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:7213: phyi rol du sbyin sreg bya /
NK066(chu)001:7214: nang du dbang mchod kyi rdzas dang rgyan rnams dgram /
NK066(chu)001:7215: de nas zhi khro gang yin gyi las gzhung bsrang zhing /
NK066(chu)001:7216: tshogs mchod bya ba rnams so //
NK066(chu)001:7219: dbang phyug 'jug dang bzod gsol dang //
NK066(chu)001:7220: khrus dgab dri dag lus dbul dang //
NK066(chu)001:7221: bgegs bskrad lhar rlob dam tshig sbyin //
NK066(chu)001:7222: de nyid dbog dang chu nan dang //
NK066(chu)001:7223: bsgrag dang rin chen dor ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:7224: lha dbog pa dang nan tan dang //
NK066(chu)001:7225: mig dbye dkyil 'khor legs bstan dang //
NK066(chu)001:7226: tshogs mchog yon dang rnam bco brgyad //
NK066(chu)001:7228: zhes pa'i bco brgyad ris bsdus na gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:7233: slob ma 'jug par gsol ba gdab pa gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:7235: dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba sngon du song nas 'jug ste /
NK066(chu)001:7236: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK066(chu)001:7238: de'ang slob dpon khrus byas dbang gos gyon nas dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgor 'dug ste /
NK066(chu)001:7239: rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul bas /
NK066(chu)001:7240: lha dang gnyis su med par bsam pa ni bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas 'jug ste /
NK066(chu)001:7242: dbang gos ldan pa dbang phyug ste //
NK066(chu)001:7243: gzhan dag gzhan gyis mdzes par bya //
NK066(chu)001:7245: lha rnams mngon byas rin chen ldan //
NK066(chu)001:7246: 'bru lnga rdo rje'i dam tshig gi /
NK066(chu)001:7247: sngags kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan //
NK066(chu)001:7248: phrin las ye shes gnyis med sbyar //
NK066(chu)001:7250: bskul ba'i dam tshig rjes dran pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:7251: 'od zer gzi brjid ldan par bya //
NK066(chu)001:7255: rdo rje ye shes 'thob byed pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:7256: zhes sogs kyis gsol ba btab cing bzod par gsol
NK066(chu)001:7257: bas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dgyes nas 'dzum pa
NK066(chu)001:7258: dang bcas pas gnang ba sbyin bar bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7260: slob dpon zhugs pa'i rjes su 'jug ste /
NK066(chu)001:7261: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK066(chu)001:7263: de la las rim bcu drug las /
NK066(chu)001:7265: phyi rol du dri'i chus bkru bar bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7267: shin tu bzang por 'gro ba rnams //
NK066(chu)001:7268: dri yi chu yis dag par bya //
NK066(chu)001:7271: ras dmar pos gdong g.yogs la snyim pa me tog
NK066(chu)001:7272: dang bcas te dkyil 'khor du 'jug par gsol ba
NK066(chu)001:7275: 'dod don dris shing lan gsol nas las kyi rdo
NK066(chu)001:7276: rjes dkyil 'khor khang ba'am yol ba'i nang du drang
NK066(chu)001:7278: bu khyod ci la dga' zhes dri //
NK066(chu)001:7279: skal bzang bdag dga' lan blan la //
NK066(chu)001:7280: 'khor lo'i drung du bkri bar bya //
NK066(chu)001:7282: bzhi pa lus dbul ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:7284: thal sbyar gus dang bcas pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:7285: phyogs bcu sras dang bcas pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:7286: dbang phyug sangs rgyas da ltar bdag /
NK066(chu)001:7287: ma 'ongs rang bzhin sems can la //
NK066(chu)001:7288: dgos pa gsum phyir lus dbul bya //
NK066(chu)001:7290: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa ste sarba bud+d+ha dang /
NK066(chu)001:7291: da ltar gyi sangs rgyas +aa ts+aar+ya ste slob dpon dang /
NK066(chu)001:7292: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas sa ka la sa t+wa zhes sems can mtha' dag ste /
NK066(chu)001:7293: de dag la rim pa bzhin du sangs rgyas kyi ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:7294: de'i snod rung du bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:7295: 'gro don mi 'dor zhing mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:7296: p+au dzo bas+th+aa n+aa ya +aat+m+aa nam nir+y+aa ta y+aa
NK066(chu)001:7297: mi zhes pas lus dbul bar dmigs la phyag 'tshal
NK066(chu)001:7298: du 'jug pa'o // lnga pa bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:7299: thog mar tshe mi yar bar bya ba'i ched du /
NK066(chu)001:7300: slob dpon gyi sbyor mtshams nas b+h+r+aum bu'i smin phrag
NK066(chu)001:7301: tu spros pas zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang
NK066(chu)001:7303: de'i dbus su h+aum sngo skya la bu'i tshe'i dngos
NK066(chu)001:7304: po thams cad bsdus te h+aum mdzad du bskyed la
NK066(chu)001:7305: / sgor mi g.yo bas tshe bsrung bar bsam /
NK066(chu)001:7306: de nas bi shwa badz+ra gyis sprul pa spros nas sum+b+ha'i sngags kyis bgegs skrod pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7308: tshe bsrung sbyor ba'i khro tshogs kyis //
NK066(chu)001:7309: bar gcod bgegs bskrad mtshams bcad la //
NK066(chu)001:7311: drug pa lhar rlob pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:7312: lag sor la dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i yi ge zung
NK066(chu)001:7313: las rigs lnga yab yum bskyed nas bden pa bdar
NK066(chu)001:7314: nas / phyag rgya bcings shing sprugs pas sbyor mtshams
NK066(chu)001:7315: nas spros pa'i 'od zer gyis bu'i sgrib pa bsregs
NK066(chu)001:7316: te 'od du zhu ba las cho ga gsum gyis
NK066(chu)001:7317: nas / / zhi khro gang yin gyi skabs dang
NK066(chu)001:7318: bstun nas rdo rje sems dpa' 'am badz+ra he ru
NK066(chu)001:7319: nas / / kar bskyed la / go bgo zhing lus bsrung bar bya ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:7321: sgrib sbyang rnam shes cho ga yis //
NK066(chu)001:7322: h+aum las sems dpa' 'am gzhan yang rung //
NK066(chu)001:7324: bdun pa dam tshig byin pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:7325: bdud rtsi sku gsung thugs su rlobs la /
NK066(chu)001:7326: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang la sogs pa'i tshig sngags dang /
NK066(chu)001:7327: 'bru gsum gyi 'phro 'dus dam tshig gsum ster bar bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7329: dam tshig chen po'i bdud rtsi lnga //
NK066(chu)001:7330: rang bzhin 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK066(chu)001:7331: gzi byin ldan par byin rlob la //
NK066(chu)001:7332: dam tshig sdom pa mchog ces bya //
NK066(chu)001:7335: dam tshig de nyid tshig gis dbog pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7336: rdo rje snying gar bzhag pa la //
NK066(chu)001:7337: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba 'di //
NK066(chu)001:7341: tsan+dana dkar dmar sbyar ba la //
NK066(chu)001:7342: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab gnas bya //
NK066(chu)001:7343: zhes pas tsan+dana gyi chu rdo rje gnod sbyin du bskyed nas /
NK066(chu)001:7344: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK066(chu)001:7345: zhes sogs ma bsrungs pa'i nyes dmigs kyi g.yang sa bstan te lcer lan gsum bzhag pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7346: yang chu rdo rje sems dpar bskyed nas /
NK066(chu)001:7347: de lta bas na bu khyod kyi /
NK066(chu)001:7348: zhes sogs bsrungs pa'i phan yon kyi brod pa bskyed
NK066(chu)001:7349: de lcer lan gsum bzhag la chu nan byed pa'o
NK066(chu)001:7351: rdo rje dang bcas pa'i thal mo bu'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK066(chu)001:7352: thabs dang shes rab sems nyid kyis //
NK066(chu)001:7353: zhes bya ba la sogs pas theg pa 'di /
NK066(chu)001:7354: gzhung bzhin du spyod cig par bsgrag pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7355: bcu gcig pa rin chen dor ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:7356: phyi dkyil lam bla ma'i lus dkyil gang rung la
NK066(chu)001:7357: me tog dor la lha gang dang las 'brel yod
NK066(chu)001:7359: dkyil 'khor yid la mngon sbyar nas //
NK066(chu)001:7360: 'dod pa'am yang na gzhan yang rung //
NK066(chu)001:7361: dor te 'brel pa legs par brtag /
NK066(chu)001:7363: bcu gnyis pa lha dbog pa la phyi nang gnyis las /
NK066(chu)001:7365: me tog de bu'i spyi bor bzhag ste /
NK066(chu)001:7366: yi dam lha gang yin pa nyid spyan drangs la
NK066(chu)001:7367: bstims pas snying gar chu nan gyi chu dang gnyis
NK066(chu)001:7368: su med par bsam pa ste /
