NK066(chu)001:7370: lcags kyu e his dgug bya ste //
NK066(chu)001:7371: nyes legs phrin las gsal byas la //
NK066(chu)001:7372: phyag rgya bstims la brtan par bya //
NK066(chu)001:7375: rigs dang mthun pa'i gsang mtshan gdags shing lha de nyid bsgom bzlas dbog pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7379: lhag pa'i lha gsum gang rung zhig dbog ste //
NK066(chu)001:7381: gang la mos pa'i lha de las dang thugs rjes 'brel bar grub pa'i phyir de nyid bsgom pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7383: las 'brel zab pas dngos grub nye ba'i phyir me tog gang la babs pa'i lha de bsgom pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7385: dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo kho na bsgom pa'o gsung /
NK066(chu)001:7386: de dag kyang mi rigs pa ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:7388: mtshan mas grol la brgya byin pas //
NK066(chu)001:7389: dkyil 'khor chen por zhugs pa'i tshe //
NK066(chu)001:7390: gang la babs pa'i lha de nyid //
NK066(chu)001:7391: yang na lha kun gcig pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:7392: gang mos lha de yi dam bya //
NK066(chu)001:7394: bcu gsum pa nan tan du bya ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:7395: khe nyen bstan pa'i sgo nas lha de nyid bsgom par gdams pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7397: skal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes de //
NK066(chu)001:7398: gnyer na nye bar 'byung ba yi //
NK066(chu)001:7399: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK066(chu)001:7400: dad med nyams na phung bar 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:7403: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:7404: gang zhig phyag rgya 'di spangs na //
NK066(chu)001:7405: nyon mongs ngan song gsum du skye //
NK066(chu)001:7408: bdag nyid lha dang mnyam sbyor nas //
NK066(chu)001:7410: gcig dang du mar yongs bral phyir //
NK066(chu)001:7413: de'ang brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes su /
NK066(chu)001:7414: nang gi lha dbog pa dang nan tan du bya
NK066(chu)001:7415: ba gnyis 'og tu dkyil 'khor bstan pa dang sbrel
NK066(chu)001:7416: nas mdzad do // bcu bzhi pa mig dbye ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:7417: ru'i thugs ka nas spros pa'i 'od zer thur ma
NK066(chu)001:7418: lta bu'i ma rig pa'i ling tog bsal te ye
NK066(chu)001:7419: shes kyi dkyil 'khor mthong bar bsams la /
NK066(chu)001:7420: mig phye zhing gdong g.yogs dgrol te /
NK066(chu)001:7422: 'od zer thur mas dbye byas la //
NK066(chu)001:7424: bco lnga pa dkyil 'khor ston pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:7425: gser sogs mtshon byed nges blangs la //
NK066(chu)001:7426: zhes pas phyag shing sogs kyis bstan te /
NK066(chu)001:7427: dkyil 'khor gyi don rtags dang lha'i de kho na nyid rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7428: bcu drug pa yon dbul ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:7430: dbang dang dngos grub 'dod pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:7431: 'di la shin tu nan tan bya //
NK066(chu)001:7432: zhes pas yon ci 'byor ba dbul te /
NK066(chu)001:7434: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK066(chu)001:7437: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK066(chu)001:7438: zhes sogs tshigs su bcad pa gcig gsungs so //
NK066(chu)001:7439: gal te phongs pas dngos su ma 'byor na phyis dbul bar khas blang ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:7440: yid kyis lus longs spyod thams cad ltos pa med par phul bar bsam zhing /
NK066(chu)001:7442: de dag ni 'jug pa'i cho ga'o //
NK066(chu)001:7443: der zhugs pas thob pa'i yon tan gang zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:7445: dang po dkyil 'khor 'dir zhugs pas dkyil 'khor thams
NK066(chu)001:7446: cad du zhugs par 'gyur ba'i yon tan yod de
NK066(chu)001:7448: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar legs zhugs pas //
NK066(chu)001:7449: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK066(chu)001:7450: dkyil 'khor kun tu zhugs pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:7453: 'dir zhugs pas sngon 'og min du mthar lam bzhugs pa dang skal ba mnyam par 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:7458: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:7459: 'khor lo mngon du mthong ba yi //
NK066(chu)001:7460: bsod nams brtag pa gang yin pa //
NK066(chu)001:7461: phyis byas pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:7463: gsum pa 'dir mos pa tsam la yang rgyal ba
NK066(chu)001:7464: thams cad kyis nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur
NK066(chu)001:7466: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK066(chu)001:7469: 'dir zhugs na dngos grub thams cad bde blag tu thob par 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:7471: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rigs nges shing /
NK066(chu)001:7472: gdon rnams bzlog cing ngan song spong //
NK066(chu)001:7473: longs spyod 'du ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK066(chu)001:7474: ye shes spyan gyi gzhi ru nges //
NK066(chu)001:7475: de la sogs pa bsam yas mchog /
NK066(chu)001:7477: gsum pa dbang bskur ba la /
NK066(chu)001:7482: bus phyag byas te gsol ba gdab //
NK066(chu)001:7483: rus gnang ba sbyin la dkyil 'khor bskor zhing bstod nas nam mkhar bteg /
NK066(chu)001:7484: de bzhin gshegs pa ma lus pa mdun mkhar spyan drangs te gsol ba gdab /
NK066(chu)001:7485: de nas dbu rgyan gyon te dkyil 'khor gyi steng du'am drung du dbang khri la 'dug par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:7487: snod rim dang sbyar te bskur ba dngos dang /
NK066(chu)001:7488: dbang gi grangs dang rim pa la dpyad pa /
NK066(chu)001:7489: de dbang bzhir bsdu tshul lo //
NK066(chu)001:7491: skal ldan gyi slob bu dad brtson brtul zhugs can
NK066(chu)001:7492: gsum la rim pa ltar phan nus zab mo'i dbang
NK066(chu)001:7493: rnams so so'i blo'i theg tshad dang sbyar nas sbyin
NK066(chu)001:7495: gal te mi theg pa la sbyin na bu'i rgyud
NK066(chu)001:7496: chud zos par 'gyur ba'i phyir nyes pa chen por
NK066(chu)001:7498: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK066(chu)001:7499: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK066(chu)001:7500: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK066(chu)001:7501: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK066(chu)001:7503: de yang ji ltar bskur ba'i tshul la /
NK066(chu)001:7504: rje sgro phug pa'i gsung rgyun snga phyii gnyis las /
NK066(chu)001:7506: dbang thams cad la mtshungs ldan dang //
NK066(chu)001:7508: skur thabs gsum du gsung na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:7509: phyis don brgyad brgyad du bsdus nas gsung zhes bla ma rtsags tsha gsungs pa ltar /
NK066(chu)001:7510: 'dir yang phyi ma'i rjes su 'brang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:7511: de la phan dbang bcu ni /
NK066(chu)001:7512: dbu rgyan cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:7514: de re re la yang don brgyad brgyad de //
NK066(chu)001:7516: rgyu rkyen ngo bo 'bras bu dang //
NK066(chu)001:7517: rim las skyon yon brgyad ces bya //
NK066(chu)001:7521: lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:7523: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar ye nas gnas pa ni dbu rgyan gyi mtshungs ldan no //
NK066(chu)001:7524: de bzhin du rtsa ro rkyang gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:7527: rtsa dbu ma'i nang na thig le so gnyis gnas pa phreng ba'i /
NK066(chu)001:7528: lus rtsa'i d+r+wa bas khebs pa go cha'i //
NK066(chu)001:7529: pho mo'i dbang po rgyal mtshan gyi /
NK066(chu)001:7530: rtog tshogs ye nas lhar gnas pa phyag rgya'i /
NK066(chu)001:7533: rtsa gnas thig les gang ba bum pa /
NK066(chu)001:7534: mgrin pa'i thig le bza' btung gi /
NK066(chu)001:7535: khams lnga'i bcud dam rdzas lnga ni snying po lnga'i mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu'o //
NK066(chu)001:7536: de ltar yang thal rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:7540: dbu ma bcud sdud phreng ba mtshan ldan pa //
NK066(chu)001:7541: d+r+wa ba'i rtsa go cha dang dbang rgyal mtshan po dang //
NK066(chu)001:7542: phung sogs phyag rgya ye shes bde gdugs 'khor lo //
NK066(chu)001:7543: bza' btung h+aum gi bde ba'i ye shes 'bab //
NK066(chu)001:7544: tshogs brgyad dbu rgyan rang bzhin ye shes lnga //
NK066(chu)001:7545: sngags rdzas dgongs pas gang blangs pa //
NK066(chu)001:7546: kun nas ldan zhing skyob pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:7547: sdug bsngal las grol rigs su nges //
NK066(chu)001:7550: dbang rdzas rab gnas dang ldan pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7552: dbu rgyan dang phreng ba la rin 'byung gi rab gnas bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7554: rin chen rab gnas las byung ba'i //
NK066(chu)001:7555: rin chen mdzes pa'i dbu rgyan bcing //
NK066(chu)001:7557: rin chen rab gnas phreng bas bcing //
NK066(chu)001:7559: cod pan mthing dmar gnyis la kha cig rdor sems
NK066(chu)001:7560: dang mtha' yas gnyis kyis so sor mdzad mod kyi
NK066(chu)001:7561: / 'dir ni gnyis ka la mtha' yas kyis bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7563: rab gnas chos 'byung ye shes dngos /
NK066(chu)001:7564: kha dog gnyis ldan dbang bskur bya //
NK066(chu)001:7567: phreng ba cod pan rin chen pad //
NK066(chu)001:7569: go cha la nges 'byed du rdor sems kyis bya bar bshad kyang /
NK066(chu)001:7571: las mchog rab gnas rdo rje'i go //
NK066(chu)001:7572: zhes pa ltar don grub kyis mdzad do //
NK066(chu)001:7573: rgyal mtshan dang gdugs la mi bskyod pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7575: rdo rje rab gnas las byung ba'i //
NK066(chu)001:7576: rgyal mtshan rin chen tog ldan pa //
NK066(chu)001:7578: mi bskyod rab gnas rin chen gdugs //
NK066(chu)001:7580: phyag rgya la lha rang rang gis te /
NK066(chu)001:7582: phyag rgya rang gi lha nyid dang //
NK066(chu)001:7584: bum chu la rigs lnga kar 'dus pa'i lha spyis bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7586: bum pa rang gi yab yum sems //
NK066(chu)001:7589: rigs lnga 'dus pa'i bum chu sbyin //
NK066(chu)001:7591: bza' btung la rnam snang gis bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7593: bza' btung snang mdzad rab gnas ldan //
NK066(chu)001:7595: snying po yig 'bru lnga la 'bras bu lngas rab gnas bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7597: sku gsung yon tan las byin bsdu //
NK066(chu)001:7599: gnyis pa rkyen la bzhi ste /
NK066(chu)001:7600: phan dbang bskur rung gi slob bu snod ldan ni rgyu'i rkyen /
NK066(chu)001:7601: slob dpon dgongs pa can ni bdag po'i rkyen /
NK066(chu)001:7602: ting 'dzin sngags rgya rdzas sogs 'dzom pa'i nus pa khyad par can ni dmigs pa'i rkyen /
NK066(chu)001:7603: dbang snga mas go phye nas phyi mar rim par snang ba ni de ma thag rkyen no //
NK066(chu)001:7606: ngo bo snod kyi mtshan nyid kyis //
NK066(chu)001:7607: dbye ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:7608: zhes thob bya lnga las 'dir phan dbang bcu'o //
NK066(chu)001:7610: bskur bas thob bya rang la gnas pa'i don mngon
NK066(chu)001:7611: du 'gyur rung gi nus pa'i sa bon tsam bzhag
NK066(chu)001:7613: dbang thob zhes pa'i tha snyad ni //
NK066(chu)001:7614: spyod rgyun mngon sum thob pa yang //
NK066(chu)001:7615: go mi 'gog cing rigs la snang //
NK066(chu)001:7616: tha mar sangs rgyas 'thob byed pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:7617: nus pa gang skyes thob pa'i tshad //
NK066(chu)001:7618: chos ni skabs kyi nyan bshad de //
NK066(chu)001:7619: phyi rol drang don mnyan du rung //
NK066(chu)001:7621: lnga pa rim pa'i sdom ni /
NK066(chu)001:7622: snying po lnga dang dbu rgyan dang //
NK066(chu)001:7623: bum pa cod pan phreng ba ste //
NK066(chu)001:7624: go cha rgyal mtshan gdugs phyag rgya //
NK066(chu)001:7625: bza' btung dbang rnams rim par bskur //
NK066(chu)001:7626: zhes brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes te 'grel sgrol t+aika /
NK066(chu)001:7627: chung gi lugs su bzhed do //
NK066(chu)001:7628: gnyags 'grel las bum pa sngon du bskur zhes 'byung /
NK066(chu)001:7629: rdo rje las rim du gzhan lugs snga ma dang 'dra ba las /
NK066(chu)001:7630: phyag rgya thog mar smos shing /
NK066(chu)001:7631: cod pan dang phreng ba gnyis go barje ba tsam khyad par du snang ste /
NK066(chu)001:7632: 'di dag zhi ba'i dbang gi go rim tsam du zad do //
NK066(chu)001:7633: drug pa bskur ba'i las la /
NK066(chu)001:7640: gnas ni spyi dang khyad par te //
NK066(chu)001:7643: khyad par bstim gnas gnyis te /
NK066(chu)001:7645: gzhag pa'i gnas dang bstiim pa'i gnas //
NK066(chu)001:7646: de bzhin khong du chud pa gces //
NK066(chu)001:7650: phyi dbang lus la bskur ba ste //
NK066(chu)001:7651: 'o na lus kyi gang du bskur zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:7652: khyad par snying po dbu rgyan bum //
NK066(chu)001:7653: gdugs dang cod pan phreng ba mgo /
NK066(chu)001:7654: go cha lus te rgyal mtshan lag /
NK066(chu)001:7655: bza' btung ngag gi lam du'o //
NK066(chu)001:7656: phyag rgya spyi bo'am snying ga ste //
NK066(chu)001:7659: rang rang gi mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu la bstim pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7661: slob bu lhar gsal lus kyi gnas lngar 'bru lnga
NK066(chu)001:7662: bkod la byin bsdus te cho ga gsum gyis rigs
NK066(chu)001:7663: lngar bskyed pas khams lnga 'bras bu lnga'i ngo bor
NK066(chu)001:7664: dag par bsam pa ni snying po lnga'i dgongs pa'o
NK066(chu)001:7665: // dbu rgyan mu ku ta'i sngags kyis bskon pa rin po che'i khang bu lngar gyur /
NK066(chu)001:7666: ru'i sor mor 'bru bcu bkod la dam rgya bcas
NK066(chu)001:7667: nas mgo bo'i gnas lngar bzhag pas rigs lnga yab
NK066(chu)001:7668: yum sbyor ba'i sems rgyun gnas so sor thim ste
NK066(chu)001:7669: rtags rigs lnga / don tshogs brgyad ye shes lnga'i
NK066(chu)001:7670: ngo bor dag par bsam pa ni dbu rgyan gyi'o
NK066(chu)001:7671: rtags rigs lnga / // de bzhin du /
NK066(chu)001:7672: bum pas rigs lnga'i chu rgyun gyis nyon mongs pa'i
NK066(chu)001:7673: dri ma dag nas ye shes lnga'i dbang thob par
NK066(chu)001:7674: dang / cod pan gyis dmar po gyen du 'phur bas /
NK066(chu)001:7675: chos kyi rgyal srid la mnga' brnyes shing mthing ga mthur du 'phyang bas /
NK066(chu)001:7676: gdug pa can zil gyis gnon par dang /
NK066(chu)001:7677: me tog gi phreng bas gzungs ting sogs 'bras chos thams cad rdzogs par dang /
NK066(chu)001:7678: go chas phas rgol gyis mi tshugs par dang //
NK066(chu)001:7679: rgyal mtshan gyis bdud dang mu stegs la sogs pa log lta zil gyis gnon par dang /
NK066(chu)001:7680: gdugs kyi nyon mongs pa'i tsha gdung las skyob par dang /
NK066(chu)001:7681: phyag rgyas rtog pa rang kha ma lha'i ngo bor dag par dang /
NK066(chu)001:7682: bza' btung gis 'dod yon lnga la ma 'gags par longs spyod pa'i dbang thob par bsam pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7684: tshigs bcad dang sngags rnams rdo rje las rim na gsal lo //
NK066(chu)001:7687: dgongs pa dang rjes su mthun par thob bya gang yin 'grub pa'i smon lam brjod pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7688: skyon yon gnyis ni 'og tu 'chad do //
NK066(chu)001:7689: de dag la phan pa'i dbang zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7690: 'di phyir phan pa'i sa bon tsam las da lta
NK066(chu)001:7691: nyid nas rang gzhan gyi don sgrub pa'i nus pa
NK066(chu)001:7692: so sor bzhag pa med pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:7693: de bskur ba'i dus ni 'jug pa'i chos bcu drug
NK066(chu)001:7694: gis dkyil 'khor du bcug ste bskur ba yin no
NK066(chu)001:7695: // gal te 'jug pa dang dngos gzhi gnyis zhag gis bar chod na /
NK066(chu)001:7696: slob dpon dbang khrir bzhugs pa yan tshar ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:7697: bgegs bskrad de bu rnams lhar bskyed la go bgo
NK066(chu)001:7698: lus bsrung ba rnams bya zhes bla ma rtsags tsha
NK066(chu)001:7699: dang / 'gos rtsi lung pa'i dbang chog las 'byung ngo //
NK066(chu)001:7700: gnyis pa nus dbang la'ang sngar ltar don brgyad brgyad de /
NK066(chu)001:7701: dang po mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni /
NK066(chu)001:7702: bu'i rna ba gnyis kyi rtsa nang sgra nyan byed
NK066(chu)001:7703: kyi thig le shin tu dwangs par gnas pa ni
NK066(chu)001:7704: nyan dbang gi mtshungs ldan no //
NK066(chu)001:7705: de bzhin du snying ga'i dran byed kyi thig le bsgom dbang gi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7706: lag pa'i skyod byed kyi thig le las kyi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7707: lce'i smra byed kyi thig le 'chad pa'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:7708: yan lag lnga'i skyod byed kyi thig le lnga ni rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan no //
NK066(chu)001:7711: rdzas ni glegs bam rgya gram dang //
NK066(chu)001:7712: 'khor lo phreng ba rdo rje dril //
NK066(chu)001:7713: 'byung ldan don yod snang mtha' yas //
NK066(chu)001:7714: yi dam rigs lnga'i rab gnas ldan //
NK066(chu)001:7715: zhes pas glegs bam rin 'byung gi rab gnas can ni nyan dbang gi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7716: phreng ba yi dam gang yin gyi rab gnas can ni bsgom pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7717: rgya gram don grub kyi rab gnas can phrin las kyi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7718: 'khor lo mtha' phyag len la dung dang phyag shing yang gtod par mdzad /
NK066(chu)001:7719: yas kyi rab gnas can 'chad pa'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:7720: rdor dril rigs lnga spyi 'dus kyi rab gnas can
NK066(chu)001:7721: ni rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang gi lhan cig byed
NK066(chu)001:7722: pa'i rgyu'o // gnyis pa rkyen bzhi ni /
NK066(chu)001:7723: nus dbang bskur rung gi slob bu rgyu'i rkyen yin pa la sogs te sngar ltar ro //
NK066(chu)001:7725: thob bya nus pa'i dbang lnga'o //
NK066(chu)001:7727: dbang bskur bas nus pa ches cher skyes pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7729: thob pa'i tshad ni nus pa lnga //
NK066(chu)001:7730: bdag nyan bsgom dang gzhan 'chad phrin dang gnyis rab 'byams ka'i don //
NK066(chu)001:7731: thogs pa med par spyod pa'i sgo ma 'gags pa ni thob pa'i tshad //
NK066(chu)001:7732: chos ni grol lam nges don gyi bshad rnams //
NK066(chu)001:7733: snang bar byed pa'i man ngag sbyin du rung //
NK066(chu)001:7735: lnga pa rim pa ni gzhung gi dkyus bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:7736: drug pa las la bzhi las /
NK066(chu)001:7737: dang po gnas la gnyis te /
NK066(chu)001:7738: spyi ni dbang rdzas lnga ka lag tu gtod pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7739: khyad par ni so so'i mtshungs ldan la bstim pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7741: gnas ni rna ba snying dang lag /
NK066(chu)001:7742: lce dang yan lag rnam lnga'o //
NK066(chu)001:7748: slob dpon kun bzang yab yum gsal ba'i sbyor mtshams nas b+h+r+aum yig dmar ser zhig chad /
NK066(chu)001:7749: de bu'i mtshungs ldan gyi rten so so la phog bar bsam zhing /
NK066(chu)001:7750: der las kyi rdo rjes bdud rtsi'i thig ler byas pas /
NK066(chu)001:7751: b+h+r+aum de zhu ba las rten gyi rtsa gzhal yas
NK066(chu)001:7752: khang dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa gru chad la
NK066(chu)001:7753: sgo btod pa zhig tu bskyed /
NK066(chu)001:7754: der rtsa nang gi bcud 'dus pa'i thig le mtshungs
NK066(chu)001:7755: ldan gyi rgyu de dag lha so so'i sa bon
NK066(chu)001:7756: du gsal ba rnams cho ga gsum bskyed kyis lhar
NK066(chu)001:7757: bskyed / spro na dbang bskur byin brlab byas te
NK066(chu)001:7758: yan lag gi lha bsgom pa yang thal ba chung
NK066(chu)001:7759: ngu nas bshad gsungs pa ltar byas na legs /
NK066(chu)001:7760: gang ltar yang ye shes pa drangs bstim mchod nas /
NK066(chu)001:7761: lha de dag snyoms 'jug mdzad pa'i sems sprin gyis byin bsdus te /
NK066(chu)001:7762: rjes chags kyi mes bzhus nas slob bu la thim
NK066(chu)001:7763: pas nyan bsgom la sogs pa mi nus pa'i sgrib
NK066(chu)001:7765: slob bu nyid kyang 'od du zhu ba las rigs gang yin gyi lhar bskyed /
NK066(chu)001:7766: de la bskur tshig rnams brjod bzhin par dbang rdzas gtad pas /
NK066(chu)001:7767: nyan pa la sogs pa'i bya ba rnams thogs med
NK066(chu)001:7768: du byed nus pa'i nus pa dngos su skyes par
NK066(chu)001:7769: bsam pa'o // de ltar yang las rim las /
NK066(chu)001:7770: sbyor ba las byung le brgan b+h+r+aum //
NK066(chu)001:7771: gang yin gnas su 'khor lo'i khang //
NK066(chu)001:7772: nyi zla'i gdan la sems byung 'bru //
NK066(chu)001:7773: lnga gnyis zung las 'khril sbyor sku //
NK066(chu)001:7774: ye shes spyan drangs cung zad mchod //
NK066(chu)001:7775: yongs gyur de yi phyag rgya gsal //
NK066(chu)001:7779: zhes sogs kyi nyan dbang gi dgongs pa bstan te /
NK066(chu)001:7780: rna rtsa gnyis kyi gzhung du nyan dbang ni /
NK066(chu)001:7781: tshig don gyi gzungs sogs yon tan rin po che'i
NK066(chu)001:7782: gter 'dzin pa'i phyir t+r+aam zung lnga las rin chen
NK066(chu)001:7783: rigs kyi gtso bo rang gi rigs chung gis bskor
NK066(chu)001:7785: de'i steng du rang rang gi sa bon las zhi
NK066(chu)001:7786: ba la gshin rje gshed sogs sgo ba yab yum
NK066(chu)001:7787: rkyang ba bsnan pas lha bco brgyad /
NK066(chu)001:7788: khro bo la rta gdong ma sogs bzhi bsnan bas lha bcu bzhi'o //
NK066(chu)001:7789: gsal ba'i 'khor lo'i sogs kyis sgom dbang ni snying ga'i gzhal yas khang du /
NK066(chu)001:7791: yang na mos pa'i yi dam gyi lha de nyid
NK066(chu)001:7792: kyi sa bon zung lnga las gtso bo rigs chung
NK066(chu)001:7793: sgo skyong dang bcas pa'i lha bco brgyad dam bcu
NK066(chu)001:7795: lag pa'i 'khor lo'i sogs kyis phrin las kyi dbang
NK066(chu)001:7796: ni las kyi rigs kyi bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:7797: lag rtsa'i dkyil 'khor la t+r+aam zung lnga las las
NK066(chu)001:7798: kyi rigs gtso 'khor bco brgyad dam bcu bzhi bsgom
NK066(chu)001:7799: pa'o // smra byed 'khor lo'i sogs kyi 'chad dbang
NK066(chu)001:7800: ni pad+ma'i rigs chos kyi rgyal po yin pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:7801: lce'i 'khor lo la h+r+aihzunga lnga las pad rigs gtso
NK066(chu)001:7802: 'khor bco brgyad dam bcu bzhi bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7803: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i sogs kyis rdo rje rgyal po
NK066(chu)001:7804: ni rigs thams cad kyi bdag po yin pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:7806: mgo la sogs pa rang rang gi rigs kyi yan
NK066(chu)001:7807: lag lnga'i dkyil 'khor la h+aum sogs sa bon las
NK066(chu)001:7808: rigs lnga so so'i rigs chung dang bcas pa'i lha
NK066(chu)001:7809: lnga bcu dang / de'i steng du /
NK066(chu)001:7810: spyi gtsug snying nas g.yas bskor du //
NK066(chu)001:7811: nu ma dpung mgo sog pa'i steng //
NK066(chu)001:7812: sog phrag sog steng dpung mgo nu //
NK066(chu)001:7813: bshang kha rnams la go rim bzhin /
NK066(chu)001:7814: h+aum mdzad rnam rgyal dbyug pa sngo //
NK066(chu)001:7815: gshin rje mi g.yo rta 'dod rgyal //
NK066(chu)001:7816: bdud rtsi sum rgyal stobs chen po //
NK066(chu)001:7817: zhes pa ltar khro bcu yum dang bcas pa'i khro phreng bskyed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7819: zhi khro'i dbang lha grangs mang nyung med de /
NK066(chu)001:7820: de ltar yod pa dag sgo skyong gis phye ba tsam du zad pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:7823: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK066(chu)001:7825: nyan dbang thob pas rang thos bsam bya bar rjes
NK066(chu)001:7826: su gnang zhing 'chad dbang ma thob par gzhan la
NK066(chu)001:7827: mi ston par dam bsgrag pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:7828: de bzhin du bsgom dbang gis sgo gsum lha sngags
NK066(chu)001:7829: ye shes kyi ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i ngang las sgrub
NK066(chu)001:7830: mchod sogs bya bar gnang ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:7831: phrin las kyi dbang gis las rnam pa bzhis 'gro ba 'dul ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:7832: 'chad dbang gis snod brtags te blo dang 'tshams par chos ston cig par dang /
NK066(chu)001:7833: rdo rje rgyal pos dbang bskur ba sogs dkyil 'khor
NK066(chu)001:7834: kun gyi bdag por rjes su gnang ba ster ba'o
NK066(chu)001:7835: // bzhi pa smon lam ni sngar ltar dang /
NK066(chu)001:7837: de dag la nus pa'i dbang zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7838: rang bzhin gyi don da lta nyid nas dngos su byed nus pa'i phyir te /
NK066(chu)001:7840: bdag gzhan don la sbyor nus phyir //
NK066(chu)001:7841: nus pa'i dbang zhes gsungs pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:7842: zhes nus tshad la rag lus pas de skad du gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:7845: bdag don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la nyan bsgom gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:7846: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la 'chad phrin gnyis /
NK066(chu)001:7847: gnyis ka'i don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can la rdo
NK066(chu)001:7848: rje rgyal po bka' rab 'byams kyi dbang bskur ba
NK066(chu)001:7849: yin no // gsum pa zab dbang gsum la'ang don brgyad brgyad de /
NK066(chu)001:7851: slob bu'i lus la thig le mi rtog pa'i ye
NK066(chu)001:7852: shes don dam bden pa'i ngo bor ye nas rang
NK066(chu)001:7853: chas su gnas pa ni gsang dbang gi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7854: don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes rang chas su gnas pa shes rab ye shes kyi dang /
NK066(chu)001:7855: dbyer med kyi ye shes rang chas su gnas pa ni bde ba chen po'i mtshungs ldan no //
NK066(chu)001:7857: slob dpon gyis yum lo nyi shu ma dang rol
NK066(chu)001:7858: ba'i nyi zla gnyis 'dres ni gsang dbang gi ste
NK066(chu)001:7860: rdzas ni dngos dang nus pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:7861: dngos ni nyi zla byang chub sems //
NK066(chu)001:7863: bu nyid kyi yum lo bcu drug ma zla ba 'dzag pa ni sher dbang gi ste /
NK066(chu)001:7865: rdzas ni skabs kyi phyag rgya mo //
NK066(chu)001:7868: yang bu'i yum lo bcu gnyis ma nyi ma 'dzag
NK066(chu)001:7869: pa ni bde ba chen po'i dbang gi lhan cig
NK066(chu)001:7871: khyad bar bcu de nyid ldan ma //
NK066(chu)001:7874: spyod rig mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs gsum ldan gyi slob
NK066(chu)001:7875: bu zab dbang gi snod rung ni rgyu'i rkyen yin
NK066(chu)001:7878: thob bya zab dbang gsum mo //
NK066(chu)001:7880: dper na rno la ngar btags pa ltar dbang thob pas nus pa dngos su skyes pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:7882: rno la ngar btags nus pa bzhin //
NK066(chu)001:7883: nus pa skyes pa thob pa'i tshad //
NK066(chu)001:7885: lnga pa rim pa ni go sla bar zad do //
NK066(chu)001:7887: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK066(chu)001:7888: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK066(chu)001:7889: rdo rje'i lam nas pad mor 'khyil //
NK066(chu)001:7890: rtse nas bstim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK066(chu)001:7891: zhes pa'i gzhung rdo rje'i tshig gcig gi steng du
NK066(chu)001:7892: zab dbang gsum ga sbrags te bshad rgyud thal bas
NK066(chu)001:7894: de la dang po gsang dbang bskur thabs ni /
NK066(chu)001:7895: rdo rje slob dpon yab yum gtso bo yab yum du bskyed pa'i mkha' gsang rlob /
NK066(chu)001:7896: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul nas phyag rgya bzhis rol pas
NK066(chu)001:7897: lhan skyes bde ba'i rang bzhin byang chub sems kyi
NK066(chu)001:7898: chu rgyun h+aum yig gi rnam par yab kyi rdo
NK066(chu)001:7899: rje'i lam nas dbab thabs kyis phab ste /
NK066(chu)001:7900: yum gyi pad mor bskyil ba las /
NK066(chu)001:7901: bskur thabs gsum po gang rung gis gsang dbang bskur te /
NK066(chu)001:7902: 'jam dpal dmar po'i bang mdzod las /
NK066(chu)001:7903: ba dang be'u'i tshul dag gam //
NK066(chu)001:7904: de bzhin bung ba sbrang rtsi'i tshul //
NK066(chu)001:7905: yang na bya dang bye'u'i tshul //
NK066(chu)001:7907: thabs kyi gsang dbang yab kyi rdo rje'i rtse nas bus len pa ba dang be'u'i tshul dang /
NK066(chu)001:7908: shes rab kyi gsang dbang yum gyi pad+ma'i sna rtse
NK066(chu)001:7909: nas len pa me tog dang bung ba'i tshul dang
NK066(chu)001:7910: / de ltar mi nus pa'i thabs shes gnyis med
NK066(chu)001:7911: kyi gsang dbang yab kyi lces pad+ma las blangs te
NK066(chu)001:7912: bu la ster ba bya dang bye'u'i tshul du bskur
NK066(chu)001:7913: / ba'o // de nyid bzhag gnas slob bu'i lce dang /
NK066(chu)001:7916: sems kyi dkyil nas drangs pa'i chu //
NK066(chu)001:7917: khyod kyi lce la bzhag pa 'di //
NK066(chu)001:7918: snying gi dkyil du gzung bar byos //
NK066(chu)001:7921: byang chub kyi sems rgyun h+aum gi 'bru tshogs su
NK066(chu)001:7922: gsal ba de nyid rdo rje sems dpa' yungs kar
NK066(chu)001:7923: gyi tshad tsam pa mang por gyur te snying la
NK066(chu)001:7924: thim pas chos kyi 'khor lo'i rtsa chen bzhi la
NK066(chu)001:7925: gnas pa'i rigs drug gi sa bon gnyid dang bcas
NK066(chu)001:7926: pa bsregs nas don dam mi rtog pa'i ye shes
NK066(chu)001:7929: mi bskyod yab yum rol ba yi //
NK066(chu)001:7930: rnam par bde ba gsal zhing mi ngo bo dmigs pa //
NK066(chu)001:7931: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK066(chu)001:7932: rdo rje ye shes h+aum tshogs kyis //
NK066(chu)001:7933: bad mo'i ye shes bsdus 'khyil ba'i //
NK066(chu)001:7934: yungs kar tshad tsam rdo rje sems //
NK066(chu)001:7935: rtse nas rtse ru bstim pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:7936: rang bzhin chos kyis gnas pa'i steng /
NK066(chu)001:7938: sa bon zung gsum gnyid dang bcas //
NK066(chu)001:7939: gnas ngan len pa gsum sbyangs te //
NK066(chu)001:7940: dmigs med sems kyi ye shes lnga //
NK066(chu)001:7941: gsal bas sa bon tshig pa bzhin //
NK066(chu)001:7942: gyis 'khor bar mi skye ste dbang gi thabs kyi dbugs 'khor ba'i duhkha las dbyung ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:7944: de la ci'i phyir gsang dbang zhes bya zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:7945: rtog med kyi bde ba'i ye shes ngos zin dka'
NK066(chu)001:7946: ba'i don de rten zhu ba ye shes kyi ro
NK066(chu)001:7947: dang ldan pa la brten nas thob pa'i phyir dang
NK066(chu)001:7948: / de byin kyang da dung bla ma yab yum
NK066(chu)001:7949: gyis myong ba ltar slob ma la mi snang ba'i
NK066(chu)001:7950: / phyir dang / gnas skabs su theg pa 'og
NK066(chu)001:7951: ma la gsang ba'i spyod pa yin pa'i phyir gsang
NK066(chu)001:7952: / phyir dang / ba'o // de bskur bas dus
NK066(chu)001:7953: ni nus dbang thob nas steng sgo rnam par grol
NK066(chu)001:7954: ba'i rdzogs rim la slob pa'i sngon du'o //
NK066(chu)001:7955: gnyis pa ye shes rang gnas kyi bskur thabs ni /
NK066(chu)001:7956: shes rab ma bcu drug lon pa dang bu nyid
NK066(chu)001:7957: sngar bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas rol pas h+aum gi
NK066(chu)001:7958: rnam pa'i nyi zla byang chub kyi sems rgyun dga'
NK066(chu)001:7959: bzhi'i 'gros kyis rdo rje nas pad+ma'i lam du dbab
NK066(chu)001:7960: ste bzung ba'i thabs kyis bskyil ba de nyid /
NK066(chu)001:7961: bzhag gnas gsang rtsa phan tshun du bsnol mar bkod pas thig le gnyis rtse 'phrad pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:7962: bstim gnas ni rig pa'i pho brang ste /
NK066(chu)001:7964: gnas ni rig pa'i pho brang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:7966: de'i tshe mtshon byed dpe'i bde ba ni byang sems
NK066(chu)001:7967: gnyis shor gnyis mnyam gyi tshe lhan skyes kyi dga'
NK066(chu)001:7968: ba rtog bcas su myong zhing /
NK066(chu)001:7969: des mtshon bya sems nyid don dam 'od gsal gyi ye shes su bsgyur ba ste /
NK066(chu)001:7971: rjes su 'jug pa'i phyag rgya nyid //
NK066(chu)001:7972: zil pa'i thig le sngon rdo rje'i lam bzhin //
NK066(chu)001:7973: bcu drug phyed phyed thig le gcig /
NK066(chu)001:7974: phan tshun 'god pa'i stobs kyis bstim //
NK066(chu)001:7975: bde ba gnyis pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK066(chu)001:7976: gsum pa'i ye shes dkyil 'khor du //
NK066(chu)001:7977: gsal bar shar bas dkyil 'khor gyur pa'i sgra //
NK066(chu)001:7980: de la ye shes rang gnas kyi dbang zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:7981: nyams su myong bya'i ye shes de rang la gsal ba'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:7982: rang gnas mtshungs ldan gyi rgyud de shes rab ma'i
NK066(chu)001:7983: lhan cig byed rgyu la brten nas rgyud la myong
NK066(chu)001:7984: ba'i phyir shes rab ye shes kyi dbang zhes grags
NK066(chu)001:7985: so // de bskur ba'i dus ni /
NK066(chu)001:7986: gsang dbang thob nas 'og sgo bde ba chen po'i rdzogs rim la bslab pa'i sngon du'o //
NK066(chu)001:7987: gsum pa dbyer med bde chen gyi dbang ni /
NK066(chu)001:7988: shes rab ma lo bcu gnyis ma dang bu nyid
NK066(chu)001:7989: snyoms par zhugs pa'i yas babs kyi dga' bzhi'i 'gros
NK066(chu)001:7990: re re la'ang / dga' ba bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug dang /
NK066(chu)001:7991: de la nyi zla zung 'brel gyis mtshan so gnyis dang /
NK066(chu)001:7992: zla ba'i thig le re re'ang ye shes lnga'i ro
NK066(chu)001:7993: dang ldan pa'i phyir dpe byad brgyad cu rdzogs shing
NK066(chu)001:7995: de'i tshe rtog med yum gyi mkha' gsang ba'i 'og
NK066(chu)001:7996: min du 'khyil ba las rtsa kha kha mu kha'i
NK066(chu)001:7997: rtse nas bzlog pa'i thabs kyis ldog ste /
NK066(chu)001:7998: 'khor lo bzhir mas brtan gyi dga' ba bcu drug nyams su myong ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:7999: de'i dus na le lag las /
NK066(chu)001:8000: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod med rdzogs //
NK066(chu)001:8001: kun tu 'od gsal pad+ma can yang rdzogs //
NK066(chu)001:8002: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen thabs dang ldan //
NK066(chu)001:8003: zhes pas dga' ba bcu drug gi dga' ba'i dga' ba sogs bzhi ni tshogs lam /
NK066(chu)001:8004: mchog dag'i dga' ba ni sbyor lam /
NK066(chu)001:8005: mchog dag'i mchog dga' ni mthong lam /
NK066(chu)001:8006: de nas mchog dag'i dga' bral sogs dgu ni sgom lam sa dgu /
NK066(chu)001:8007: dga' ba bcu drug gi mtha'i lhan cig skyes dag'i
NK066(chu)001:8008: lhan skyes dga' ba ni nyi zla byang chub kyi
NK066(chu)001:8009: sems zung du 'brel ba'i brdas snang stong gi mthas
NK066(chu)001:8010: ma bsgribs par gsal ba'i phyir bcu gcig kun tu
NK066(chu)001:8011: 'od kyi sa'o // de'i yon tan gyi thig les
NK066(chu)001:8012: lus thams cad du khyab cing brtan pas 'khor ba'i
NK066(chu)001:8013: skyon gyis ma gos pa'i phyir bcu gnyis pad+ma can
NK066(chu)001:8014: 'od kyi sa'o // gyi sa dang / rtog tshogs
NK066(chu)001:8015: thams cad sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK066(chu)001:8016: rang snang ba'i phyir bcu gsum pa yi ge 'khor
NK066(chu)001:8017: lo'i sa rdzogs nas bden pa dbyer med blo'i spyod
NK066(chu)001:8018: yul dang bral ba'i gnas lugs mngon du byas pa
NK066(chu)001:8019: ni bde ba chen po'i dbang ste /
NK066(chu)001:8021: rdo rje nyi ma thabs kyi rgya //
NK066(chu)001:8022: phung sogs phyag rgya'i tshogs dang ldan //
NK066(chu)001:8023: de zla bsil byed shes rab ye shes kyi dngos //
NK066(chu)001:8025: dus gcig ro mnyam thig le che //
NK066(chu)001:8026: sum cu rtsa gnyis mtshan rdzogs shing //
NK066(chu)001:8027: zla ba'i ye shes lnga bcu drug /
NK066(chu)001:8028: dpe byad la sogs dpag tu med //
NK066(chu)001:8029: sems shes mngon par shes dang ldan //
NK066(chu)001:8030: sems lnga'i mtha' ma 'gro 'ong shes pas na /
NK066(chu)001:8033: lhan cig skyes dag'i gnas nas log pa thim pa'i sgra //
NK066(chu)001:8034: mtha' gnyis ma gos pad+ma can //
NK066(chu)001:8035: sprul pa'i gnas nas bkye ba yis //
NK066(chu)001:8036: bzhi bcu lnga sogs mtha' yas kun //
NK066(chu)001:8037: rang bzhin nyid nas rang gsal ba //
NK066(chu)001:8038: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lor brjod //
NK066(chu)001:8040: de la bde ba chen po'i dbang zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:8041: sngar gyi lhan skyes kyi bde ba'i ye shes 'dir
NK066(chu)001:8042: rgyud la shin tu brtan byed kyi dbang yin pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8044: gnyis med bde ba mtha' bral ba //
NK066(chu)001:8045: grub dang bde ba gcig pas bde //
NK066(chu)001:8046: ngo bo 'gyur med brtan par brjod //
NK066(chu)001:8048: de bskur dus phyi ni sa bcu mthar phyin pa'i dus dang /
NK066(chu)001:8049: nang ni mthur du rgyu ba sa rlung gi dus su ste /
NK066(chu)001:8051: dus ni phyi dang nang gnyis te /
NK066(chu)001:8052: phyi rol sa bcu mthar phyin dus //
NK066(chu)001:8053: shes rab ye shes thob pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:8054: nang gi sa rlung rgyu ba'i dus //
NK066(chu)001:8056: 'dir zab dbang gsum ni ye shes dngos su rgyud
NK066(chu)001:8057: la skye bar byed pa mthar thug gi dbang yin
NK066(chu)001:8058: pa'i phyir bsam rgyud dang bsgrag tshig la ltos pa
NK066(chu)001:8060: zhes rgyal ba g.yung gsungs pa ltar 'dir yang ma bris mod /
NK066(chu)001:8061: 'on kyang las rgya la brten te dngos dbang bskur
NK066(chu)001:8062: ba dang len par nus pa'i blo stobs can la
NK066(chu)001:8064: de mi nus pa ting nge 'dzin dang byang sems
NK066(chu)001:8065: bdud rtsi'i ril bu tsam la brten dgos pa'i gang
NK066(chu)001:8066: zag la ni nges par bsam rgyud dang bsgrag tshig
NK066(chu)001:8067: dgos te / de'i phyir de dag dbang gi gal por shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:8068: de 'dra ba'i gang zag la dbang gi dkyil 'khor
NK066(chu)001:8069: kyang yab yum gyi mkha' gsang mtshon byed sor bzhi
NK066(chu)001:8070: pa'i pad+ma dang / mdzub gang ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK066(chu)001:8071: de gnyis la rigs lnga yab yum gyi mtshan ma dgod par gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:8073: shin tu phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK066(chu)001:8076: sor bzhi pa'am mdzub gang tshad //
NK066(chu)001:8078: yang 'dir g.yung gi zhi ba'i dbang chog tu /
NK066(chu)001:8079: deng sang chos 'di'i zab dbang gsum dngos su bskur ba'i bka' chad nas phyag len du mi mdzad /
NK066(chu)001:8082: zhi ba'i zab dbang gi bka' chad pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8083: khro bo'i ma chad pa'i rnam dbye 'byed pa mi rigs te /
NK066(chu)001:8084: da lta'i khro bo'i dbang chog tu zab dbang gsum 'byung ba ni gnubs rat+na sh+r+ais kha skong gis /
NK066(chu)001:8085: sgrol ma pa'i yig cha gtsang mar sngar drangs pa'i tshig don de kho na yod pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8086: dngos su zhes pa'i tshig gi nus pas 'dir dngos
NK066(chu)001:8087: dbang rten can du bskur ba'i bka' chad gsungs par
NK066(chu)001:8089: gal te sgrol g.yung gnyis la rgyun mi bzhugs pa'i dbang du btang nas /
NK066(chu)001:8090: 'dir brgyud par se ston bzhugs pa'i phyir zab dbang gnyis ka'i rgyun yod dgos te /
NK066(chu)001:8091: dam pa ya ses skyo bye ma lung pa la
NK066(chu)001:8092: rten can dang sbas don rnal 'byor la rten med
NK066(chu)001:8093: du nod pa'i rgyun da lta zab dbang zu lung
NK066(chu)001:8094: nas brgyud pa 'di khungs zab ces se ston nyid
NK066(chu)001:8095: gces spras su mdzad pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8096: 'di khungs zab ces pas sgrol ma ba'i lugs lo
NK066(chu)001:8097: chen dang rog tshang du gsan pa la'ang rgyun yod
NK066(chu)001:8098: par shugs kyis 'phangs pa'i phyir snyam mo //
NK066(chu)001:8099: des na tshig rkyen des phyis kyi bla ma dag
NK066(chu)001:8100: gis zo lung ba'i zhi ba'i zab dbang rgyun bcad
NK066(chu)001:8101: bar mngon te bstan pa'i sku chag tu zad do
NK066(chu)001:8102: // 'on kyang bdag gi rje bla ma la ni
NK066(chu)001:8103: gtsang brgyud chad kyang mdo khams kyi brgyud pa rnam
NK066(chu)001:8109: snga rabs pa kha cig na re /
NK066(chu)001:8110: zab dbang ni nus pa dngos su 'jog byed yiin
NK066(chu)001:8111: pa'i phyir nus dbang du 'du bas grangs bco lnga
NK066(chu)001:8113: de ltar kho bos dbang gcig kho na ste /
NK066(chu)001:8114: zab nus gnyis ka phan dbang gi khongs su 'du ba'i phyir te /
NK066(chu)001:8115: bdag gzhan gyi don dngos su sgrub pa'i sgo nas phan par byed pa'i dbang yin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8118: gnyags t+aika pa bum dbang dang /
NK066(chu)001:8119: gsang dbang gnyis su 'du bar 'dod pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8121: zab dbang gsum gcig tu byas te bcu drug tu 'dod pa gnyis ka mi rigs te /
NK066(chu)001:8123: dang po sa bon 'jog pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:8124: zhes sogs kyis gnod pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8125: rang lugs sngar bshad pa ltar rtsa ba lnga las phye ba'i dbang bco brgyad du shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:8128: nus dbang lnga yang gsang dbang gi bye brag tu byas te /
NK066(chu)001:8129: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK066(chu)001:8131: byang chub sems kyi thig les dbang bskur ba spyir bstan pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8132: de'i yan lag nus dbang so sor bskur ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:8133: nyan byed 'khor lo'i zhes sogs kyis bstan pa'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:8134: bskur ba'i rim pa'ang de bzhin no gsungs pa mi
NK066(chu)001:8135: rigs te lung rigs man ngag gsum kas gnod pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8137: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK066(chu)001:8138: zhes pa'i skabs kyi thar lo 'gyur las /
NK066(chu)001:8139: dad dang brtson 'grus brtul zhugs la //
NK066(chu)001:8140: phan dbang nus pa'i dbang bskur bya //
NK066(chu)001:8141: shes rab dbang bskur rim par bcas //
NK066(chu)001:8142: brtse bas chud ma zos par sbyin //
NK066(chu)001:8144: drangs ma thag pa'i bshad rgyud rdo rje'i lung gis kyang gnod pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8147: ngo bo snod kyi mtshan nyid kyis //
NK066(chu)001:8148: dbye ba rnam pa lnga ru 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8149: bdag phan nus pa gnyis ka'i las //
NK066(chu)001:8150: nying lag lnga phrag gnyis dang gcig /
NK066(chu)001:8151: de dag phyi rol don shes bya //
NK066(chu)001:8152: bde sogs spyod pa gsang bar 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8153: rang gnas rang rig ye shes gsal //
NK066(chu)001:8154: rang bzhin lhun grub de bzhin nyid //
NK066(chu)001:8155: mngon byas rgyu 'bras dbyer med pas //
NK066(chu)001:8156: yang dag rdzogs pa'i bde chen po //
NK066(chu)001:8157: rdo rje'i sku phyir bstan pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:8160: dad dang brtson 'grus gsum ldan dang //
NK066(chu)001:8161: brtul zhugs gsum ldan slob ma la //
NK066(chu)001:8162: zhes snod rim gsungs pas kyang gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:8164: rgyud du go rim de ltar byung ba ltar bskur dgos na /
NK066(chu)001:8165: phan dbang kyang nus dbang gi rjes su bskur dgos par 'gyur te /
NK066(chu)001:8166: rgyu mtshan mtshungs pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8167: thog mar gsang ba b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs
NK066(chu)001:8168: rjes lus dkyil du nus dbang bskur ba'i go rim
NK066(chu)001:8169: yang mi rigs pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:8171: 'jam dpal dmar po'i dbang rtsar yang /
NK066(chu)001:8172: gsang dbang gi bye brag tu nus dbang byung ba'i phyir skyon med do zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:8174: de ni zab mo gsang ba'i dbang la nus dbang
NK066(chu)001:8175: rdzogs par ston pa'i che ba brjod nas dbugs dbyung
NK066(chu)001:8176: ba ste / dbang gi gal po las /
NK066(chu)001:8177: rigs kyi bu khyod deng phan chad //
NK066(chu)001:8178: phyi dang nang dang gsang ba yi //
NK066(chu)001:8179: zhes sogs gsungs pa dang tshig don gnyis ka gcig pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8180: gal por bshad pa de dag rgyud 'dir dngos su
NK066(chu)001:8181: gsungs pa'i zab dbang du 'chad rigs so snyam na
NK066(chu)001:8184: nus dang phan pa'i dbang thob nas //
NK066(chu)001:8185: brtul zhugs ldan pa'i bu mchog la //
NK066(chu)001:8186: zhes sogs kyis gnod pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:8187: des na sangs rgyas gsang ba'i nges 'byed dang rdo
NK066(chu)001:8188: rje las rim sogs su khrigs rim gsal bar gsungs
NK066(chu)001:8189: pa rnams dang 'gal ba'i phyir khyed kyi lugs 'di
NK066(chu)001:8192: 'o na dbang bco brgyad po de dag dbang bzhir 'dus sam ma 'dus she na /
NK066(chu)001:8194: 'dir spyi'i sdom ni dbang lngar bsdu ste /
NK066(chu)001:8195: nyang ston rig pa'i 'byung gnas kyi sras po'i dbang bzhi so sor bsdu ba'i yig cha yod kyang /
NK066(chu)001:8196: de ni gsar ma'i bzhed pa 'dir bkod pa yin pas mi 'thad de zer na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:8199: rgyud phyi ma'i dri ba bcu gsum par /
NK066(chu)001:8200: dbang bskur ba yi don yang ci //
NK066(chu)001:8202: slob dpon gsang ba shes rab dang //
NK066(chu)001:8203: de ma thag pa bzhi pa ste //
NK066(chu)001:8204: rnam rtog dri ma dag bya'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:8205: dbang bskur rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK066(chu)001:8208: phan nus kyi dbang bco lnga po ni bum pa'i dbang du bsdu ste /
NK066(chu)001:8209: de thob pas lam bskyed rim bsgom pa'i snod rung du byas pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8210: de ltar yang khog gzhung las /
NK066(chu)001:8211: phyi nang dkyil 'khor rnam gsum du //
NK066(chu)001:8212: rim par bskur ba dang po ru //
NK066(chu)001:8213: ri mo bzhengs gsol phan nus bskur //
NK066(chu)001:8214: bskyed pa'i rim pa bslab pa'i dus //
NK066(chu)001:8216: de yang phan dbang thob pas phyi dkyil la brten
NK066(chu)001:8217: pa'i drang don gyi bskyed rim thun mong pa'i snod
NK066(chu)001:8218: rung du byas pa ste nges 'byed las /
NK066(chu)001:8219: phyi rol drang don mnyan du rung //
NK066(chu)001:8221: de'i steng du mnyan bsgom gyi dbang gnyis kyis nang
NK066(chu)001:8222: rang bzhin gyis grub pa'i lus dkyil la brten pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8223: nges don gyi bskyed rim mnyan bsgom nus pa dang
NK066(chu)001:8225: rdo rje rgyal po ni rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dngos dang /
NK066(chu)001:8226: 'chad phrin gnyis de'i byed las yin pas /
NK066(chu)001:8227: de ltar na rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang thob
NK066(chu)001:8228: nas bum dbang dang rjes su 'brel ba'i lam thams
NK066(chu)001:8229: cad la spyod pa'i bdag por gyur pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8231: rim pa ltar gsang dbang dang /
NK066(chu)001:8233: tshig dbang rnams su dngos su 'dus par zad la /
NK066(chu)001:8234: de gsum thob pas rdzogs rim steng 'og gi sgo
NK066(chu)001:8235: dang bde ba chen po de kho na nyid bsgom
NK066(chu)001:8236: pa'i snod rung du byas pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8237: de yang khog gzhung gi lung de'i 'phros las /
NK066(chu)001:8238: rdzogs rim gdams ngag sbyor dus su //
NK066(chu)001:8239: gsang dbang bskur ba sor bzhi pa //
NK066(chu)001:8240: rol pa 'jug dus gsang ba yi //
NK066(chu)001:8241: dkyil 'khor brtan la shes rab sbyin //
NK066(chu)001:8243: gsum pa rjes kyi rim pa la bdun te /
NK066(chu)001:8244: dbang rtags rdor dril byin zhing ru'i bka' nyan par bsgo ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:8245: bum chu blud cing brtan par byas la smon lam gdab pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8246: dbang rdzas kyi rab gnas bsdu zhing ci 'byor pa'i yon gyis bu'i lus bslu ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:8247: ru mchod cing yon dbul ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:8248: lhag ma dang brtan ma bskyang ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:8249: dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing rdul tshon gshegs pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8250: las rjes shis par bya ba rnams te dbang byang las shes par bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:8251: lnga pa dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK066(chu)001:8253: slob dpon mnyes par ma byas shing //
NK066(chu)001:8254: dbang rnams thob par ma byas par //
NK066(chu)001:8255: nyan pa la sogs brtson pa ni //
NK066(chu)001:8259: dkyil 'khor du ni ma zhugs shing //
NK066(chu)001:8260: dam tshig rnams ni spangs pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:8261: gsang ba'i de nyid mi shes pas //
NK066(chu)001:8262: bsgrubs kyang ci yang mi 'grub bo //
NK066(chu)001:8265: dper na bu tsha med pa'i khyiim //
NK066(chu)001:8266: shi ba tsam gyis stongs pa nyid //
NK066(chu)001:8267: de bzhin dbang dang bral ba ni //
NK066(chu)001:8268: ye shes kun gyis stong pa nyid //
NK066(chu)001:8271: gsang ba nyams las ltung 'jigs pas //
NK066(chu)001:8272: so ma btang ba'i rdza spyod ltar //
NK066(chu)001:8273: 'gyur ba gsang ba'i rgyud kun ltos //
NK066(chu)001:8277: dus 'di phyin chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK066(chu)001:8278: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:8279: tshe ring bde ba phun sum tshogs //
NK066(chu)001:8280: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8282: he ru ka mngon byung las /
NK066(chu)001:8283: dkyil 'khor bdag po mthong nas ni //
NK066(chu)001:8284: cung zad de ni mi 'grub med //
NK066(chu)001:8285: sdig pa kun las rnam par grol //
NK066(chu)001:8286: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8288: lnga pa mi 'da' ba dam tshig la drug las /
NK066(chu)001:8290: gzhan sel ngan song dang theg dman du mi ltung zhing /
NK066(chu)001:8291: don gnyer zhing sa gshin po la sa bon btab
NK066(chu)001:8292: na 'bras bu smin par 'gyur ba ltar lam dang
NK066(chu)001:8293: 'bras bu'i gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ste /
NK066(chu)001:8294: lam gyi 'bad pa don can du byed pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8296: sngags 'chang rnams don yod par bya ba'i phyir dam tshig chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK066(chu)001:8299: bsrung bya'i don khyad par can la sems pa rgyun dang bcas pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:8301: gsang sgor zhugs pa thams cad kyis //
NK066(chu)001:8302: sgo gsum rang gi bsrung bya la //
NK066(chu)001:8303: rgyal po'i bka' rtags ji lta bar //
NK066(chu)001:8304: mi 'bral sdom pa de ngo bo //
NK066(chu)001:8308: yal gam bcas pa'i tha tshig dang /
NK066(chu)001:8311: don ji ltar bcas pa las 'da' bar bya ba ma yin pa'i phyir dam tshig ste /
NK066(chu)001:8313: 'da' dka' rdo rje dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK066(chu)001:8316: nges tshig skyon yon skabs kyis bsgyur //
NK066(chu)001:8318: bsrungs pa'i phan yon gyis dam tshig tu bzhag pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:8320: dam pa rnams kyi dgongs pa la //
NK066(chu)001:8321: dbang du byin rlabs thob pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:8322: dam pa'i tshul bzhin nges spyad na //
NK066(chu)001:8323: mi mthun tshogs rnams tshig par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8325: gal te de las 'das na ngan song gi gnas
NK066(chu)001:8326: su rgyud tshig par 'gyur ba'i nyes dmigs kyis dam
NK066(chu)001:8330: rdo rje can yang tshig par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8333: mi 'da' dam pa mchog gyur pa //
NK066(chu)001:8334: 'das par gyur na tshig par bshad //
NK066(chu)001:8337: thob byed kyi cho ga dang /
NK066(chu)001:8340: nyams na bskang ba'i thabs so //
NK066(chu)001:8342: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa'i cho ga kho na
NK066(chu)001:8343: las thob kyi gzhan las ni dam tshig dang sdom
NK066(chu)001:8344: pa med de / brtul zhugs tsam du zad do //
NK066(chu)001:8345: thob pa'i dus la sngon gyi mkhan po rnams kyis
NK066(chu)001:8346: dbang gi snga rol du sdom pa bzung ba'i cho
NK066(chu)001:8347: ga lan gsum brjod pa'i cha tha ma'i mjug tu
NK066(chu)001:8349: gal te 'di'i skabs su gang bzung ba'i sdom pa de nyid mi skye zer na /
NK066(chu)001:8350: 'o na so byang gi sdom chog las kyang de dag mi skye bar mtshungs te /
NK066(chu)001:8351: gzhan gnyis la skye ba'i nus pa yod pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8352: 'di la med pa'i lung rigs tshad ma med pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:8353: 'di la skye ba'i tshad ma yod de /
NK066(chu)001:8354: sdom pa ni skye mi skye gnyis las mi 'da' la /
NK066(chu)001:8355: mi skye ba'i tshad ma med pa nyid kyis skye bar grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8357: rgyal bas cho ga bshad pa'ang nus med du 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:8359: lo ts+aa ba chen po rong zom gyis mdzad pa'i sdom chog las /
NK066(chu)001:8360: dang po thun mong gi sdom pa nos nas /
NK066(chu)001:8361: de nas khyad par gyi sdom pa nos te /
NK066(chu)001:8362: dkyil 'khor la zhugs nas dbang thob par byas la /
NK066(chu)001:8363: dngos grub kyi snod du 'gyur bar bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:8366: rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig dang sdom pa tha dag bzung grub pa ni ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:8367: da dung dbang dam tshig dang sdom pa mi 'dra ba du ma 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8368: dper na dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa thob pas so
NK066(chu)001:8369: thar gyi sdom pa thob pa'i grangs su 'gro mod
NK066(chu)001:8370: kyang / so thar gyi sdom pa'i yan lag tshang ba ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:8371: da dung dge tshul dang dge slong gi sdom pa blang du yod pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8373: thun mong gi sdom pa len lugs ltar 'jug pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8374: skabs su smin byed kyi rten sdom ldan du bya
NK066(chu)001:8375: ba'i phyir khas blangs kyi sgo nas sdom pa bzung
NK066(chu)001:8377: slar dbang blangs pa'i tshe na sdom pa'i nus pa gong 'phel du 'gro dgos te /
NK066(chu)001:8378: kun mkhyen chen po'i t+wi ka'i dgongs pa ltar dam
NK066(chu)001:8379: tshig dang sdom pa gnyis ngo bo gcig la ldog
NK066(chu)001:8380: pa tha dad pa'i gnad kyis so //
NK066(chu)001:8382: cho gas sems rgyud kyi yon tan dge ba'i sa
NK066(chu)001:8383: bon gsos btab pa'i cha de sangs rgyas kun gyi
NK066(chu)001:8384: gsang ba'i rdo rje gsum 'dzin pa'i cha nas dam
NK066(chu)001:8386: rang gi rgyud sdom pa'i cha nas sdom pa'ang yin pa'i phyir te /
NK066(chu)001:8387: dper na bum pa nyid byas pa'ang yin la mi rtag pa'ang yin pa bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:8388: de ltar yang rgyud phyi ma las /
NK066(chu)001:8389: gang zhig nan tan las mi 'gong //
NK066(chu)001:8390: rmi lam du'ang dam tshig brjod //
NK066(chu)001:8391: dam bca' ba ni sdom par 'dod //
NK066(chu)001:8394: de ltar sum brgya drug cu rnams //
NK066(chu)001:8395: bdag gi rdo rje mchog gsum pos //
NK066(chu)001:8396: log par mi gtong sdom pa'i dngos //
NK066(chu)001:8397: sa gzhi lta bur gsungs pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:8399: 'dir 'jug pa'i skabs su dbang byang las sdom pa
NK066(chu)001:8400: so sor dmigs phye nas gzung ba ma byung na'ang
NK066(chu)001:8401: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig byin pa nyid sdom
NK066(chu)001:8404: rang bzhin 'bru gsum sku gsung thugs //
NK066(chu)001:8405: gzi byin ldan par byin brlabs la //
NK066(chu)001:8406: dam tshig sdom pa mchog ces bshad //
NK066(chu)001:8408: gnyis pa thob bya'i ngo bo la //
NK066(chu)001:8409: dam tshig gi rang bzhin dang /
NK066(chu)001:8411: dbye ngo dngos gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8413: rtsa ba dang yan lag la sogs pa'i dam tshig
NK066(chu)001:8414: ji snyed pa thams cad rang sems gnyis su med
NK066(chu)001:8416: de'i don las de bzhin gshegs pa kun kyang 'da' bar mi mdzad pa'i bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8418: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK066(chu)001:8419: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK066(chu)001:8422: dam tshig dam tshig ces bya ba //
NK066(chu)001:8423: gud na yod pa ma yin te //
NK066(chu)001:8424: rang gi sems nyid dam tshig yin //
NK066(chu)001:8427: spyod sgo yangs pa'i che ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:8430: gnas lugs la rtogs goms kyi gdeng dang ldan na mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig la gnas pa'am /
NK066(chu)001:8431: bla na med pa'i theg par nges pa zhes bya ste /
NK066(chu)001:8432: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa ji spyad kyang phyogs 'dzin gyi blo mi skye ba'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8433: de 'dra ba'i gdeng gis zin pa'i gang zag des /
NK066(chu)001:8434: las dang nyon mongs pa gang la spyad kyang sgyu
NK066(chu)001:8435: ma'i sprul pa la spyod pa ltar ma zhen pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8436: phyir / des sgrib pa dang bag chags mi gsog
NK066(chu)001:8437: pa'i steng du tshogs gnyis rdzogs par 'gyur ba dang
NK066(chu)001:8438: phyir / / so byang phyi rgyud kyi tshul khrims
NK066(chu)001:8439: dang sdom pa thams cad kyang rnam par dag par
NK066(chu)001:8441: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK066(chu)001:8442: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang /
NK066(chu)001:8443: byas la mi sogs tshogs 'gyur te //
NK066(chu)001:8444: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum tshogs //
NK066(chu)001:8448: bla ma mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK066(chu)001:8449: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i skabs su spyir sdom pa la /
NK066(chu)001:8452: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pa gsum ste /
NK066(chu)001:8454: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK066(chu)001:8457: rje bla ma'i gter byon thugs thig gi dbang byang las /
NK066(chu)001:8458: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK066(chu)001:8459: rig 'dzin nang gi sdom pa'i tshogs //
NK066(chu)001:8462: rnam pa 'gal la ngo bo tshang ba dang gnas gyur pa'i phyir 'dus shing rnam par dag pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8463: rnam pa ji ltar 'gal zhe na //
NK066(chu)001:8466: gang gi rjes su bslab pa'i dang //
NK066(chu)001:8467: dngos gzhi gtso bo'i dbang du byas pa'i dang //
NK066(chu)001:8468: ched du bya ba'i khyad par ro //
NK066(chu)001:8470: so thar ji srid 'tsho'i bar du dang /
NK066(chu)001:8471: byang sdom snying po byang chub la thug gi bar dang /
NK066(chu)001:8472: sngags sdom 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du khas len par ro //
NK066(chu)001:8475: sa chen po la zhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK066(chu)001:8476: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rjes su bslab pa'i khyad par ro //
NK066(chu)001:8478: phyi lus ngag gi spang ba bdun la bslab pa'i spyor ba ni so thar /
NK066(chu)001:8479: nang yid kyi las gsum gtso bor spang ba'i snying rje la bslab pa ni byang sdom /
NK066(chu)001:8480: rtogs goms kyi gdeng gis mnyam pa'i don las mi 'da' ba ni sngags sdom mo //
NK066(chu)001:8484: gzhan don rlabs po che la dmigs pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:8490: so thar ni gzhan la gnod pa'i sbyor ba las log pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8491: byang sdom ni de'i steng du phan 'dogs pa'i sbyor ba la zhugs pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8493: de gnyis ka la zhugs pa'i steng du sangs rgyas
NK066(chu)001:8494: kyi mdzad pa nyams su blangs te mnyam pa chen
NK066(chu)001:8495: po'i ngang nas gzhan don rtsol med du mdzad pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8496: thabs la mkhas pas thamsasa cad tshang ba'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8497: rgyu mtshan des sngags kyi dam tshig ma nyams par
NK066(chu)001:8498: thub na 'og ma'i 'dul sdom rnams zhar la thub
NK066(chu)001:8499: pas logs su bsrung mi dgos te /
NK066(chu)001:8500: bre gsum tshang na de nang du do mi tshang
NK066(chu)001:8501: ba'i dogs pa med pa ltar yon tan yar ldan
NK066(chu)001:8503: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK066(chu)001:8504: theg chen dam tshig la gnas na //
NK066(chu)001:8506: bsrung ba med par thub pas na //
NK066(chu)001:8507: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK066(chu)001:8510: gnyis pa gnas gyur pas rnam par dag pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:8511: nyon mongs pa rang ga mar spyad pa'i sgo gsum gyi las kyis 'khor bar 'ching mod /
NK066(chu)001:8512: de nyid shes rab dang snying rje phyogs gcig gi
NK066(chu)001:8513: rtsis bzung ste bya ba ma yin pa spong ba'i
NK066(chu)001:8514: sdom pa la zhugs pa na mtho ris dang thar
NK066(chu)001:8516: de nyid thabs dang shes rab chen po'i rtsis zin
NK066(chu)001:8517: pas gzhan don gyi bya ba la spyad pa na
NK066(chu)001:8518: bla na med pa'i byang chub tu grol ba'i rgyur
NK066(chu)001:8519: 'gyur ba dang / de nyid kyang thabs shes chen
NK066(chu)001:8520: po'i yang chen pos zin par spyad na rdzogs pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8521: byang chub 'bad rtsol med pa lhun gyis 'grub par
NK066(chu)001:8522: 'gyur ba dang / 'gyur te / dper na zangs
NK066(chu)001:8523: rdo bzhu bas zangs de la rtsis btab na gser
NK066(chu)001:8524: du 'gyur ba bzhin sgo gsum gyi bya ba gzhi
NK066(chu)001:8525: gcig la'ang thabs che chung gis gong ma gong mar
NK066(chu)001:8527: de bas na so thar gyi gzhan gnod gzhi bcas
NK066(chu)001:8528: spang ba dang byang sdom gyis gzhan la phan 'dogs
NK066(chu)001:8529: pa'i ldog cha gnyis po de rdzas gong 'phel gyi
NK066(chu)001:8530: tshul gyis sngags kyi sdom rdzas su ngo bo gnas
NK066(chu)001:8531: 'gyur zhing / mnyam pa chen po'i thabs kyis ma
NK066(chu)001:8532: zin pa'i tha mal snang zhen gyi ldog cha re
NK066(chu)001:8533: yod pa de rtsa ba nas btang nas mnyam pa
NK066(chu)001:8534: chen po'i thabs khyad par can du 'gyur ba yin
NK066(chu)001:8535: 'gyur zhing / te / snang bas mun pa bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:8536: de'i tshul gyis mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig tu
NK066(chu)001:8537: 'og ma'i 'dul sdom rnams 'dus shing rnam par dag
NK066(chu)001:8538: pa yin no // 'dir kha cig 'di snyam du /
NK066(chu)001:8539: sdom pa 'og ma gnyis gong mar 'dus shing rdzogs pa mi 'thad de /
NK066(chu)001:8540: so thar gyi gzhan gnod gzhi bcas spong ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:8541: byang sdom gyi gzhan la phan 'dogs pa'i ldog cha
NK066(chu)001:8542: gnyis sngags sdom gyis mi spang ba'i dam tshig dang
NK066(chu)001:8543: dngos su 'gal bar snang ba'i phyir zhe na /
NK066(chu)001:8545: de la so so thar pa'i sdom pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:8546: phas pham bzhi byung na rtsa ba zhig par gsungs pa las /
NK066(chu)001:8547: 'dir gnas lugs rtogs pa'i gdeng gis zin na ji
NK066(chu)001:8548: ltar spyad kyang mi gos pas ngo bo yar ldan
NK066(chu)001:8549: dang slar tshogs su 'gyur ba'i phyir yon tan yar
NK066(chu)001:8551: bye brag tu srog gcod pa ni //
NK066(chu)001:8552: yod med dbu ma mi dmigs shing //
NK066(chu)001:8554: bdag gzhan gnyis ka sems nyid du gsal zhing /
NK066(chu)001:8555: de don dam par yod med dbu ma'i mtha' gsum dang bral la /
NK066(chu)001:8556: kun rdzob tu snang yang rang rgyud pas stong par rtogs na /
NK066(chu)001:8557: srog gcod pa ltar snang yang gcad bya gcod byed
NK066(chu)001:8558: ma grub cing gcad do ba'i 'du shes med pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8559: phyir nyes pas mi gos shing /
NK066(chu)001:8560: zhing bcu la sogs pa las ngan gyi rgyun gcod
NK066(chu)001:8561: pa'i phyir bsgral bas tshogs gnyis rdzogs pas na srog
NK066(chu)001:8562: gcod spong ba'i sdom pa'ii ngo bo dang yon tan
NK066(chu)001:8564: de ltar yang dkon brtsegs kyi nye ba 'khor gyis zhus pa'i skabs las /
NK066(chu)001:8565: ji ltar sgyu ma mkhan gyis 'jig rten na //
NK066(chu)001:8566: sems can brgya phrag mang po sprul byas te //
NK066(chu)001:8567: sprul pa de dag thams cad bsad gyur kyang //
NK066(chu)001:8568: sgyu ma de dag bsad pa yod min ltar //
NK066(chu)001:8569: 'gro ba 'di dag sgyu ma'i rang bzhin te //
NK066(chu)001:8570: 'di la mtha' ni nam yang dmigs su med //
NK066(chu)001:8571: gang dag de ltar mtha' yas med byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:8572: de dag 'jig rten na ni tshor ba med //
NK066(chu)001:8573: gang dag rang bzhin med chos 'di shes pas //
NK066(chu)001:8574: dpa' bo de dag 'jig rten mya ngan 'da' //
NK066(chu)001:8577: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pas //
NK066(chu)001:8579: chos thams cad ni sems nyid bden pa gnyis kyi
NK066(chu)001:8580: rang bzhin du dbyer med don dam par ma dmigs
NK066(chu)001:8581: shing / tha snyad kun rdzob tu'ang ma grub pas bdag gzhan tha dad med par rtogs pa la /
NK066(chu)001:8582: rdzas dang bdag po gnyis ka gzhan na med pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8583: 'phrul dag'i lha rnams rang gis sprul pa'i longs spyod
NK066(chu)001:8584: len pa ltar ci blangs kyang bdag nyid las mi
NK066(chu)001:8585: 'da' bar shes pas don la blang ba med pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8586: phyir / nyes pas mi gos pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8587: 'jungs pa las blangs te bkren pa la ster ba
NK066(chu)001:8588: sogs gzhan don du 'gyur ba'i phyir ma byin len
NK066(chu)001:8589: spang ba'i sdom pa 'dus shing rnam par dag pa
NK066(chu)001:8591: ji ltar sgyu mas sgyu ma'i nor blangs te //
NK066(chu)001:8592: rmi lam nang bzhin dgos pa der spyad kyang //
NK066(chu)001:8593: de la las med rnam par smin pa med //
NK066(chu)001:8594: de bzhin chags med ye shes 'dir bslabs te //
NK066(chu)001:8595: mya ngan 'das pa dam pa mchog zhir 'gro /
NK066(chu)001:8598: 'jungs pa rnams las nor blangs te //
NK066(chu)001:8599: sems can bkren la byin par bya //
NK066(chu)001:8600: de phyir mi yi bdag po dang //
NK066(chu)001:8601: phyug po rnams kyi nor 'phrog go /
NK066(chu)001:8604: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu la //
NK066(chu)001:8606: chos thams cad med bzhin du log rtog gis brtags
NK066(chu)001:8607: pa'i zhen blo la snang ba ni ngo bo nyid
NK066(chu)001:8608: kyi rdzun no // zhen pa nyid snang ba las
NK066(chu)001:8609: ming tshig tu brtags nas de la bden par 'dzin
NK066(chu)001:8610: pa ni rjes su spyod pa'i rdzun te /
NK066(chu)001:8612: rab 'byor chos thams cad ni rang bzhin gyis dngos po med pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:8613: gang brjod cing snang la brtags pa de dag ni glo bur ba yin pa'i phyir rdzun pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8615: de dag las kyang 'gal bar smra ba ni log pa'i rdzun no //
NK066(chu)001:8616: des na bden pa nyid ma grub na de la ltos pa'i rdzun pa ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8617: chos thams cad la bden par 'dzin pa zad de rdzun par shes pas rdzun smras na'ang /
NK066(chu)001:8619: ji ltar phan pa de ltar smras pas gzhan don
NK066(chu)001:8620: du'ang 'gyur ba'i phyir rdzun smra ba spang ba'i sdom
NK066(chu)001:8621: pa 'dus shing rnam par dag ste /
NK066(chu)001:8623: ji ltar chang ba bcangs te byis pa la //
NK066(chu)001:8624: ston zhing ngag tu yod ces brjod byas nas //
NK066(chu)001:8625: de yis chang ba ston pa mthong nas ni //
NK066(chu)001:8626: byis pa de ni cho nges ngu ba ltar //
NK066(chu)001:8627: de bzhin sangs rgyas bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK066(chu)001:8628: sems can tshul la mkhas shing mkhyen pa rnams //
NK066(chu)001:8629: chos rnams 'di kun gsog gsob mkhyen gyur nas //
NK066(chu)001:8630: 'jig rten dag la yod dang med ces ston //
NK066(chu)001:8633: sems can rnams la phan spyod pas //
NK066(chu)001:8634: rtag tu dam tshig bla ma'i nor //
NK066(chu)001:8635: sems can srog ni bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:8636: rdzun du yang ni smra bar bya //
NK066(chu)001:8639: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:8641: chos thams cad sems nyid du rang snang bas yul sems gnyis med du gsal ba la /
NK066(chu)001:8642: gnyis su zhen cing chags pa'i dus na /
NK066(chu)001:8643: sems nyid kyi ngo bor shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK066(chu)001:8644: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi bsgom pa dang /
NK066(chu)001:8645: thabs kyi spyod pa gsum gyis zin na chags pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8646: ro ye shes su gsal ba'i phyir spyad kyang nyes
NK066(chu)001:8648: 'dzag med kyi ye shes 'grub pa sogs don du 'gyur bas /
NK066(chu)001:8649: mi tshangs spong ba'i sdom pa 'dus la dag pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:8651: ji ltar rmi lam sgyu ma'i rang bzhin du //
NK066(chu)001:8652: skyes bu 'dod bsten de yang de 'dra ste //
NK066(chu)001:8653: ngo bo nyid kyis stong la dngos po med //
NK066(chu)001:8654: las med rnam par smin pa de yod min //
NK066(chu)001:8656: rje bla ma'i gter byon bde gshegs kun 'dus las /
NK066(chu)001:8657: 'di ni tshangs par spyod pa che //
NK066(chu)001:8658: dge slong nyid du yang dag 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8659: de las 'ching ba kun ldan pa'i //
NK066(chu)001:8660: rtags tsam gyi ni ma yin te //
NK066(chu)001:8661: gang phyir rgyal bas chos bstan pa //
NK066(chu)001:8662: rnam pa'i khyad par ma gtogs pa //
NK066(chu)001:8663: nyon mongs spong bar mtshungs pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:8664: gnyen por gyur na thabs shes bya //
NK066(chu)001:8667: sangs rgyas rnams ni mnyes bya dang //
NK066(chu)001:8668: dam tshig rnams ni bsrung ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:8669: gsang sngags rig pas sgrub pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:8670: gzhan gyi bud med bstan par bya //
NK066(chu)001:8672: gnyis pa byang sdom dang mi 'gal ba 'dus tshul ni /
NK066(chu)001:8673: bshad ma thag pas kyang go bar 'gyur mod kyi /
NK066(chu)001:8675: byang sems kyi sdom pa ni /
NK066(chu)001:8676: nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims kyis rgyud bsdam /
NK066(chu)001:8677: gnyen po legs spyod dge ba'i tshogs bsgrub pa dge
NK066(chu)001:8678: ba chos sdud kyis rtogs pa dang yon tan khyad
NK066(chu)001:8679: par can bsgrub / sems can don byed kyis dngos
NK066(chu)001:8680: brgyud kyi sgo nas gzhan la phan 'dogs pa gsum
NK066(chu)001:8682: 'dir yang las dang nyon mongs pa la spyod pa
NK066(chu)001:8683: ltar snang yang ma zhen pa'i phyir don gyi ngo
NK066(chu)001:8684: bo la ci yang byas pa med pa ni sdom
NK066(chu)001:8685: pa'i tshul khrims / gang ltar spyod kyang sgo gsum
NK066(chu)001:8686: rdo rje gsum gyi phyag rgyas btab ste mi 'da'
NK066(chu)001:8687: ba ni dge ba chos sdud /
NK066(chu)001:8688: gzhan don du 'gyur na 'khor ba'i chos gang yang
NK066(chu)001:8689: mi 'dor bar spyod pa ni sems can don byed
NK066(chu)001:8690: de / 'dul sdom thams cad 'dus shing rnam par dag pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8691: gsum pa dbye ngo dngos gtan la dbab ba la /
NK066(chu)001:8692: bsrung du med pa cig car ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK066(chu)001:8693: bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i dam tshig go //
NK066(chu)001:8695: mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig la gnas pas blang dor med pa'i phyir bsrung du med pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:8697: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba yis //
NK066(chu)001:8698: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK066(chu)001:8699: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:8702: rgyud gzhung spyi'i lugs kyi dam tshig mdor bstan /
NK066(chu)001:8703: 'di nyid las gsungs pa'i dam tshig rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK066(chu)001:8705: bde 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:8708: bsrung zhing bsdam par bya ba dag /
NK066(chu)001:8709: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa yi //
NK066(chu)001:8710: rnam par dbye bas gzung bya ste //
NK066(chu)001:8716: so thar byang sems phyi rgyud gsum gyi sdom pa'i bsrung mtshams su grags pa'i dam tshig rnams te /
NK066(chu)001:8718: so so thar dang byang chub sems //
NK066(chu)001:8719: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud rnams las //
NK066(chu)001:8720: bsrung bar bya ba gang gsungs pa //
NK066(chu)001:8721: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig yin //
NK066(chu)001:8725: rtsa bar gyur pa bzhi dag dang //
NK066(chu)001:8726: yan lag nyi shu rtsa lnga ste //
NK066(chu)001:8727: zhes pas rtsa ba sku gsung thugs gsum mam byang sems bsnan pas bzhi dang /
NK066(chu)001:8728: yan lag gi dam tshig lnga tshan lnga ni /
NK066(chu)001:8730: spyad pa lnga dang mi spang lnga //
NK066(chu)001:8731: dang du blang dang sgrub de bzhin //
NK066(chu)001:8732: shes bya lnga rnams thun min bshad //
NK066(chu)001:8735: spyi dang khyad par gyi dam tshig la gnas pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8736: rnal 'byor pas sgrub pa chen po la sogs pa'i
NK066(chu)001:8737: skabs su bsrung ba lhag par bstan pa'i dam tshig
NK066(chu)001:8738: nyi shu ste / zhi ba rtsa rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:8739: gzhung don lhag pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK066(chu)001:8740: rab tu lhag par bsrung bar bya //
NK066(chu)001:8741: gcan gzan rgyal po'i rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku la mi 'tshe /
NK066(chu)001:8743: za ma slob dpon gyi yum la mi spyad /
NK066(chu)001:8745: rin chen lcug dad pa can gyi tshogs mi bcag /
NK066(chu)001:8747: zhun khol lta bu mi mkhas pa dang dkon mchog gi rdzas la mi 'bag /
NK066(chu)001:8749: pad+ma'i ze 'bru kha mi mched kyi yum la mi spyad /
NK066(chu)001:8751: bug brdol snod ngan la gsang sngags mi ster /
NK066(chu)001:8753: don dang mi thod ngan sogs ma brtags pa'i /
NK066(chu)001:8755: shel sgong 'dam du bsub mi bya //
NK066(chu)001:8756: mkhas pa'i yon tan la mi smad /
NK066(chu)001:8757: ma dag snod du dag pa min //
NK066(chu)001:8758: gzungs ma mtshan ngan la mi spyad /
NK066(chu)001:8759: yid bzhin mtshan ldan gyi gzungs ma dang slob ma mi spang /
NK066(chu)001:8761: khyung chen gshog pa ya mi bral //
NK066(chu)001:8763: gnam lcags ngur mo'i mtshon mched nang 'thag /
NK066(chu)001:8765: gcan gzan rol ba'i lhag mi gzhan gyis nyams pa'i rdzas la mi spyad /
NK066(chu)001:8767: rdo rje brag chen mi gzhig gzhan gyi dkyil 'khor la slob dpon gyi gdan mi gzhig /
NK066(chu)001:8769: gzhan gyi ra ba d+r+wa ba'i mtshams mi khongs dbral //
NK066(chu)001:8770: sgron me rlung gis bsad ting 'dzin byings rmugs su mi gtong /
NK066(chu)001:8772: ye shes chu rgyun bzlas pa'i rgyun mi bcad bcad pa spang //
NK066(chu)001:8773: bka' rtags phyag rgya dbang rtags dang brda ma brjed par bya /
NK066(chu)001:8775: rdo rje pha lam mkhar mi skye bo mthu byed pa mi bzlog /
NK066(chu)001:8777: gtsug gi nor bu slob dpon la mi smad /
NK066(chu)001:8779: 'di dag bsrung bar bya ba ste //
NK066(chu)001:8780: lhag par gces pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK066(chu)001:8784: de las phye ba'i rnam grangs so //
NK066(chu)001:8786: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK066(chu)001:8787: yan lag gi dam tshig bcu'o //
NK066(chu)001:8789: bla med mi spang bla ma bkur //
NK066(chu)001:8792: byang sems rnam gnyis slob dpon drug /
NK066(chu)001:8793: mched bzhi sngags gsum phyag rgya bzhi //
NK066(chu)001:8794: gsang bcu rtsa bar shes par bya //
NK066(chu)001:8795: zhes pas rtsa ba lnga'i dang po bla med mi spang ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:8796: yul lhag pa don dam dang kun rdzob byang sems gnyis so //
NK066(chu)001:8797: de mi spang ba ni snang stong gnyis su med
NK066(chu)001:8798: par rtogs nas sgo gsum lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK066(chu)001:8799: phyag rgya las mi 'da' bar byed pa ste /
NK066(chu)001:8801: rang lus rgyal ba'i phyag rgya che //
NK066(chu)001:8802: sems can khams kyang der shes shing //
NK066(chu)001:8803: snang stong gnyis med rdo rje'i sku //
NK066(chu)001:8804: byas mthong thos pa thams cad kyang //
NK066(chu)001:8805: sems phyir gang yang byas snang med //
NK066(chu)001:8806: dran dang shes bzhin sngon btang la //
NK066(chu)001:8807: dus gsum rgyun du ma dran na //
NK066(chu)001:8808: theg chen sngags par ci yis chud //
NK066(chu)001:8810: gnyis pa bla ma bkur ba la //
NK066(chu)001:8812: kun gyis dam par bkur zhing bka' drin cung zad thob pa spyi'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:8813: rab byung gi mkhan po lta bu chos sgor 'dren pa'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:8814: dam tshig 'bogs shing dbang bskur ba ni dam tshig dbang gi dang /
NK066(chu)001:8815: bshags yul du gyur pa nyams chag skong ba'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:8816: chos 'chad pa'i slob dpon lta bu shes rgyud 'grol ba'i dang /
NK066(chu)001:8817: zab mo'i man ngag ston pa'i bla ma dang drug ste /
NK066(chu)001:8819: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK066(chu)001:8820: nyams chag skong dang shes rgyud 'grol //
NK066(chu)001:8821: man ngag lung gi slob dpon rnams //
NK066(chu)001:8825: man ngag nod pa rnams ni lhag par yang bkur ba'i yul te /
NK066(chu)001:8827: rgyud 'grol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK066(chu)001:8831: yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po dang //
NK066(chu)001:8832: khu bo pha dang ma dang mig /
NK066(chu)001:8833: snying bas lhag pa'i tshul bltas te //
NK066(chu)001:8834: zhes pa'i bkur tshul gyi dpe slob dpon drug la rim bzhin sbyar la /
NK066(chu)001:8835: khyad par du lhag pa'i yul gsum ni /
NK066(chu)001:8838: dkon mchog bzhi par blta ba gang rung zhig nos
NK066(chu)001:8839: te sgo gsum zol zog med pas ci mnyes byed
NK066(chu)001:8840: pa'o // gsum pa sngags rgya rgyun mi gcod pa la //
NK066(chu)001:8841: yul sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi ste /
NK066(chu)001:8843: rtsa ba bskyed dang las sngags dang //
NK066(chu)001:8844: dam tshig las dang chos dang ni //
NK066(chu)001:8845: sku nyid phyag rgya chen po bzhi //
NK066(chu)001:8847: de dag rgyun mi gcad par nyams su len pa'i tshul ni /
NK066(chu)001:8848: brtson pa rab 'bring tha gsum du sbyar nas gsungs te /
NK066(chu)001:8850: rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nam //
NK066(chu)001:8851: nyin gsum mtshan gsum gnyis gcig tu //
NK066(chu)001:8852: ma yengs tsam du ngang gis bzla //
NK066(chu)001:8853: 'bring gis zla gcig dus drug dang //
NK066(chu)001:8854: dus bzhi'i bar du mi gcad cing //
NK066(chu)001:8855: tha ma bya ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK066(chu)001:8856: zla re'am ra ba'i dus dag tu //
NK066(chu)001:8857: brtson pas 'bad de mi byed pa //
NK066(chu)001:8858: byang chub sa bon brlag pa yin //
NK066(chu)001:8859: tshogs dang gtor ma'ang de bzhin du //
NK066(chu)001:8863: mched la byams par bya ba la //
NK066(chu)001:8865: spyi'i mched sems can thams cad /
NK066(chu)001:8866: ring ba'i mched sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la zhugs so cog /
NK066(chu)001:8867: nye ba'i mched sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa /
NK066(chu)001:8868: de las kyang khyad par nang 'dres pa'i mched bla
NK066(chu)001:8869: ma gcig gis bsdus pa ni pha gcig gi spun
NK066(chu)001:8870: dang / de'i shugs kyis dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus
NK066(chu)001:8871: pa ni ma gcig pa'i spun du don gyis 'gyur
NK066(chu)001:8872: dang / te / de gnyis ni lhag par yang byams par bya ba'i yul lo //
NK066(chu)001:8873: de ltar yang gsal bkra las /
NK066(chu)001:8874: mtha' yas sems can rang rig phyir //
NK066(chu)001:8875: gang yang bdag las gzhan min dang //
NK066(chu)001:8876: bde gshegs snying po'i spun yin phyir //
NK066(chu)001:8877: ma 'ongs sangs rgyas rang bzhin ni //
NK066(chu)001:8878: spyi yi mched de pha tshan bzhin //
NK066(chu)001:8879: sangs rgyas chos zhugs ring ba dang //
NK066(chu)001:8880: lta spyod mthun pa nye bar bshad //
NK066(chu)001:8881: pha gcig dam tshig nang 'dres pa /
NK066(chu)001:8883: de dag la byams pa bya lugs ni /
NK066(chu)001:8884: snying po byang chub kyi bar du mi 'bral bar
NK066(chu)001:8885: bya ba'i bsam pas rtag par brtse zhing gdung bar
NK066(chu)001:8886: bya ba ste / rngam glog las /
NK066(chu)001:8887: rdo rje spun la gdung sems kyang //
NK066(chu)001:8889: yang dag lam du zhugs pa la //
NK066(chu)001:8890: rngan dang bcas pa'i sems tsam yang //
NK066(chu)001:8891: rtag tu spang bar bya ba yin //
NK066(chu)001:8892: brtse zhing gdung ba'i shugs phyung la //
NK066(chu)001:8893: gcig la gcig ni mig bzhin blta //
NK066(chu)001:8897: dam nyams dam las log pa dang //
NK066(chu)001:8898: dam med dkyil 'khor ma mthong dang //
NK066(chu)001:8901: de dag la gsang bar bya ba ni /
NK066(chu)001:8903: spyi dang bar gsang bzhi bzhi dang //
NK066(chu)001:8904: 'os dang gnyer gtad rnam pa bcu //
NK066(chu)001:8906: de la spyir gsang bzhi ni /
NK066(chu)001:8908: lta zab spyod pa barlang po dang //
NK066(chu)001:8909: lha ming gzungs dang grub rtags rnams //
NK066(chu)001:8911: theg dman sogs blo dman rnams dang //
NK066(chu)001:8912: spyod pa ni ma 'dres pa la gsang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:8913: yi dam gyi lha dang sngags dang grub rtags gsum
NK066(chu)001:8914: ni ma 'dres pa la bstan na dam tshig nyams
NK066(chu)001:8915: la / 'dres pa la bstan na'ang dngos grub nyams par gsungs pas thams cad du gsang bar bya'o //
NK066(chu)001:8918: sgrub pa'i gnas dus grogs dang rdzas //
NK066(chu)001:8919: bar du gsang la bsgrub par bya //
NK066(chu)001:8921: sgrub pa byed pa'i bar de srid du khyad par du gsang bar bya ba'o //
NK066(chu)001:8923: mchod rdzas dang gsang ba'i spyod pa dang mched kyi
NK066(chu)001:8924: ngan spyod la sogs pa mthong ba dang thos su
NK066(chu)001:8927: bla ma dang mched kyis 'di dang 'di gsang bar gyis shig ces gdams pa rnams so //
NK066(chu)001:8928: de dag ni chos la skyon yod pas gsang dgos pa ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:8930: gsang sngags skyon yod ma yin te //
NK066(chu)001:8931: sems can don phyir rab tu gsang //
NK066(chu)001:8932: gsang thub dngos grub mi yal bas //
NK066(chu)001:8933: gsang phyir brda dag sna tshogs gsungs //
NK066(chu)001:8935: de ltar lnga po de ni lam dang 'bras bu'i
NK066(chu)001:8936: gzhir gyur pas na rtsa ba'i dam tshig ces bya'o
NK066(chu)001:8937: // de dag rtsa ba gsum du bsdu na /
NK066(chu)001:8938: bla ma dang mched la bsrung ba gnyis sku'i dam tshig /
NK066(chu)001:8939: sngags rgya gsung gi dam tshig /
NK066(chu)001:8940: byang sems dang gsang bcu thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK066(chu)001:8944: gsang ba mi smra ba gsum bsrung ba'i dam tshig /
NK066(chu)001:8945: byang sems dang sngags rgya gnyis sgrub pa'i dam tshig go //
NK066(chu)001:8947: sku gsung thugs kyi bgrang tshul gzhan sngar ltar las
NK066(chu)001:8948: bla med mi spang bzur du bgrangs te rtsa ba
NK066(chu)001:8949: bzhir 'dod na'ang / kho bo ni bla med mi
NK066(chu)001:8950: spang ba thugs su bsdus na legs par mngon te
NK066(chu)001:8951: bzhir 'dod na'ang / / bde 'dus zhi ba'i rgyud las /
NK066(chu)001:8952: byang chub sems gsum bsgom pa ni //
NK066(chu)001:8953: rdo rje thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK066(chu)001:8955: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig la /
NK066(chu)001:8959: gti mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK066(chu)001:8960: nga rgyal phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:8963: mi spang dam tshig bshad bya ba //
NK066(chu)001:8964: yang dag dug lnga log dug lnga //
NK066(chu)001:8965: zhes pas spyir yang dag pa'i dug lnga dang /
NK066(chu)001:8968: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK066(chu)001:8969: lta bas phyogs ris dang spyod pas blang dang dor bya'i chos 'byed pa med pa ni gti mug /
NK066(chu)001:8970: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i 'gro la thugs rjes chags pa ni 'dod chags /
NK066(chu)001:8971: rang byung gi ye shes kyis log lta 'joms pa'i zhe sdang /
NK066(chu)001:8972: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba gshongs su mi 'bebs pa'i nga rgyal /
NK066(chu)001:8973: gnyis 'dzin can gyi lta spyod mnyam nyid kyi klong
NK066(chu)001:8974: du mi shong ba'i phrag dog rnams ni bdag gzhan
NK066(chu)001:8975: chos gsum gyi don gyi phyir mi spang ngo //
NK066(chu)001:8977: nyon mongs pa lnga mi spong bar bshad pa de dag /
NK066(chu)001:8978: gsang ba yin nam bsgrag pa yin zhe na //
NK066(chu)001:8981: drang don yin nam nges don yin zer na //
NK066(chu)001:8982: nyon mongs pa mi spang ba drang don du bstan pa la dgos pa med pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:8983: 'dir blo chen mnyam pa'ang lta bas zin pa la nges don du bstan no //
NK066(chu)001:8984: ci'i phyir mi spong zhe na //
NK066(chu)001:8985: log pa'i dug lnga chos can spang bya ma yin te /
NK066(chu)001:8986: spang bya'i rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8987: thabs la mkhas pa'i lam yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK066(chu)001:8988: rang bzhin chen po yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:8990: chos thams cad rang rang gi ngo bos stong pa'i phyir spang mi dgos te /
NK066(chu)001:8991: smig rgyu la chu rags mi dgos pa bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:8992: de ltar yang rdo rje las /
NK066(chu)001:8993: nyon mongs rnams ni sgyu 'dra ngo bos stong //
NK066(chu)001:8995: phyir mi ldog pa 'khor lo'i mdo las /
NK066(chu)001:8996: ma rig nam mkha' ji bzhin te //
NK066(chu)001:8997: chos rnams thams cad mtshan nyid med //
NK066(chu)001:8998: 'dod chags med cing zhe sdang med //
NK066(chu)001:8999: nga rgyal dang ni phrag dog kun //
NK066(chu)001:9000: sgyu 'dra ngo bo nyid med de //
NK066(chu)001:9001: yod med mi dmigs rten dang bral //
NK066(chu)001:9004: thabs kyis zin na nyon mongs pa spyad kyang mi
NK066(chu)001:9005: 'ching bar rnam par grol ba'i lam du'agyura ba'i phyir
NK066(chu)001:9007: dug gi sman mar gyis dug nad 'joms pa bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:9009: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa che //
NK066(chu)001:9010: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchog /
NK066(chu)001:9011: thams cad thams cad rol pa yis //
NK066(chu)001:9012: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:9015: thabs chen rnams dang ldan pa la //
NK066(chu)001:9016: nyon mongs byang chub yan lag 'gyur //
NK066(chu)001:9019: nyon mongs lnga nyid don ye shes lnga yin la /
NK066(chu)001:9020: rtags rgyal ba rigs lnga yin pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:9022: nyon mongs pa las rdzas gzhan du sku dang ye shes ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK066(chu)001:9023: byas pa dang mi rtag pa bzhin no //
NK066(chu)001:9024: de ltar yang dam tshig nyer brgyad pa las /
NK066(chu)001:9025: phrag dog la sogs nyon mongs lnga rnams ni //
NK066(chu)001:9026: ye nas rigs lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:9028: yang mi spong ba'i dgos pa gang zhe na //
NK066(chu)001:9029: nyon mongs pa dug lnga chos can /
NK066(chu)001:9031: dgos pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir //
NK066(chu)001:9032: de'ang dngos zhen bzlog pa'i dgos pa yod de /
NK066(chu)001:9033: sngon khyim bdag mes nyen pa zhig me ni bsreg pa kho na'o snyam pa la /
NK066(chu)001:9034: phyis drang srong me'i gtsang sbra can dang ri dwags
NK066(chu)001:9035: me byi la'i spyod pa mthong bas me tsha ba
NK066(chu)001:9036: phyogs gcig pa'i mngon zhen log pa ltar theg pa
NK066(chu)001:9037: 'og ma bas dug lnga 'khor ba'i rgyu kho nar
NK066(chu)001:9038: 'dzin pa'i mngon zhen bzlog pa'i phyir ro //
NK066(chu)001:9039: gnyis pa bka' zab mo la gus pa skye ba'i dgos pa yod de /
NK066(chu)001:9040: theg pa 'og mas nyon mongs pa la skyon du bltas te spang 'geg sbyong sgyur byed la /
NK066(chu)001:9041: 'dir spyad pas grol ba ni ngo mtshar ro snyam
NK066(chu)001:9042: du bka' zab mo la yid ches kyi gus pa
NK066(chu)001:9043: skye ba'o // gsum pa chos nyid zab mo la rtogs pa'i blo myur ba'i dgos pa yod de /
NK066(chu)001:9044: nyon mongs pa chos nyid dang dbyer med du rtogs
NK066(chu)001:9045: pas lam 'bras gzhan nas btsal mi dgos par thag
NK066(chu)001:9047: mdor na gnyen pos spangs pa dang rang ga mar
NK066(chu)001:9048: spyad pa gnyis ka nyes pa las mi 'da' ste
NK066(chu)001:9049: / zhe sdang sogs nyon mongs pa rnams gnyen po
NK066(chu)001:9050: byams pa sogs kyis spangs na rgyu'i theg par grol
